var book = {
	"name": "Eksodos",
	"numChapters": 40,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang Israel, kiba la wan sha ka ri Ijipt; uwei pa uwei bad la ka ïing ki la ïawan ryngkat bad u Jakob.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Reuben, u Simeon, u Lebi, bad u Judah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u Issakhar, u Sabulon, bad u Benjamin;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u Dan, u Naphtali, u Gad, bad u Asher.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki mynsiem baroh te kiba la mih na ka syngkai u Jakob ki la long jin hynñiewphew ki mynsiem; naba u Joseph u la don lypa ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Joseph u la ïap noh, bad ki hynmen jong u baroh, bad kata ka pateng bynriew.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïaroi, bad ki la ïaroi kyrhai, ki la ïaman bun eh, bad ki la nang khraw bor ruh shikatdei; te la pyndap ïa kata ka ri da ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta te, la mih u syiem thymmai ha ka ri Ijipt, u bym shym la ithuh ïa u Joseph.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la ong ha la ki briew, “Ha khmih, ki briew jong ki khun Israel ki la kham bun bad ki kham don bor ruh ban ïa ngi:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ïa, ngin ïakham leh sian bad ki; ba ïoh kin ïaroi, bad haba kan mih ka thma, kan jia ba kin ïashah bad ki nongshun jong ngi, bad ïaleh bad ngi, te kumta kin leit mih noh na kane ka ri.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, ki la thung ïa ki sordar halor jong ki ban pynshitom ïa ki da ki jingkit jong ki. Te ki la tei ki nongbah ki jingkynshew ïa u Pharaoh, ka Pithom bad ka Raamses keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te katba ki la nang pynshitom ïa ki, katta ki la ïa nang roi pynban. Bad la pynjynjar ïa ki namar ki khun Israel.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki Ijipt ki la pyntrei ïa ki khun Israel da kaba jur eh:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki la ïa-pynkthang ïa ka jingim jong ki da ka jingpynlong mraw kaba shitom ha ka 'dewbyrtha bad ha u maw-it, bad ha ka kynja jingtrei baroh ha ka lyngkha, ka jingtrei jong ki baroh, ha kaba la pyntrei ïa ki ka la long da kaba jur keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta u syiem ka ri Ijipt u la kren ha ki Hebru kynthei kiba bat khun, kiba ka kyrteng kawei na ki long “Ka Shiphrah”, bad ka kyrteng kawei pat “Ka Puah”:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad u la ong, “Haba phi leh ïa ka kam bat khun ha ki kynthei Hebru, bad ba phi khmih ïa ki haba ki dang kha; lada i long shynrang, te phin pynïap noh ïa u; hynrei, lada i long kynthei, te kan ïoh im.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, kita ki nongbat khun ki la sheptieng ïa U Blei, bad kim shym leh kumba uta u syiem ka ri Ijipt u la hukum ïa ki, hynrei, ki la ri im ïa ki khun shynrang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uta u syiem ka ri Ijipt u la khot ïa kita ki nongbat khun, bad u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi la leh ïa kane, bad ba phi la ri im ïa ki khun shynrang?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kita ki nongbat khun te ki la ong ha u Pharaoh, “Namar ki kynthei Hebru kim long kum ki kynthei Ijipt; naba ki long kiba shait, bad ki kha haba ki nongbat khun kim pat poi ha ki.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar kata, U Blei u la leh bha ïa kita ki nongbat khun: bad kita ki briew ki la nang roi, bad ki la nang khraw bor de shikatdei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te namar ba kita ki nongbat khun ki la sheptieng ïa U Blei, ki Hebru ki la ïa nang roi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la hukum ïa ki briew jong u baroh, u da ong, “Ïa ki khun shynrang baroh kiba yn kha to phin bred noh sha kata ka wah, hynrei, ïa ki khun kynthei baroh phin ri im.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la leit uwei u briew na ka ïing u Lebi, bad u la shongkurim ïa ka khun u Lebi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kata ka kynthei ka la punkhun, bad ka la kha khun shynrang de; te haba ka la ïohi ba u long uba bhabriew, ka la buhrieh ïa u, lai bnai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba kam lah buhrieh shuh ïa u, ka la thaw ka shang ïa u da ki thungshut, bad ka la lape ïa ka da ka 'dewbyrtha bad da ka bsiang ruh; bad ka la buh ïa ita i khunlung hapoh ruh, bad ka la buh ïa ka hapdeng ki kor harud kata ka wah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka hynmen jong u ka la ïeng na sha jngai, ban ïoh tip aïu kan sa jia ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka khun u Pharaoh ka la wan hiar ban sum ha kata ka wah; bad ki shakri kynthei jong ka ki la ïaid kai harud ka wah; te haba ka la ïohi ïa kata ka shang hapdeng ki kor, ka la phah shim ïa ka ha ka shakri jong ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ynda ka la plie ïa ka, ka la ïohi ïa ita i khunlung; te ha khmih, ita i khunlung i ïam. Bad ka la sngewsynei ïa u, ka la ong ruh, “Une u long uwei na ki khun Hebru.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ka hynmen jong u te ka la ong ha ka khun u Pharaoh, “Ngan leit khot ka nongbat khun ïa pha na ki kynthei Hebru, ba kan ïoh ri ïa ita i khunlung ïa pha?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ka khun u Pharaoh ka la ong ha ka, “Khie leit.” Te kata ka khynnah ka la leit, bad ka la khot ïa ka kmie jong ita i khunlung.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka khun u Pharaoh te ka la ong ha ka, “To shim noh ïa ine i khunlung, bad to ri ruh ïa i na ka bynta jong nga, bad ngan ai ïa ka bainong jong pha.” Kata ka briew te ka la shim ïa ita i khunlung, bad ka la ri ïa i.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynba uta u khynnah u la san, ka la wallam ïa u ha ka khun u Pharaoh, bad u la long u khun jong ka. Bad ka la khot ka kyrteng jong u, “u Moses”: namar, ka la ong, “na ka um nga la sei ïa u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha kita ki sngi, mynba u Moses u la rangbah, ba u la mih shabar sha ki para jong u, bad u la khmih ïa ki jingkit jong ki: bad u la ïohi ïa uwei u Ijipt ba u da shoh ïa u Hebru uba na ki para jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u la khmih shane bad shawei, te haba u la ïohi bymdon mano mano, u la pynïap ïa uta u Ijipt, bad u la buhrieh ïa u ha u shyiap.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te mynba u la leit pat ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, ha khmih, ar ngut kiba na ki Hebru ki la ïashoh: te u la ong ha uta uba la leh bymdei, “Na ka balei ba me shoh ïa la u para?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la ong, “Uei ba la pynlong syiem bad nongbishar ïa me halor jong ngi? Me mut ma me ban pynïap ïa nga, kumba me la pynïap ïa uta u Ijipt?” Te u Moses u la sheptieng, bad u la ong ruh, “Shisha ïa kane la bna.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te mynba u Pharaoh u la ïohsngew ïa kane, u la thew ban pynïap noh ïa u Moses. Hynrei, u Moses u la phet ïap noh na khmat u Pharaoh, bad u la shong sah ruh ha ka ri Midian: bad u la shong lyngngeit harud ka pukri.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u lyngdoh ka ri Midian u la don hynñiew ngut ki khun kynthei: bad kita ki la wan tong um, bad ki la pyndap ïa ki shyngoid ïa ka ban ai um ïa ki kynhun langbrot u kpa jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ki nongaplangbrot ki la wan bad ki la beh noh ïa ki: hynrei, u Moses u la ïeng joit bad u la ïarap ïa ki, u la ai um ruh ïa ki kynhun langbrot jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan ha u Reuel u kpa jong ki, u la kylli, “Kumno ba phi la ïawan shen katta katta mynta?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la ïathuh te, “U kynja Ijipt u la pyllait noh ïa ngi na ka kti kita ki nongaplangbrot, bad u la tong um ruh biang ïa ngi, bad u la ai um ïa ka kynhun langbrot.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la kylli ïa la ki khun kynthei, “Shano te u don? balei phi la iehnoh ïa uta u rangbah? to khot ïa u ban bam jingbam.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Moses u la sngewbha ban shong duh bad uta u briew: u te u la ai kurim ha u Moses ïa ka Sipporah ka khun jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka te ka la kha khun shynrang, bad u la khot ka kyrteng jong u, “u Gershom”: naba u la ong, “nga la long u nongwei ha ka ri nongwei.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ka la jia te hadien bun sngi, ba u la ïap noh uta u syiem ka ri Ijipt: te ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ud namar kata ka jinglongmraw, bad ki la ïalynñiar ruh, bad kata ka jinglynñiar jong ki ka la wan kiew sha U Blei namar kata ka jinglongmraw.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Blei u la sngew ïa ka jingud jong ki, bad U Blei u la kynmaw ruh ïa ka jutang jong u bad u Abraham, bad u Isaak, bad u Jakob ruh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te U Blei u la khmih isynei ruh ha ki khun Israel, bad U Blei u la ïit ithuh ïa ki."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Moses u la dang ap ïa ka kynhun u Jethro u kthaw kurim jong u, uba u lyngdoh ka ri Midian: bad u la ïalam ïa kata ka kynhun sha lyndet ka ri khlaw, bad u la wan sha u lum U Blei, sha Horeb keiñ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u angel U Trai u la mihpaw ha u ha ka thylliej ding napdeng ka 'law lynnong: te u la khmih, bad ha khmih, kata ka 'law lynnong ka la ing da ka ding, hynrei, kata ka 'law lynnong kam ing duh noh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Moses u la ong, “Ngan phai kyrpang mynta ban khmih ïa kane ka jingipaw bakhraw, na ka balei ba ka 'law lynnong kam ing duh noh.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te mynba U Trai u la ïohi ba u la phai kyrpang ban jngoh, U Blei u la khot ïa u napdeng kata ka 'law lynnong, bad u da ong, “Ko Moses, Ko Moses.” U te u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih ma nga.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la ong, “Wat wan hajan shane: to da loit noh ïa ki juti jong me na la ki sla'jat, naba kata ka jaka ha kaba me ïeng ka long ka khyndew bakyntang.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la ong ruh, “Nga long ma nga U Blei u kpa jong me, U Blei u Abraham, U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob de.” Bad u Moses u la buhrieh ïa la ka khmat; naba u la sheptieng ban khmih ha U Blei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Trai u la ong ruh, “Nga la ïohi shisha ïa ka jingshitom ki briew jong nga kiba ha ka ri Ijipt, bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jinglynñiar jong ki namar ki sordar jong ki; naba nga la tip ïa ka jingsngewsih sat jong ki;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad nga la wan hiar ma nga ban pyllait noh ïa ki na ka kti ki Ijipt, bad ban ïalam noh ïa ki na kata ka ri sha ka ri babha bad bakhraw, sha ka ri keiñ kaba tuid da ka dud bad ka ngap; sha ka jaka ki Kanaan, bad ki Hit, bad ki Amor, bad ki Peris, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus de.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mynta te namar kata, ha khmih, ka jinglynñiar ki khun Israel ka la wan kiew sha nga: bad nga la ïohi ïa kata ka jingbanbeiñ da kaba kita ki Ijipt ki la ïabanbeiñ ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, ale mynta te, ngan phah ïa me sha u Pharaoh, ba men ïoh ïalam noh ïa ki briew jong nga ki khun Israel keiñ, na ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u Moses u la ong ha U Blei, “Nga, nga long uei, ba ngan leit sha u Pharaoh, bad ba ngan ïalam noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la ong, “Shisha ngan long lem bad me; bad kane kan long ka dak ïa me, ba ma nga hi nga la phah ïa me: ynda me la ïalam noh ïa ki briew jong nga na ka ri Ijipt, phin ïoh shakri ïa U Blei halor une u lum.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Moses u la ïathuh ha U Blei, “Ha khmih, haba ngan wan sha ki khun Israel, bad ngan ong ha ki, ‘U Blei ki kpa jong phi u la phah ïa nga ha phi’; bad ba kin kylli ïa nga, ‘Kaei ka kyrteng jong u?’ ngan ong aïu ha ki?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad U Blei u la ïathuh ha u Moses, “NGA long ba NGA long”: u la ong ruh, “Kumne men ong ha ki khun Israel, NGA long u la phah ïa nga ha phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nalor kane U Blei u la ong ruh ha u Moses, “Kumne men ong ha ki khun Israel, ‘U Trai uba U Blei ki kpa jong phi, U Blei u Abraham, U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob ruh, u la phah ïa nga ha phi’: kane ka long ka kyrteng jong nga ha la ka rta, bad kane ka long ka jingpynkynmaw ïa nga sha ki pateng bynriew baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To leit, to ïalum lang ruh ïa ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel, bad to ong ruh ha ki, ‘U Trai uba U Blei ki kpa jong phi, U Blei u Abraham, u Isaak, bad u Jakob de, u la mihpaw ha nga, u da ong, “Shisha nga la wan jngoh ïa phi, bad nga la ïohi ïa kaba la leh ïa phi ha ka ri Ijipt;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> nga la ong ruh, Ngan ïalam noh artet ïa phi na ka jingshitom ka ri Ijipt sha ka ri ki Kanaan, bad ki Hit, bad ki Amor, bad ki Peris, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus ruh de, sha ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud bad ka ngap.” ’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki te kin sngap ïa ka ktien jong me: bad men wan, ma me, bad ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel, sha u syiem ka ri Ijipt, bad phin ong ha u, ‘U Trai, uba U Blei jong ki Hebru, u la ïashem bad ngi: mynta te ngi kyrpad ïa me, to ai ba ngin ïaleit lai sngi lynti sha ri khlaw, ba ngin ïoh kñia ainguh ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te nga tip skhem ba u syiem ka ri Ijipt un ym shah ïa phi ban leit, lymda da ka kti badonbor.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar kata, ngan kner ïa la ka kti, bad ngan shoh ïa ka ri Ijipt da ki kam phylla jong nga baroh ïa kiba ngan sa leh hapdeng jong ka: hadien kata te, un sa pyllait noh ïa phi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ngan ai ha une u paidbah ka jingsngewbha ha khmat ki Ijipt: kan sa jia ruh, ha kaba phin leit noh, phin ym leit noh suda,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hynrei, ka kynthei baroh kan pan na la ka paramarjan, bad na kata kaba shong basa ha ïing jong ka, ïa ki jingdeng rupa, bad ïa ki jingdeng ksiar, bad ïa ki jaiñkup jaiñsem: bad phin pynkup ïa ki ha ki khun shynrang jong phi bad ha ki khun kynthei jong phi; bad phin lute ïa ki Ijipt.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Moses u la ïathuh pat bad u la ong, “Hynrei, ha khmih, kin ym ïangeit ïa nga, lymne sngap ïa ka ktien jong nga: naba kin ong, ‘U Trai um shym la mihpaw ha me.’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U Trai u la kylli ïa u, “Kaei kata kaba ha ka kti jong me?” U te u la ïathuh, “U diengduh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la ong, “To bred ïa u ha ka khyndew.” Bad u la bred ïa u ha ka khyndew, te u la kylla bseiñ; bad u Moses u la kiar noh na u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To sei noh ïa la ka kti, bad to bat ïa u na u tdong”: (u te u la sei noh ïa la ka kti, bad u la kem ïa u, bad u la kylla diengduh pat ha ka kti jong u:)",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “ba kin ïoh ngeit ba U Trai uba U Blei ki kpa jong ki, U Blei u Abraham, bad U Blei u Isaak, bad U Blei u Jakob ruh, u la mihpaw ha me.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nalor kata ruh, U Trai u la ong ha u, “To buh mynta ïa la ka kti ha la ka shadem.” U te u la buh ïa la ka kti ha la ka shadem: te mynba u la sei noh ïa ka, ha khmih, ka la thohlieh, kat ka ïor.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la ong ruh, “To buh ïa la ka kti ha la ka shadem pat.” (Bad u la buh ïa la ka kti ha la ka shadem pat; bad u la sei noh ïa ka na la ka shadem, te, ha khmih, ka la kylla pat kum ka doh jong u hi.)",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Te kan sa jia, lada kim ïangeit ïa me, lymne sngap ïa ka jingsawa jong ka dak banyngkong, ba kin sa ngeit keiñ ïa ka jingsawa ka dak ba-ar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, lada kin ym ngeit ruh ïa kine ki dak baroh ar, lymne sngap ïa ka ktien jong me, to men shim na ka um jong kata ka wah, bad theh ïa ka ha ryngkew: bad kata ka um ïa kaba me shim na kata ka wah kan sa kylla snam ha ryngkew.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha U Trai, “A Trai jong nga, ngam long uba pnah ka shyntur, lymne mynno mynno, lymne naduh ba me la kren bad la u shakri: hynrei, nga long uba thlun ka jingkren, bad uba thlun u thylliej.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la kylli ïa u, “Uei ba la thaw ïa ka shyntur u briew? Lane uei ba la thaw ïa u bymnangkren, lane u bakyllut, lane u bapeit, lane u bamatlah? Ym long ma nga U Trai?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata, to leit mynta, bad nga ngan long lem bad ka shyntur jong me, bad ngan hikai ïa me ïa kaei ba men kren keiñ.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U te u la ong, “A Trai, to phah, nga kyrpad ïa me, da uta ïa uba me dei ban phah.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh pyrshah ïa u Moses, bad u la ong, “U Aaron uba u Lebi um long u hynmen jong me? Nga tip ba u nang kren bha. Bad ha khmih ruh, u wan mih ban tan ïa me: te ynda un ïohi ïa me, un kmen ha la ka dohnud.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad to men kren ha u, men buh ruh ïa kine ki ktien ha ka shyntur jong u: ma nga te ngan long lem bad ka shyntur jong u ruh, bad ngan hikai ïa phi ïa kaei ba phin leh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad un long u nongpynkren jong me ha u paidbah: kumta, ma u shisha un long kum ka shyntur ïa me, bad ma me ruh men long kum U Blei ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Men shim ruh ïa une u diengduh ha ka kti jong me, da uba men sa leh ïa ki dak phylla.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Moses u la leit phai pat sha u Jethro u kthaw kurim jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan leit wan noh sha ki para jong nga kiba ha ka ri Ijipt, bad khmih la ki dang im ne em.” Te u Jethro u la ong ha u Moses, “To khie leit ha kaba suk.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses ha ka ri Midian, “To leit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt: naba ki la ïap noh baroh kita ki briew kiba la wad ïa ka jingim jong me.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim ïa la ka tnga bad ïa la ki khun shynrang, bad u la buh ïa ki halor ki kadda, bad u la leit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt: bad u Moses u la shim ïa u diengduh jong U Blei ha la ka kti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ynda me la leit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt, to sumar ba men leh ha khmat u Pharaoh ïa kita ki kam phylla baroh ïa kiba nga la ai ha ka kti jong me: hynrei, ngan pyneh ïa ka dohnud jong u, te un ym pyllait noh ïa u paidbah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad men ong ha u Pharaoh, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, u Israel u long u khun jong nga, uba kha nyngkong jong nga keiñ,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad nga la ong ha me, “To pyllait noh ïa u khun jong nga ba un ïoh shakri ïa nga;” te lada mem treh ban pyllait noh ïa u, ha khmih, ngan pynïap noh ïa u khun jong me, uba la kha nyngkong jong me keiñ.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ka la jia te ha lynti ha ka ïingbasa, ba U Trai u la ïashem bad u, bad U la thew ban pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ka Sipporah ka la shim ïa u maw banep, bad ka la otsher ïa u khun jong ka, bad ka la bred ha ki kjat jong u; bad ka la ong ruh, “Shisha u tnga uba bit snam me long ïa nga.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la pyllait noh ïa u. Te ka la ong, “Me long u tnga uba bit snam, namar ka jingotsher.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Aaron, “To leit sha ri khlaw ban tan ïa u Moses.” U la leit te, bad u la ïashem bad u ha u lum jong U Blei, bad u la doh ïa u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Moses u la ïathuh ha u Aaron ïa ki ktien baroh jong U Trai uba la phah ïa u, bad ïa kita ki dak phylla baroh ïa kiba u la lah hukum ïa u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïaleit bad ki la ïalum lang ïa ki tymmen basan baroh jong ki khun Israel.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Aaron u la kren ïa kita ki ktien baroh ïa kiba U Trai u la lah kren ha u Moses, bad u la leh ruh ïa kita ki dak phylla ha khmat u paidbah.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad uta u paidbah u la ngeit: te mynba ki la ïohsngew ba U Trai u la wan-i ïa ki khun Israel, bad ba u la khmih ruh de ïa ka jingshitom jong ki, ynda kumta, ki la dem ïa la ki khlieh bad ki la ïamane ruh."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kata, u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïaleit hapoh, bad ki la ïathuh ha u Pharaoh, “Kumne u ong U Trai uba U Blei jong ki Israel, ‘To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam ïa nga ha ri khlaw.’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong, “U Trai u long uei, ba ngan kohnguh ma nga ïa ka ktien jong u ïa ka ban pyllait noh ïa ki Israel? Ïa U Trai ngam ithuh, bad ïa ki Israel ngan ym pyllait noh keiñ.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “U Blei jong ki Hebru u la ïashem bad ngi: to shah ba ngin leit, ngi kyrpad ïa me, lai sngi lynti sha kata ka ri khlaw, ba ngin ïoh kñia ainguh ha U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi; ïoh ba un pynhap halor jong ngi da ka jingïapthem, lane da ka waitlam.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u syiem ka ri Ijipt u la ong ha ki, “Na ka balei ma phi, u Moses bad u Aaron, phi pynpep ïa ki briew na ka jingtrei jong ki? khie leit phi sha la ki jingkit.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Pharaoh u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, kine ki briew jong kane ka ri mynta ki la bun, bad phi la pynpep ïa ki na ki jingkit jong ki.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la hukum ha kajuh ka sngi ïa ki sordar jong kita ki briew, bad ïa ki rangbah jong ki, u da ong,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Wat ai 'langïap shuh ha kine ki briew ban thaw maw-it kumba baroh shi katta: to kin leit ïalum 'langïap ïa lade.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ka jingkheiñ ki maw-it ïa kiba ki ju thaw mynno mynno ruh, phin buh halor jong ki; wat pynduna satia na kata: naba ki long jaipdeh; namar kata, ki ïapyrta, da kaba ong, ‘To shah ba ngin leit kñia ainguh ïa U Blei jong ngi.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To nang pynban khia ïa ka jingtrei halor kine ki briew, ba kin ïatrei shitom ha ka; bad wat shah shuh ba kin ïasngap ïa ki ktien thala.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki sordar jong u paidbah ki la ïamih noh, bad ki rangbah jong ki, bad ki la kren ha u paidbah, ki da ong, “Kumne u ong u Pharaoh, ‘Ngan ym ai 'langïap shuh ïa phi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Khie leit phi, to wad 'langïap ïa lade kat shaba phin shem ïa u: pynban, yn ym pynduna satia na ka jingtrei jong phi.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, uta u paidbah u la saphred kylleng ka ri Ijipt ban ïalum ïa u 'lang kba ha ka jaka u 'langïap.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te kita ki sordar ki la pynkyrkieh ïa ki, da kaba ong, “To pyndep noh ïa ki jingtrei jong phi, ïa la ka bynta shi sngi shi sngi, kum mynba la don u 'langïap.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te la shoh ïa ki rangbah jong ki khun Israel, ïa kiba la buh ki sordar u Pharaoh halor jong ki, bad la kylli ïa ki ruh, “Na ka balei ba phim shym la pyndep noh ïa la ka bynta da kaba thaw maw-it mynhynnin bad mynta de, kumba mynno mynno ruh?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah ki khun Israel ki la ïawan kyrpad ha u Pharaoh, ki da ong, “Na ka balei me leh kumne bad la ki shakri?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kim ai shuh ïa u 'langïap ïa ki shakri jong me, bad la ong ha ngi, ‘To thaw maw-it:’ te ha khmih, la shoh ïa ki shakri jong me; hynrei, ka palat ka long ka jong ki briew jong me hi.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, u la ong, “Phi jaipdeh, phi jaipdeh keiñ: namar kata, phi ong, ‘To shah ngin ïaleit kñia ainguh ïa U Trai.’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Namar kata, khie leit mynta, bad trei; naba yn ym ai 'langïap shuh ha phi, pynban, phin ai ïa kajuh ka jingkheiñ ki maw-it.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki rangbah ki khun Israel ki la ïohi ba ki la long ha ka jingjynjar, haba la ong, “Phin ym pynduna satia ïa ki maw-it, kiba long ka bynta jong phi ha la ka sngi ka sngi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la ïashem bad u Moses bad u Aaron, kiba la ïeng ha ka lynti, haba ki la ïawan mih noh na u Pharaoh:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ki la ong ha ki, “To U Trai un khmih ha phi, bad un bishar de; namar phi la pynlong ïa ngi ban iwkhong ha khmat u Pharaoh, bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u, ba phi la ai ka waitlam ha ka kti jong ki ban pynïap ïa ngi.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Moses u la leit phai pat sha U Trai, bad u la ong, “A Trai, na ka balei ba me la pynsniew ïa une u paidbah? balei ba me la phah ïa nga?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar naduh ba nga la wan ban kren ha u Pharaoh ha ka kyrteng jong me, u la pynsniew ïa une u paidbah; bad mem shym la pyllait noh satia ïa la ki briew.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Mynta men ïohi kaei ba ngan sa leh ïa u Pharaoh: naba da ka kti badonbor un pyllait noh ïa ki, bad da ka kti badonbor un pynmih noh ïa ki na ka ri jong u.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U Blei u la kren ha u Moses, bad U la ong ha u, “Ma nga, nga long U Jehobah:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ha u Abraham, ha u Isaak, bad ha u Jakob, nga la mihpaw da ka kyrteng U Blei U Badonbor Baroh, hynrei, da ka kyrteng jong nga ‘JEHOBAH’ kim shym la ithuh ïa nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga la pynskhem ruh ïa ka jutang jong nga bad ki, ïa ka ban ai ha ki, ïa ka ri Kanaan, ïa ka ri ki jingleit jong ki keiñ ha kaba ki la long ki nongwei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ruh ïa ka jingud ki khun Israel, ïa kiba ki Ijipt ki bat ha ka jinglongmraw; bad nga la kynmaw ïa la ka jutang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar kata, to ong ha ki khun Israel, ‘Nga long ma nga U Jehobah, bad ngan wallam noh ïa phi napoh ka jingpynshitom ki Ijipt, bad ngan pyllait noh ïa phi na ka jingpynlong mraw jong ki, bad ngan siewspah ïa phi da ka ksang'ti ba la kner, bad da ki jingbishar bakhraw:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ngan shim ruh ïa phi ban long ki briew ïa nga, ma nga ruh, ngan long U Blei ïa phi: bad phin sa tip ba nga, nga long U Jehobah U Blei jong phi, uba wallam noh ïa phi napoh ki jingpynshitom ki Ijipt.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngan wallam ruh ïa phi sha kata ka ri, shaphang kaba nga la smai ban ai ïa ka ha u Abraham, ha u Isaak, bad ha u Jakob ruh; te ngan ai ïa ka, ban long ka bynta jong phi: ma nga, nga long U Jehobah.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la kren kumta ha ki khun Israel: hynrei, ki, kim shym la shahshkor ïa u Moses namar kata ka jingpisa mynsiem bad namar kata ka jingpynlong mraw bashitom eh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “To leit hapoh, to kren ha u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt, ba un pyllait noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri jong u.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Moses u la kren ha khmat U Trai, u da ong, “Ha khmih, ki khun Israel kim shym la shahshkor ïa nga; kumno te un sngap u Pharaoh ïa nga uba khlem otsher ki rmiang shyntur?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron, bad ha ki U la ai hukum ïa ki khun Israel, bad ïa u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt, ïa ka ban wallam noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine te ki rangbah ha ki ïing ki kpa jong ki: ki khun shynrang u Reuben u khun nyngkong jong u Israel: u Hanokh, bad u Pallu, u Hesron, bad u Karmi: kine ki long ki ïing jong u Reuben.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Simeon ruh: u Jemuel, bad u Jamin, bad u Ohad, bad u Jakhin, bad u Sohar ruh, bad u Shaul u khun ka kynja Kanaan: kine ki ïing jong u Simeon.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kine ruh ki kyrteng ki khun shynrang u Lebi ha ka jinghiar pateng jong ki: u Gershon, bad u Kohath, bad u Merari: te ki snem ka rta u Lebi ki la long shispah laiphew hynñiew snem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Gershon: u Libni, bad u Shimi, ha ki ïing jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kine ki khun shynrang u Kohath: u Amram, bad u Ishar, bad u Hebron ruh, bad u Ussiel; te ki snem ka rta u Kohath ki la long shispah laiphew lai snem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Merari de: u Mahli bad u Mushi; kine ki long ki ïing jong u Lebi ha ki jinghiar pateng jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Amram u la shim ïa ka Jokhebed ka ñiakha jong u ban long ka tnga jong u; ha u ka la kha ruh ïa u Aaron bad ïa u Moses: te ki snem ka rta u Amram ki la long shispah laiphew hynñiew snem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun shynrang u Ishar: u Korah, bad u Nepheg, bad u Sikhri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki khun shynrang u Ussiel: u Mishael, bad u Elsaphan, bad u Sithri.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Aaron u la shim ïa ka Elisheba ka khun u Amminadab, ka para jong u Naashon ban long ka tnga ïa u; ha u te ka la kha ïa u Nadab, bad ïa u Abihu, ïa u Eleasar, bad ïa u Ithamar.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kine ki khun u Korah de: u Assir, u Elkanah ruh, bad u Abiasaph; kine ki ïing jong u Korah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Eleasar u khun u Aaron u la shim ïa kawei na ki khun kynthei jong u Putiel ban long ka tnga jong u; ha u te ka la kha ïa u Phinehas. Kine ki long ki rangbah jong ki kpa jong ki Lebi, katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kine ki long uta u Aaron bad uta u Moses, ha kiba U Trai u la ong, “To wallam noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt katba kum ki paid jong ki.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kine, ki long kita kiba la kren ha u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt, ïa ka ban wallam noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt: kine keiñ, ki long uta u Moses bad uta u Aaron.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ka la jia te ha kata ka sngi ha kaba U Trai u la kren ha u Moses ha ka ri Ijipt,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ba U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong, “Nga long ma nga U Trai: to men kren ha u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt ïa baroh kaba nga ong ha me.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Moses u la ïathuh ha khmat U Trai, “Ha khmih, nga uba khlem otsher ki rmiang shyntur, kumno te un shahshkor u Pharaoh ïa nga?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ha khmih, nga la pynlong blei ïa me ha u Pharaoh: bad u Aaron u hynmen jong me un sa long u nongïathuhlypa jong me.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> To men kren baroh ïa kaba nga hukum ïa me: bad u Aaron u hynmen jong me un kren ha u Pharaoh, ba un phah noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ngan pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, bad ngan pynbun ïa ki dak khyllah bad ïa ki jingphylla jong nga ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Pharaoh un ym shahshkor ïa phi, ba ngan ïoh buh ïa la ka kti halor ka ri Ijipt, bad ba ngan pynmih noh de ïa la ki paidbah, kiba ki briew jong nga, ki khun Israel keiñ, na ka ri Ijipt da ki jingbishar bakhraw.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki Ijipt kin sa tip ba nga long ma nga U Trai, haba nga la kner ïa la ka kti halor ka ri Ijipt, bad ba nga la pynmih noh ïa ki khun Israel napdeng jong ki.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la leh kumta kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa ki, kumta keiñ ki la leh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Moses u la don phraphew snem ka rta, bad u Aaron phraphew lai snem ka rta mynba ki la kren ha u Pharaoh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron, u da ong,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Haba u Pharaoh un kren ha phi da kaba ong, ‘To pyni ïa ka kam phylla na phi:’ te men ong ha u Aaron, ‘To shim ïa la u diengduh, to bred ruh ha khmat u Pharaoh, ba un sa kylla bseiñ.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïaleit hapoh ha u Pharaoh, bad ki la leh kumta, kumba U Trai u la lah hukum: bad u Aaron u la bred ïa la u diengduh ha khmat u Pharaoh bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u, te u la kylla bseiñ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pharaoh ruh u la khot ïa ki riewstad, bad ïa ki nongleh byrtong: te ki nongleh byrtong ka ri Ijipt, ki hi ruh ki la leh kumjuh da ki jingleh myntor jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba ki la bred uwei uwei baroh ïa la u diengduh, te ki ruh ki la kylla bseiñ: hynrei, u diengduh u Aaron u la nguid noh ïa ki diengduh jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, bad kumta, um shym shahshkor ïa ki; kumba U Trai u la lah ong.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ka dohnud u Pharaoh ka la eh, um treh ban pyllait noh ïa u paidbah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> To men leit ha u Pharaoh la dang step; ha khmih, u wan mih noh shabar sha kata ka um; te men ïeng harud kata ka wah hamar kaba u wan; to shim ruh ha la ka kti ïa uta u diengduh uba la kylla bseiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad men ong ruh ha u, ‘U Trai, U Blei jong ki Hebru, u la phah ïa nga ha me, u da ong, “To da pyllait noh ïa ki briew jong nga, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa nga ha ri khlaw: te ha khmih, haduh mynta mem shahshkor satia.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumne u ong U Trai, “Da kane men sa tip ba ma nga, nga long U Trai: ha khmih, nga ngan shoh da une u diengduh uba ha ka kti jong nga halor kita ki wah, te kin sa kylla snam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki dohkha ruh kiba ha kata ka wah kin ïap noh, bad kata ka wah kan iwtung; bad ki Ijipt kin isih ban dih na ka um jong kata ka wah.” ’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To ong ha u Aaron, ‘To shim ïa u diengduh jong me, to kner ruh ïa la ka kti halor ki um ka ri Ijipt, halor ki wah bah jong ki, halor ki wah duid jong ki ruh, bad halor ki pukri jong ki, bad halor ki pung um jong ki baroh de, ba kin kylla snam; bad ba kin long snam ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei, ha ki diang dieng bad ha ki diang maw ruh.’ ”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la leh kumta, kumba U Trai u la hukum; bad u la rah ïa uta u diengduh, bad u la shoh ruh ïa kita ki um kiba ha kata ka wah ha khmat u Pharaoh, bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u; te ïa kita ki um baroh kiba ha kata ka wah la pynkylla snam.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad kita ki dohkha kiba ha kata ka wah ki la ïap noh; bad kata ka wah ka la iwtung, te ki Ijipt kim lah ban dih shuh na ka um jong kata ka wah; te la don ka snam ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad kita ki nongleh byrtong ka ri Ijipt ki la leh kumjuh da ki jingleh myntor jong ki: te ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh la pyneh, bad um shym la shahshkor ïa ki; kumba U Trai u la lah ong.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u Pharaoh u la phai u la leit sha la ïing, bad um shym la buh ïa kane ruh ha ka dohnud jong u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki Ijipt baroh te ki la ïatih baroh sawdong ïa kata ka wah ba kin ïoh ka um ban dih; naba kim lah dih shuh na ka um jong kata ka wah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te la pyndep hynñiew sngi, naduh ba U Trai u la lah shoh ïa kata ka wah."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To leit ha u Pharaoh, to ong ruh ha u, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, “To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh ïashakri ïa nga.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te lada mem treh ban pyllait noh ïa ki, ha khmih, ngan shoh ïa ki phang jong me baroh da ki jakoid:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad kata ka wah kan boi da ki jakoid, ki ban sa kiew, kin ïarung ruh shapoh ïing jong me, bad sha ka kamra thiah jong me, bad halor ka jingthiah jong me, bad shapoh ïing ki shakri jong me, bad halor ki briew jong me de, bad sha ki jaka shet kpu jong me, bad sha ki kpu im jong me ruh;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> kita ki jakoid te kin ïarynsied halor jong me, bad halor ki briew jong me, bad halor ki shakri jong me baroh.” ’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, “To ong ha u Aaron, ‘To kner ïa la ka kti bad la u diengduh halor kita ki wah bah, bad halor kita ki wah duid, bad halor kita ki pung de, bad to pynmih ïa ki jakoid halor ka ri Ijipt.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Aaron u la kner ïa la ka kti halor kita ki um ka Ijipt; bad ki jakoid ki la ïamih, bad ki la ïatyllup ïa ka ri Ijipt.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kita ki nongleh byrtong ruh ki la leh kumjuh da ki jingleh myntor jong ki, bad ki la ïa-pynmih ïa ki jakoid halor ka ri Ijipt.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pharaoh u la khot ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron, bad u la ong, “To kyrpad ïa U Trai ba un shim noh ïa kine ki jakoid na nga, bad na ki briew jong nga; te ngan sa pyllait noh ïa uta u paidbah, ba kin ïoh kñia ha U Trai.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong ha u Pharaoh, “To ïoh kane ka burom halor jong nga: hamar kano ka por ba ngan kyrpad na ka bynta jong me, bad na ka bynta ki shakri jong me, bad na ka bynta ki briew jong me, ïa ka ban pynduh noh ïa kine ki jakoid na me hi, bad na ki ïing jong me ruh, ba kin long sa tang ha kata ka wah?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U te u la ong, “Lashai.” Bad u la ong, “To kan long katba kum ka ktien jong me: ba men ïoh tip ba ym don uno uno ruh uba kum U Trai U Blei jong ngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad kita ki jakoid kin ïaleit noh na me, bad na ki ïing jong me, bad na ki shakri jong me, bad na ki briew jong me; kin long sa tang ha kata ka wah.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïaleit noh na khmat u Pharaoh: bad u Moses u la kyrpad eh ha U Trai namar kita ki jakoid ïa kiba u la lah wallam halor u Pharaoh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad U Trai u la leh katba kum ka ktien u Moses; kita ki jakoid te ki la ïap noh na ki ïing, na ki shnong ruh, bad na ki lyngkha de.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki la ïa-pynlang ïa ki ha ki jaka jaka: kumta, kata ka ri ka la iwtung.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, mynba u Pharaoh u la ïohi ba la ïohlait, u la pyneh ïa la ka dohnud, bad um shym la shahshkor ïa ki; kumba U Trai u la lah ong.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To ong ha u Aaron, ‘To kner noh ïa la u diengduh, bad to shoh ïa ka 'dewmet jong kane ka ri ba kan kylla jynreiñ ha ka ri Ijipt kylleng baroh.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la leh kumta; bad u Aaron u la rah ïa la ka kti bad la uta u diengduh, bad u la shoh ïa ka 'dewmet jong ka khyndew, te ka la kylla jynreiñ ha u briew bad ha u mrad; ka 'dewmet jong ka ri baroh keiñ ka la kylla jynreiñ ha ka ri Ijipt kylleng baroh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad kita ki nongleh byrtong ruh, ki la leh kumta, ban pynmih jynreiñ da ki jingleh myntor jong ki, hynrei, kim lah: kumta, la don kita ki jynreiñ ha u briew, bad ha u mrad.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki nongleh byrtong ki la ong ha u Pharaoh, “Kane ka long ka shynriah'ti ka jong U Blei:” te pynban, la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, bad um shym la shahshkor ïa ki; kumba U Trai u la lah ong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To khie la dang step lashai, to ïeng ruh ha khmat u Pharaoh; ha khmih, u wan mih sha kata ka um; to ong ruh ha u, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai, “To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa nga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, lada men ym pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ha khmih, ngan phah ïa ki bun jaid ki skain ha me, bad ha ki shakri jong me, bad ha ki briew jong me ruh, bad hapoh ki ïing jong me; bad ki ïing ki Ijipt kin dap da ki bun jaid ki skain, bad kata ka khyndew ruh ha kaba ki don.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ngan pynkyrpang ha kata ka sngi ïa ka ri Goshen, ha kaba ki ïashong u paidbah jong nga, ba kita ki bun jaid ki skain kin ym don hangta; khnang ba men ïoh tip ba nga long U Trai hapdeng ka pyrthei.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ngan buh ïa ka jingïapher hapdeng ki briew jong nga bad ki jong me: te lashai keiñ kan long kane ka dak.” ’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Trai u la leh kumta; bad la boi bun jaid ki skain ba pynshitom eh ha ïing u Pharaoh, bad ha ki ïing ki shakri jong u; bad ha ka ri Ijipt baroh ïa ka ri te la pynsniew noh khoit da kita ki bun jaid ki skain.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la khot ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron, bad u la ong, “To khie leit phi, to kñia ïa U Blei jong phi ha kane ka ri.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Moses te u la ong, “Kam bit ban leh kumta; namar ngin kñia ïa ka jingisih ki Ijipt ha U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi: ha khmih, lada ngin ïakñia ïa ka jingisih ki Ijipt ha khmat jong ki, hato kin ym lynthem ïa ngi?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Lai sngi lynti ngin ïaleit sha kata ka ri khlaw, ïa ka ban kñia ha U Trai U Blei jong ngi, katba un hukum ïa ngi.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la ong, “Ngan shah ba phin ïaleit, ba phin kñia ha U Trai U Blei jong phi ha kata ka ri khlaw; hynrei, tang ba phin ym leit jngai eh: to duwai na ka bynta jong nga.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Moses u la ong, “Ha khmih, ngan leit mih noh na me, bad ngan kyrpad ruh ha U Trai ba kine ki bun jaid ki skain kin kynriah noh lashai na u Pharaoh, bad na ki shakri jong u, bad na ki briew jong u ruh: hynrei, wat ai ba u Pharaoh un shukor shuh da kaba un ym pyllait noh ïa u paidbah ba kin ïoh kñia ha U Trai.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Haba u Moses u la mih noh na u Pharaoh, u la kyrpad ha U Trai.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad U Trai u la leh kat kum ka ktien u Moses, bad u la pynkynriah noh ïa kita ki bun jaid ki skain na u Pharaoh, na ki shakri jong u, bad na ki briew jong u ruh; ym shym sah shuh iwei ruh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la pyneh ïa la ka dohnud ha kane ruh, bad um shym la pyllait noh ïa uta u paidbah."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To leit ha u Pharaoh, to ïathuh ruh ha u, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai U Blei ki Hebru: “To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa nga.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar lada mem kohnguh ban pyllait noh ïa ki, bad me shu dang bat ïa ki,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ha khmih, ka kti U Trai kan long halor ki jingri jong me kiba ha ka lyngkha, halor ki kulai, halor ki kadda, halor ki ut, halor ki masi de, bad halor ki langbrot ruh: kan wan ka jingïapkhlam ki mrad kaba jur eh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Trai ruh un pynïapher ïa ki jingri jong ki Israel bad ki jingri ka ri Ijipt; ba kan ym ïap kaei kaei ruh em kaba dei ka jong ki khun Israel.” ’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Trai u la buh ïa ka Ïa ruh, u da ong, “Lashai U Trai un sa leh ïa kane ha kane ka ri.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Trai u la leh ruh ïa kata ha kaba lashai, bad ki jingri baroh jong ka ri Ijipt ki la ïap noh: hynrei, na ki jingri jong ki khun Israel kawei ruh kam shym la ïap.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la phah tohkit, te ha khmih, na ki jingri ki khun Israel kawei ruh kam shym ïap noh. Te pynban, ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh la pyneh, bad um shym la pyllait noh ïa uta u paidbah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron, “To shim shi kham da ka dpei na ka pajwa, bad ai ha u Moses un synreit ïa ka sha bneng ha khmat u Pharaoh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kan sa man pum pum ha ka ri Ijipt baroh, bad kan long ki tohjaw ba-mih ksuit ruh ha u briew bad ha u mrad, kylleng ka ri Ijipt baroh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la shim ïa ka dpei na kata ka pajwa, bad ki la ïeng ha khmat u Pharaoh; bad u Moses u la synreit ïa ka sha bneng; te ki la man tohjaw ba-mih ksuit ha u briew bad ha u mrad.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kita ki nongleh byrtong te kim lah ïeng ha khmat u Moses namar kita ki tohjaw; namar kata, ki tohjaw ba-mih ksuit ki la don ha kita ki nongleh byrtong, bad ha ki Ijipt baroh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Trai u la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, bad um shym shahshkor ïa ki, kumba U Trai u la lah kren ha u Moses.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To khie la dang step, bad to ïeng ha khmat u Pharaoh, bad to ong ha u, ‘Kumne u ong U Trai U Blei jong ki Hebru, “To pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa nga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Naba ha kane ka por, ngan sa phah ïa ki jingpynshitom jong nga baroh halor ka dohnud jong me, bad halor ki shakri jong me, bad halor ki briew jong me; khnang ba men ïoh tip ba ym don uba kat nga ha ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba lada nga la lah kner ïa la ka kti, bad shoh ïa me bad ïa ki briew jong me da ka jingïapthem, te ïa me la lah ot noh na ka pyrthei;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> hynrei, shisha na ka bynta kane hi nga la pynïeng ïa me, ïa ka ban pyni ha me ïa ka bor jong nga, bad ïa ka ban pynbna ïa ka kyrteng jong nga de ha ka pyrthei baroh kawei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te me dang pynmeng ïa lade pynban halor u paidbah jong nga, ba mem pyllait noh ïa ki?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha khmih, lashai hamar kane ka por ngan pynhap da u phria uba jur eh, kat uta ym ju don ha ka ri Ijipt naduh ba ka dang long haduh mynta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata te, to phah ïalum mynta ïa ki jingri jong me bad ïa baroh kat kiba me don ha ka lyngkha; u briew bad u mrad baroh kat ki ban shem ha ka lyngkha, bad ki ban ym wallam ha ïing, uta u phria un hap keiñ halor jong ki, bad kin ïap noh.” ’ ”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uta na ki shakri u Pharaoh uba la sheptieng ïa ka ktien U Trai u la pynphet ïa la ki shakri bad ïa la ki jingri shapoh ki ïing;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hynrei, uta u bym shym la suidñiew ïa ka ktien U Trai u la iehnoh ïa la ki shakri bad ïa la ki jingri ha ka lyngkha.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To kner ïa la ka kti sha bneng, ba un hap u phria ha ka ri Ijipt baroh, halor u briew, bad halor ki mrad, bad halor ki jhur ka lyngkha baroh, kylleng ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u Moses u la kner ïa la u diengduh sha bneng: bad U Trai u la phah da ki pyrthat bad da u phria, bad ka ding ruh ka la nang pur halor ka khyndew; bad U Trai u la pynhap ïa u phria halor ka ri Ijipt.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, la don u phria, bad ka ding ba la ïakhleh lem bad uta u phria bapynshitom eh, ym shym la don kat uta ha ka ri Ijipt baroh naduh ba ka la man jaid bynriew.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad uta u phria u la shoh baroh kylleng ka ri Ijipt ïa baroh kat kiba ha ka lyngkha, ïa u briew ruh bad ïa u mrad; bad uta u phria u la shoh ruh ïa ki jhur ka lyngkha baroh, u la pynkheiñ ruh ïa u dieng baroh jong ka lyngkha.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Tang ha ka ri Goshen, ha kaba la shong ki khun Israel, ym shym la don phria.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la phah khot ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ha kane shi sien nga la leh pop: U Trai u long u bahok, ma nga te bad ki briew jong nga ngi long ki bymman.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To kyrpad ïa U Trai; naba katne ki la biang ki pyrthat U Blei bad u phria; te ngan pyllait noh ïa phi, bad phin ym shong shuh.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha u, “Haba nga dang shu mih noh na kane ka nongbah, ngan sa kner ïa la ki kti sha U Trai; te uta u pyrthat un duh, bad uta u phria ruh un ym hap shuh; khnang ba men ïoh tip ba ka pyrthei ka long ka jong U Trai.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, shaphang jong me bad ki shakri jong me, nga tip ba phim pat sheptieng ïa U Trai U Blei.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te la shoh ïa u 'saihon bad ïa u Kew Barli: naba uta u Kew Barli u dang long ha ka kop, bad uta u 'saihon u dang sei soh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei, ïa u Kew bad ïa u Kew rie ym shym la shoh: naba kim pat mih.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Moses u la mih noh na u Pharaoh shabar kata ka nongbah, bad u la kner ïa la ki kti sha U Trai: te uta u pyrthat bad uta u phria de ki la jah noh, bad ym shym la pynhap shuh ïa u slap ha ka khyndew.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te haba u Pharaoh u la ïohi ba uta u slap bad uta u phria bad uta u pyrthat ruh ki la jah noh, u la nang leh pop shuh shuh, bad u la pyneh ïa la ka dohnud ruh: ma u bad ki shakri jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kumta, ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh la pyneh, bad um shym la pyllait noh ïa ki khun Israel; kumba U Trai u la lah kren ha u Moses."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To leit shapoh ha u Pharaoh: namar nga la pyneh ïa ka dohnud jong u, bad ïa ka dohnud ki shakri jong u, ba ngan ïoh pyni ïa kine ki dak phylla jong nga ha khmat jong u:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ba me ruh men pynsngew ha la ki khun, bad ha u khun jong u khun jong me, ïa kiei kiei kat kiba nga la leh ha ka ri Ijipt, bad ïa ki dak phylla jong nga ïa kiba nga la trei hapdeng jong ki; khnang ba phin ïoh tip ba ma nga, nga long U Trai.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïawan ha u Pharaoh, bad ki la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong U Trai U Blei jong ki Hebru, ‘Slem katno ba men ym kohnguh ban pynrit ïa lade ha khmat jong nga? to pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar lada men ym treh ban pyllait noh ïa u paidbah jong nga, ha khmih, lashai ngan sa wallam ïa ki puit sha ki phang jong me:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad kin sa ïatyllup noh lin ïa ka khyndew, kat ban ym ïohi ïa ka khyndew: kin sa bam lut ruh ïa kaba la lait, kaba dang sah ha phi na uta u phria, bad kin sa bam lut ïa u dieng baroh uba mih ha phi ha ka lyngkha:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad kin sa pyndap ïa ki ïing jong me, bad ïa ki ïing ki shakri jong me baroh, bad ïa ki ïing ki Ijipt baroh; kat kita lymne ki kpa jong me lymne ki kpa ki kpa jong me, kim shym la ïohi, naduh kata ka sngi ba ki la mih ha ka pyrthei haduh kane ka sngi.’ ” Te haba u la phai, u la mih noh na u Pharaoh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki shakri u Pharaoh ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Slem katno une u briew un long ka jingriam ïa ngi? To pyllait noh ïa kita ki briew, ba kin ïoh shakri ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki: balei mem pat tip ba la pynjot ïa ka ri Ijipt?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la wallam pat ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron ha u Pharaoh: bad u la ong ha ki, “To khie noh, to shakri ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi: hynrei, kino ki ban leit?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la ïathuh, “Ngin ïaleit bad ki samla bad ki tymmen jong ngi, lem bad ki khun jong ngi ruh shynrang bad kynthei, lem bad ki langbrot bad ki masi jong ngi ruh de ngin leit; naba ngi donkam ban rakhe Ka Jingkhawai Niam ïa U Trai.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Ai ba U Trai un long kumta lem bad phi, kumjuh kumba ngan pyllait noh ïa phi, lem bad ki khunlung jong phi: ha khmih, phi don ka jingpyrkhat basniew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ym kumta: to khie leit tang ma phi kiba rangbah, bad to shakri ïa U Trai; naba ïa kata phi la lah kwah.” Te kumta, la beh noh ïa ki na khmat u Pharaoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Moses, “To kner ïa la ka kti halor ka ri Ijipt ïa ka ban pynmih ïa ki puit, ba kin ïoh kiew halor ka ri Ijipt, bad ba kin ïoh bam duh ruh ïa u jhur jong kane ka ri baroh, ïa kaba sah baroh na kaba shoh u phria.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses u la kner ïa la u diengduh halor ka ri Ijipt, bad U Trai u la pynmih ïa ka lyer na mihngi halor ka khyndew ha kata baroh shi sngi, bad baroh shi miet; ynda la mynstep te, ka lyer na mihngi ka la wallam ïa ki puit.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kita ki puit te ki la ïakiew halor ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei, bad ki la ïashong ruh ha ki phang baroh jong ka ri Ijipt: kiba jynjar eh; mynshuwa kita, ym pat ju don ki puit kat kita, lymne hadien jong ki yn ym long shuh kat kita.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba ki la ïatyllup noh lin ïa ka khyndew baroh, katba la pyndum ïa kata ka ri ruh; bad ki la ïabam lut ïa u jhur ka khyndew baroh, bad ïa ki soh na ki dieng baroh kiba la sah na kata kaba shoh phria: te ym shym la sah shuh ei ei ruh ka bajyrngam, ha ki dieng lane ha ki jhur ha ka lyngkha, ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Pharaoh u la khot ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron da kaba kyrkieh; bad u la ong, “Nga la leh pop ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, bad ïa phi ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mynta te, nga kyrpad ïa me, to map ïa ka pop jong nga sa tang kane shi sien hi, bad to kyrpad ruh ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, ba un shim noh na nga sa tang kane ka jingpynïap.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda u la leit noh na u Pharaoh, u la kyrpad ha U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynphai da ka lyer bah na sepngi, kaba la shim noh ïa kita ki puit, bad la bred ïa ki ruh sha ka Duriaw Basaw; ym sah shuh iwei i puit ruh ha ki phang baroh ka ri Ijipt.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, ba kumta un ym pyllait noh ïa ki khun Israel.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To rah ïa la ka kti sha bneng, ba ka jingdum kan long halor ka ri Ijipt, ka jingdum ruh kaba da lah ban tba.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Moses u la rah ïa la ka kti sha bneng; te ka la long ka jingdum tliw tliw lai sngi ha ka ri Ijipt baroh;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> kim ïaïohi shuh paralok hi, lymne uno uno ruh um shym la ïeng na la ka jaka lai sngi: hynrei, ha ki khun Israel baroh la don ka jingshai ha ki jaka shong jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Pharaoh te u la khot ïa u Moses, bad u la ong ruh, “To khie leit phi, to shakri ïa U Trai; kin sah sa tang ki langbrot bad ki masi jong phi: to ai ba ki khynnah jong phi ruh kin leit lem bad phi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Moses u la ong, “Men ai ruh ha ngi ïa ki jingkñia bad ïa ki jingainguh thang, ba ngin ïoh kñia ainguh ha U Trai U Blei jong ngi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki jingri jong ngi ruh kin ïaleit lem bad ngi; yn ym iehnoh ïa kawei ka khnap hadien; naba na kita keiñ ngin ïashim ban ïamane ïa U Trai U Blei jong ngi; te ngim tip da ei ngi dei ban mane ïa U Trai, katba ngim pat poi hangta.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, te um treh ban pyllait noh ïa ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Pharaoh u la ong ha u, “Khie leit noh na nga, to sumar ïa lade, ba phin ym ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga shuh; naba ha kata ka sngi ba men ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga, men ïap.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Moses te u la ong, “Me la kren kaba dei; ngan ym ïohi shuh ïa ka khmat jong me.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ngan da wallam shuh sa kawei ka jingpynïapthem halor u Pharaoh, bad halor ka ri Ijipt; hadien kata te, un sa pyllait noh ïa phi nangne: haba un da pyllait noh ïa phi, shisha un da beh noh ïa phi nangne baroh phar.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> To kren mynta ha kaba ïohsngew u paidbah, bad to ai ba u briew baroh un pan na la u paramarjan, bad ka kynthei baroh na la ka paramarjan ïa ki jingdeng rupa bad ïa ki jingdeng ksiar.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Trai ruh u la ai ha uta u paidbah ka jingsngewbha ha khmat ki Ijipt. U Moses ruh u la long u briew bakhraw eh ha ka ri Ijipt, ha khmat ki shakri u Pharaoh, bad ha khmat ki briew baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Moses u la ong ruh, “Kumne u la ong U Trai, ‘Hamar shiteng synñia ngan leit mih noh shabar hapdeng ka ri Ijipt;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> te u khun nyngkong baroh uba ha ka ri Ijipt un sa ïap noh, naduh u khun nyngkong u Pharaoh uba shong halor la ka khet, haduh u khun nyngkong jong ka mraw batrei ha u mawtylliat; bad ki khun nyngkong jong ki mrad baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kan sa long te ka jinglynñiar bakhraw ha ka ri Ijipt baroh kawei, kat kata ym pat ju don, lymne kat kata ruh yn ym long shuh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, ïa uwei ruh na ki khun Israel, u ksew un ym pynkhih ïa la u thylliej, ïa u briew lane ïa u mrad: khnang ba phin ïoh tip ba U Trai u buh ka jingïapher hapdeng ki Ijipt bad ki Israel.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kine ki shakri jong me baroh kin ïawan hiar ha nga, bad kin ïanguh ïa nga, kin da ïa-ong, ‘To leit mih noh phi, bad une u paidbah baroh uba bud ïa me:’ hadien kata te, ngan sa mih noh.” Te u la leit mih noh na u Pharaoh ha ka jingbitar bakhraw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Moses, “U Pharaoh un ym shahshkor ïa phi: ba ki dak khyllah jong nga kin nang bun ha ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Moses ruh bad u Aaron ki la leh ïa kine ki dak khyllah baroh ha khmat u Pharaoh: te U Trai u la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, ba kumta un ym pyllait noh ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri jong u."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses bad ha u Aaron ha ka ri Ijipt, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Une u bnai un long ha phi u banyngkong na ki bnai: un long ïa phi u bnai nyngkong jong ka snem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To kren ha u paidbah Israel baroh, da ong, ‘Ha ka bashiphew sngi jong une u bnai, to shim ha lade man la u briew ïa u khun langbrot, katba kum ka ïing ki kpa jong ki, uwei uwei u khun langbrot khmat ka ïing keiñ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te lada shi ïing ka duna briew ïa uwei u khun langbrot, to ai ba uta bad la u paramarjan ïing kin sa ïashim ïa u katba don ka jingkheiñ ki briew; uwei uwei baroh katba u ju bam phin kheiñ ïa uta u khun langbrot.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Uta u khun langbrot jong phi un long uba janai, u shynrang uba shi snem: phin sa shim ïa u na ki jong ki langbrot, lane na ki jong ki blang;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> to ri ïa u ruh haduh khatsaw sngi jong une u bnai: bad ka jingïalang jong u paidbah Israel baroh kin ïa-pynïap ïa u ha kaba la janmiet.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kin shim ruh na ka snam, bad kin kyllan ha ki baroh ar liang ka shawkad bad ha khlieh jingkhang jong kita ki ïing, ha kiba kin sa ïabam ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kin ïabam ruh ïa ka doh ha kata ka miet, ïa kaba la syang ha ka ding, bad ïa ki kpu khlem thiat; lem bad ki jhur bakthang kin ïabam ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Phi wat ïabam doh im ïa ka, lymne ba la shet um, hynrei, ba la syang ha ka ding; ïa ka khlieh jong u lem bad ki kjat bad ki snier jong u ruh de.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Phin ym pynsah ei ei ruh na u haduh mynstep; te ïa kata kaba dang sah haduh mynstep, to thang noh ha ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kumne phin ïabam ïa u; ba la panpoh ïa la ki syngkai, la ki juti ha la ki sla'jat, bad la ki diengduh ruh ha la ki kti: bad phin ïabam ruh ïa u da kaba kyrkieh: ka long ka jinglait jong U Trai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba ngan ïaid lyngba ka ri Ijipt ha kane ka miet, bad ngan shoh ïap ïa u khun nyngkong baroh kiba ha ka ri Ijipt, u jong u briew bad u jong u mrad ruh; bad pyrshah ïa ki blei ka ri Ijipt ngan pynlong ïa ka jingbishar: ma nga, nga long U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kata ka snam te kan sa long ka dak ïa phi ha ki ïing ha kiba phi don: bad haba nga ïohi ïa kata ka snam, ngan ïaid palat ïa phi, bad kata ka jingpynïap kan ym long ïa ka ban pynjot ïa phi, haba nga shoh ïap ïa ka ri Ijipt.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “ ‘Kane ka sngi ruh kan long ïa phi ka jingpynkynmaw, bad phin rakhe ruh ïa ka kum Ka Jingkhawai Niam ïa U Trai: ha ki pateng la pateng jong phi phin rakhe ïa ka keiñ kum Ka Jingkhawai Niam da ka hukum kaba ha la ka rta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynriew sngi phin bam ïa u kpu khlem thiat; ha ka sngi nyngkong to bred noh ïa u thiat na ki ïing jong phi: naba uno uno ruh uba bam ïa u kpu ba dei thiat naduh kata ka sngi banyngkong haduh ka sngi ka bahynñiew, ïa kata ka mynsiem yn ot noh na ki Israel.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kata ka sngi banyngkong te kan long ka jingïaseng bakyntang, bad ha kata ka sngi bahynñiew ruh ka jingïaseng bakyntang ïa phi: wat leh ka kam ei ei ruh ha ki, tang ïa kaba u briew baroh u bam, tang ïa kata hi lah ban leh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Phin rakhe te ïa Ka Niam U Kpu Khlem Thiat; namar ha kane ka sngi hi, ngan ïalam noh ïa ki paidbah jong phi na ka ri Ijipt: namar kata, phin rakhe ïa kane ka sngi ha ki pateng la pateng jong phi da ka hukum ha la ka rta.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha u bnai banyngkong, ha ka bakhatsaw sngi jong uta u bnai ha kaba la janmiet, phin ïabam ïa u kpu khlem thiat, haduh ka ba-arphew wei jong uta u bnai la janmiet.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynñiew sngi wat ai ba yn shem ïa u thiat ha ki ïing jong phi: naba uno uno ruh uba bam ïa u kpu ba dei thiat, ïa kata ka mynsiem yn ot noh na ka jingïalang ki khun Israel, la u long u nongwei, ne u trai-shnong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Phin ym bam ei ei ruh ba la dei thiat; ha ki jaka shong jong phi baroh phin bam da u kpu khlem thiat.’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u Moses u la khot ïa ki tymmen basan baroh ki Israel, bad u la ong ha ki, “To kem, shim ruh ïa u khun langbrot sha lade katba kum ki ïing ki ïing jong phi, bad to pynïap ïa ka jinglait.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad to shim ruh shi song u Hyssop, bad haba phi la wieh ïa u ha ka snam kaba ha ka pliang, to kyllan ïa ka khlieh jingkhang bad ïa baroh ar liang ki shawkad da kata ka snam kaba ha kata ka pliang; te mano mano ruh na phi wat mih shabar ka jingkhang la ka jong ka ïing haduh mynstep.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Naba U Trai un sa ïaid lyngba ïa ka ban shoh ïap ïa ki Ijipt; te haba u ïohi ïa kata ka snam ha khlieh jingkhang, bad ha baroh ar liang ki shawkad, U Trai un ïaid palat ïa kata ka jingkhang, bad un ym shah ïa uta u nongpynjot ban wan hapoh ki ïing jong phi ïa ka ban pynjot.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> To phin sumar ruh ïa kane ban long ka hukum ïa me bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong me ha la ka rta.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ynda phi la poi sha kata ka ri ïa kaba U Trai un sa ai ha phi, kumba u la kular, phin leh ïa kane ka kam.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te kan jia, haba ki khun jong phi kin ong ha phi, ‘Phi mut aïu da kane ka kam?’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ba phin ïathuh, ‘Ka long ka jingkñia ka jinglait jong U Trai, uba la ïaid palat ïa ki ïing jong ki khun Israel ha ka ri Ijipt, mynba u la shoh ïap ïa ki Ijipt, bad u la pyllait ïa ki ïing jong ngi.’ ” Te uta paidbah u la nguh bad u la mane ruh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit noh bad ki la leh kumta; kumba U Trai u la lah hukum ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron, kumta ki la leh keiñ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ha kaba shiteng synñia, U Trai u la shoh ïap ïa uba kha nyngkong baroh ha ka ri Ijipt; naduh uba la kha nyngkong jong u Pharaoh uba shong halor la ka khet haduh uba la kha nyngkong jong ka mraw kaba ha ka ïing byndi; bad ïa kiba la kha nyngkong jong ki mrad baroh ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Pharaoh u la khie mynmiet, ma u, bad ki shakri jong u baroh, bad ki Ijipt baroh; te la don ka jinglynñiar bakhraw ha ka ri Ijipt; naba ym shym la don ïing khlem da don u baïap.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la khot ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron mynmiet, bad u la ong, “To ïeng, to mih noh napdeng ki briew jong nga, ma phi bad ki khun Israel ruh; to khie leit noh, da shakri ïa U Trai, kumba phi la ong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> To shim ruh ïa la ki langbrot bad ïa la ki masi, kumba phi la ong, bad to khie noh; to kyrkhu ïa nga ruh.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kita ki Ijipt ki la ïakyntu eh ïa u paidbah, ki da phah noh ïa ki na kata ka ri da kaba kyrkieh; naba ki la ïa-ong, “Ngi la ïap lut noh.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Uta u paidbah te u la shim ïa u kpu im jong ki haba ym pat la khleh thiat, ki la ïasong ruh ïa u kpu im jong ki ha la ki jaiñkup ba ki da bah ha la ki tyrpeng.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun Israel ki la leh ruh katba kum ka ktien u Moses; bad ki la ïapan na ki Ijipt ïa ki jingdeng rupa, bad ïa ki jingdeng ksiar, bad ïa ki jaiñkup jaiñsem de;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> te U Trai u la ai ha uta u paidbah ka jingsngewbha ha khmat ki Ijipt, ba kumta ki la ai ha ki katba ki la pan. Kumne ki la ïoh buria pat na ki Ijipt.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit mih noh na Rameses sha Sukkoth da ka kjat, kumba hynriewspah hajar ki rangbah, nalor ki khynnah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad bun ki paidbah bakhleh ruh ki la ïaleit kiew lem bad ki: ki langbrot ruh, bad ki masi, ki jingri shibun eh keiñ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te ki la shet ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat da uta u kpu im ïa uba ki la wallam na ka ri Ijipt, naba ym shym la khleh thiat ïa u; namar la beh noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt, katba kim lah ban sangeh shuh, lymne kim shym la ïoh khreh jingbam ïa lade.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ka jingshong sah ki khun Israel katba ki la ïashong sah ha ka ri Ijipt ka la long sawspah laiphew snem.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ynda la kut kita ki sawspah laiphew snem, ha kata ka sngi hi keiñ, ka la jia ba ki paidbah jong U Trai baroh ki la ïamih noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kane ka long ka miet ïa ka ban rakhe ha U Trai ha kaba la ïalam noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt; kane ka long kata ka miet U Trai, ïa ka ban rakhe da ki khun Israel baroh ha ki pateng la pateng jong ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses bad u Aaron, “Kane ka hukum jong kata Ka Jinglait: u nongwei un ym ïoh bam ïa ka;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> hynrei, u shakri baroh ïa uba la thied da u sbai, ynda me la otsher ïa u, te un sa bam ïa ka.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> U nongwei bad u nongbylla kin ym ïoh bam ïa ka.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Tang ha kawei ka ïing dei ban bam ïa ka; wat rah ei ei ruh em na ka doh shabar kata ka ïing; lymne wat pynkheiñ ïa kawei ka shyieng jong ka.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Baroh ka jingïalang ki khun Israel kin ïarakhe ïa kane.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te haba u nongwei un shong basa lem bad me, bad un da mon ruh ban rakhe ïa Ka Jinglait ha U Trai, to ai ban otsher ïa ki shynrang jong u baroh, ynda kumta te, ai un wan hajan ïa ka ban leh ïa ka; te un long kum uba la kha ha ka ri hi: hynrei, uno uno uba khlem otsher un ym bam ïa ka.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Tang kawei ka hukum kan long ïa uba la kha ha la ka ri hi, bad ïa u nongwei uba wanhap hapdeng jong phi.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Kumne te ki khun Israel baroh ki la leh; kat kaba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses bad u Aaron, kumta hi, ki la leh.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Bad ka la jia ba ha kata hi ka sngi ba U Trai u la wallam ïa ki khun Israel na ka ri Ijipt da ki paidbah."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To pynkyntang ha nga ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh, ïa kaei kaei baroh keiñ ïa kaba la kha nyngkong hapdeng ki khun Israel, na u briew bad na u mrad de: u long u jong nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha u paidbah, “To kynmaw phi ïa kane ka sngi, ha kaba phi la wan noh na ka ri Ijipt, na kata ka ïing ka jingpynlong mraw; naba da ka kti badonbor U Trai u la ïalam noh ïa phi nangta: wat bam ïa u kpu ba dei thiat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ha kane ka sngi phi la wan noh ha u 'nai Abib.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda U Trai u la ïalam ïa me sha ka ri ki Kanaan, bad ki Hit, bad ki Amor, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus de, ïa kaba u la smai ha ki kpa jong me ban ai ha me, ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud bad ka ngap, men leh ïa kane ka kam ha une u bnai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynñiew sngi men bam ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat, te ha ka bahynñiew sngi kan long Ka Jingkhawai Niam ha U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Phin bam ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat hynñiew sngi; bad wat ai ban ïohi bad me ïa u kpu ba dei thiat, bad wat da ai ban ïohi ïa u thiat, ha ki phang jong me baroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Men pynpaw ruh ha u khun jong me ha kata ka sngi, da kaba ong, ‘Ïa kane nga leh, namar kata, ïa kaba U Trai u la leh ha nga, mynba nga la wan noh na ka ri Ijipt.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kane te kan sa long ka dak ïa me ha ka kti jong me, bad kum ka jingpynkynmaw hapdeng ki khmat jong me, khnang ba ka hukum U Trai kan da long ha ka shyntur jong me: namar da ka kti badonbor U Trai u la ïalam noh ïa me na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, men sumar ïa kane ka hukum ha la ka aïom man la ka snem.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Bad ynda U Trai te u la wallam ïa me sha ka ri ki Kanaan, kumba u la smai ha me bad ha ki kpa jong me bad un ai ruh ïa ka ha me,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> te me ruh men pynkyntang ha U Trai ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh, bad ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh na ki mrad ruh ba me don; ki shynrang keiñ kin long ki jong U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ïa uba la kha nyngkong na ka kadda baroh ruh men siewspah da u khun langbrot; te lada men ym siewspah ïa u, to kdiah te ïa ka ryndang jong u: bad baroh ïa uba la kha nyngkong jong u briew hapdeng ki khun jong me men da siewspah ruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u khun jong me un sa kylli ïa me lashai lashisngi, u da ong, ‘Kaei kane?’ men ong ha u te, ‘Da ka kti badonbor U Trai u la ïalam noh ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, na ka ïing ka jingpynlong mraw keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka la jia te mynba u Pharaoh da kaba eh u da pyllait noh ïa ngi, ba U Trai u la pynïap ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh ha ka ri Ijipt, ïa uba la kha nyngkong na u briew, bad ïa uba la kha nyngkong na u mrad ruh. Namar kata, nga kñia ainguh ha U Trai ïa uba la kha nyngkong baroh, uba long shynrang; hynrei, ïa uba la kha nyngkong na ki khun jong nga baroh nga siewspah keiñ.’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kane te kan long ka dak ha ka kti jong me, bad ki jingteh hapdeng ki khmat jong me: namar da ka kti badonbor U Trai u la wallam ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te, mynba u Pharaoh u la pyllait noh ïa uta u paidbah, U Blei um shym la ïalam ïa ki na lynti ka ri ki Philistia, la kata ka la jan ruh; naba U Blei u la ong, “Ba ïoh uta u paidbah un kylla, haba ki ïohi ïa ka thma, bad un leit phai pat sha ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la ïalam ïa uta u paidbah sawdong, na ka lynti ka ri khlaw ka Duriaw Basaw: da kaba kieng atiar ruh ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit mih artet na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim lem bad u ïa ki shyieng jong u Joseph; naba u la pynsmai skhem ïa ki khun Israel, u da ong, “U Blei shisha un da wan-i ïa phi; phi ruh phin ïarah ïa ki shyieng jong nga artet lem bad phi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ynda ki la ïamih noh na Sukkoth, ki la shong dara ha Etham, harud ka ri khlaw.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la ïaid ha shuwa jong ki mynsngi ha u rishot lyoh, ban ïalam lynti ïa ki; bad mynmiet ruh ha u rishot ding, ban ai jingshai ïa ki; ba ki lah ban ïaid mynsngi bad mynmiet ruh:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> um shym la shim noh ïa uta u rishot lyoh mynsngi, lymne ïa uta u rishot ding mynmiet, na khmat uta u paidbah."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Trai te u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel ba kin ïaphai bad kin ïashong dara ruh ha khmat Pihahiroth, hapdeng ka Migdol bad ka duriaw, marpyrshah ïa ka Baal-sephon: ha khmat jong ka phin ïashong dara harud ka duriaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba u Pharaoh un ong shaphang ki khun Israel, ‘La riam ïa ki ha kata ka ri, kata ka ri khlaw keiñ ka la set kut ïa ki.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga ngan pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh, ba un beh nadien jong ki; kumta, ngan ïoh burom halor u Pharaoh, bad halor ki paidïapom jong u baroh; ba ki Ijipt kin ïoh tip ba nga, nga long U Trai.” Te ki la leh kumta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u syiem ka ri Ijipt ba uta u paidbah u da ïaphet noh: te ka dohnud u Pharaoh bad ka jong ki shakri jong u ka la kylla pyrshah ïa uta u paidbah, ki la ïa-ong ruh, “Balei ngi la leh ïa kane, ba ngi la pyllait noh ïa ki khun Israel na kaba shakri ïa ngi?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la pynkhreh ïa la ki kali, bad u la shim ïa la ki paidbah ryngkat bad u:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> u la shim ruh hynriewspah ki kali kiba la kynsai, bad ïa ki kali ka ri Ijipt baroh ruh, bad ïa ki nongïapom ha ki baroh kawei pa kawei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Trai u la pyneh ïa ka dohnud u Pharaoh u syiem ka ri Ijipt, te u la beh nadien ki khun Israel: hynrei, ki khun Israel ki la ïamih noh da ka kti badonbor.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki Ijipt ki la ïabeh nadien jong ki, baroh ki kulai bad ki kali ïapom u Pharaoh, bad ki nongshong kulai jong u ruh, bad ki paidïapom jong u de, bad ki la lap ïa ki ba ki da ïashong dara harud ka duriaw, hajan Pihahiroth, ha khmat ka Baal-sephon.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynba u Pharaoh u la nang jan, ki khun Israel ki la khmied ïa la ki khmat, ha khmih te, ki Ijipt ki ïabeh nadien jong ki; bad ki la khaw-eit shikatdei eh: bad ki khun Israel ki la ïalynñiar ha U Trai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki la ïa-ong ruh ha u Moses, “Namar bymdon ki jingtep ha ka ri Ijipt, ba me la ïalam noh ïa ngi ban ïap ha kane ka ri khlaw? balei ba me la leh kumne bad ngi ban ïalam noh ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kane kam long kata ka ktien ba ngi la ïathuh ha me ha ka ri Ijipt, da kaba ong, ‘To iehnoh ïa ngi, ba ngin ïoh shakri ïa kine ki Ijipt?’ Naba ka la kham bha ïa ngi ban shakri ïa ki Ijipt, ban ïa ka ban ïap ha kane ka ri khlaw.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Wat sheptieng phi, to sangeh, to khmih ruh ïa ka jingpynim jong U Trai ïa kaba un sa pyni ha phi ha kane ka sngi: namar kita ki Ijipt ïa kiba phi la ïohi ha kane ka sngi, phin ym ïohi shuh ïa ki lano lano ruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Trai un ïaleh na ka bynta jong phi, namar kata, to da sngap jar phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Balei ba me lynñiar ha nga? to kren ha ki khun Israel, ba kin nang ïaid noh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad to rah ma me ïa la u diengduh, bad to kner ruh ïa la ka kti halor ka duriaw, to pynïakhlad ruh ïa ka: te ki khun Israel kin ïoh ïaid ryngkew lyngba ïa ka duriaw.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ha khmih, ma nga hi, ngan pyneh ïa ka dohnud ki Ijipt, bad kin bud nadien jong ki: te ngan ïoh burom halor u Pharaoh, bad halor u paidïapom jong u baroh, bad halor ki kali ïapom jong u, bad halor ki nongshong kulai jong u ruh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki Ijipt te kin sa tip ba ma nga, nga long U Trai, ynda nga la ïoh burom halor u Pharaoh, bad halor ki kali ïapom jong u, bad halor ki nongshong kulai jong u ruh.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u angel U Blei uba la ju ïaid ha shuwa ka dara ki Israel, u la kynriah bad u la ïaid noh shadien jong ki; bad uta u rishot lyoh u la kynriah na khmat jong ki, bad u la ïeng shadien jong ki,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad u la wan ïeng hapdeng u paidbah ki Ijipt bad u paidbah ki Israel; bad u la long u lyoh bad ka jingdum, pynban u pynshai mynmiet: kumta, uwei ruh um shym ïajan ïa uta uwei baroh shi miet.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Moses u la kner ïa la ka kti halor kata ka duriaw, bad U Trai u la pynphai pat ïa kata ka duriaw da ka lyer mihngi kaba jur ha kata baroh shi miet, bad u la pynrngad ïa ka duriaw, ïa kita ki um ruh la pynïakhlad.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïaid ryngkew shapdeng ka duriaw: kita ki um ruh ki la long kum ka kynroh ïa ki sha kamon, bad sha kadiang jong ki de.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki Ijipt ki la ïabeh, bad ki la ïabud nadien jong ki shapdeng kata ka duriaw, ki kulai u Pharaoh baroh, bad ki kali ïapom jong u, bad ki nongshong kulai jong u ruh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha ka jingap mynstep, ba U Trai u la khmih ha u paidïapom ki Ijipt lyngba uta u rishot ding bad lyoh, te u la pynkhihwin ruh ïa u paidïapom ki Ijipt.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba u la weng noh ïa ki shalyntem ki kali jong ki, u la pynïaid khia ïa ki: katba ki Ijipt ki la ïa-ong, “Ïa, ngin ïaphet ïap noh na khmat ki Israel; naba U Trai u ïaleh na ka bynta jong ki pyrshah ïa ki Ijipt.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To kner noh ïa la ka kti halor ka duriaw, ba kita ki um kin tyllep pat halor ki Ijipt, halor ki kali ïapom jong ki, bad halor ki nongshong kulai jong ki.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u Moses u la kner noh ïa la ka kti halor ka duriaw, te kata ka duriaw ka la wan phai pat ha la ka bor hamar kaba mynstep; te ki Ijipt ki la phet ïap pyrshah ïa ka; bad U Trai u la kynther noh ïa kita ki Ijipt hapdeng ka duriaw",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kita ki um te ki la ïawan phai pat, bad ki la ïatyllep noh lin ïa kita ki kali ïapom, bad ïa kita ki nongshong kulai, bad ïa uta u paidïapom u Pharaoh baroh kiba la beh nadien jong ki hapdeng ka duriaw; ym shym la sah shuh tang uwei ruh na ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, ki khun Israel ki la ïaid ryngkew hapdeng kata ka duriaw, kita ki um ruh ki la long kum ka kynroh ïa ki sha kamon, bad sha kadiang jong ki de.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la pyllait noh ïa ki Israel ha kata ka sngi na ka kti ki Ijipt; bad ki Israel ki la ïohi ïa kita ki Ijipt ba ki la ïap harud ka duriaw.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki Israel ki la ïohi ïa kata ka kambah ka bakhraw kaba U Trai u la leh halor kita ki Ijipt, bad uta u paidbah u la sheptieng ïa U Trai: bad ki la ngeit ruh ha U Trai bad ha u Moses u shakri jong u."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Moses bad ki khun Israel ki la ïarwai ïa kane ka jingrwai ha U Trai, bad ki la kren, da kaba ong, “Ngan rwai ha U Trai, naba u la jop da ka burom bakhraw: ïa u kulai bad la u nongshong kulai u la bred sha ka duriaw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Trai u long ka bor bad ka jingrwai jong nga, bad u la wan long ka jingpynim ïa nga: U long ma U, U Blei jong nga, bad ngan pyndonburom ïa U; U Blei u kpa jong nga, bad ngan ïaroh burom ïa U.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Trai u long u nongïaleh thma: ‘U Trai’ long ka kyrteng jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ki kali ïapom u Pharaoh bad ki paidïapom jong u, U la phyrnep sha ka duriaw: ïa ki rangbah ïapom jong u ba la donnam ruh la pynngam jyllop ha ka Duriaw Basaw.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki jingjylliew ki la tyllep ïa ki: ki la ngam haduh ka trai kum u maw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka kti kamon jong me, A Trai, ka long kaba donburom ha ka bor, ka kti kamon jong me, A Trai, ka la lympat lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa ki nongshun.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad da ka jingkhraw ka burom jong me, me la pynkyllon ïa kita kiba la ïeng ïaleh ïa me: me la phah noh ïa la ka jingbitar, kaba la bam duh ïa ki kum ïa u jyntang kba.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad da ka jingpyrsad ki thliew khmut jong me la pynïalang lem ïa ki um, ki jingshlei ki la ïeng sha jrong kum ka kynton; ki jingjylliew ki la ïalang hapdeng ka duriaw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uta u nongshun u la ong, ‘Ngan sa beh, ngan sa lap, ngan sa pynïabynta ïa ka jinglute: yn sa pynhun ïa ka jingkwah jong nga halor jong ki; ngan sei ïa la ka waitlam, ka kti jong nga kan sa pynjot ïa ki.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Me la pyrsad da ka lyer jong me, ka duriaw ka la tyllep ïa ki: ki la ïangam kum ka sisa ha kita ki um bajylliew bah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Uei uba kat ma me, A Trai, hapdeng ki blei? uei uba kat ma me uba tyngshaiñ ha ka jingkhuid, uba itieng ha ki jingïaroh, uba leh ïa ki kam phylla?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Me la kner noh ïa la ka la kti kamon, ka khyndew ka la nguid tylli ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Da la ka jingisynei me la ïalam noh ïa uta u paidbah ïa uba me la siewspah: me la btin ïa ki ha ka bor jong me sha ka jaka shongneh ka jingkhuid jong me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki briew kin ïohsngew, bad kin ïasheptieng, ki jingkhuslai kin ngat ha ki nongshong ka ri Philistia.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki syiem Edom kin kyndit; ki briew bakhraw batri ka Moab, ka jingkhynñiuh kan kem ïa ki: ki Kanaan baroh kin sa um noh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka jingsheptieng bad ka jingshyrkhei kin ngat ha ki; da ka jingkhraw ka ksang'ti jong me kin ïasngap jar kum u maw; tad ynda kita ki briew jong me kin ïalait shiliang, A Trai, tad ynda ki ïalait shiliang uta u paidbah ïa uba me la siewspah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Men wallam ïa ki shapoh, bad men thung ruh ïa ki ha u lum ka bynta skhem jong me, kata ka jaka, A Trai, ïa kaba me la khreh ïa lade ban shong duh ha ka, kata ka jaka kyntang keiñ, A Trai, ïa kaba ki kti jong me keiñ ki la pynskhem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Trai un synshar ha la ka rta.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Naba ki kulai jong u Pharaoh lem bad ki kali ïapom jong u bad ki nongshong kulai jong u ruh ki la ïangam sha kata ka duriaw; bad U Trai u la pynphai ïa ki um ka duriaw halor jong ki; hynrei, ki khun Israel ki la ïaid ryngkew hapdeng ka duriaw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka Miriam ka nongïathuhlypa, ka hynmen u Aaron, ka la shim ka kanjari ha la ka kti; ki kynthei baroh ruh ki la ïamih noh hadien jong ka da ki kanjari bad ki jingshad.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka Miriam ka la ong ruh ha ki, “To rwai phi ïa U Trai, naba U la jop da ka burom; ïa u kulai bad ïa u nongshong kulai U la phyrnep sha ka duriaw.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la ïalam ïa ki Israel na ka Duriaw Basaw, ki la ïaleit ruh sha ka ri khlaw jong ka Shur; te ki la ïaid lai sngi lynti ha kata ka ri khlaw, bad kim shym la shem um.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te mynba ki la ïapoi sha Marah, kim lah ban dih ïa ki um jong ka Marah, naba ki la kthang: namar kata, la khot kyrteng “Ka Marah” ïa ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Uta u paidbah te u la khñium ïa u Moses, ki da ïa-ong, “Ngin sa dih aïu?”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u la duwai ha U Trai; te U Trai u la pyni ïa u dieng ïa u, ïa uba haba u la bred ha kita ki um, kita ki um keiñ ki la bang. Hangta u la buh ïa ka hukum bad ka rukom ïa ki, bad hangta u la tynjuh ïa ki;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad u la ong, “Lada men sngap biang biang ruh ïa ka ktien jong U Trai U Blei jong me, bad lada men leh ruh ïa kata kaba dei ha khmat jong u, bad men shahshkor ruh ïa ki hukum jong u, da kaba rakhe ïa ki niam ki rukom jong u baroh, ngan ym da buh ha me kawei ruh keiñ na kita ki jingpang ïa kiba nga la wallam halor ki Ijipt: naba ma nga, nga long U Trai uba pynim ïa me.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ki la ïawan poi sha Elim, ha kaba la don khat-ar tylli ki umpohliew, bad hynñiewphew tylli ki dieng Tlai: bad ki la ïashong dara hangta harud kita ki um."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki la nang ïaid na Elim, bad u paidbah ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïawan poi sha ka ri khlaw Sin, kaba hapdeng ka Elim bad Sinai, ha ka sngi ka bakhatsan jong u bnai u ba-ar hadien ba ki la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad uta u paidbah ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïakhñium ïa u Moses bad ïa u Aaron ha kata ka ri khlaw;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ong ha ki, “A ban da ngi, ngi la ïap da ka kti U Trai ha ka ri Ijipt, mynba ngi la ïashong hajan ki khiew doh, mynba ngi la ïabam ïa u kpu ha ban da kdang; naba phi la wallam noh ïa ngi ha kane ka ri khlaw, ban pynïap ïa une u paidbah baroh da ka jingthngan.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Moses, “Ha khmih, ngan pynhap ïa u kpu ha phi na bneng; bad u paidbah un mih noh ban lum kaba biang shi sngi shi sngi, ba ngan ïoh tynjuh ïa ki, la kin ïaid ha ki hukum jong nga ne em.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka bahynriew, kin ïa-pynkhreh ïa kaba ki wallam hapoh ïing, kata ruh kan long ar shah ïa kaba ki ju lum ha la ka sngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Moses bad u Aaron ki la ïathuh ha ki khun Israel baroh, “Ynda la janmiet, phin sa tip ba U Trai u wallam noh ïa phi na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ha kaba mynstep, phin ïohi ïa ka burom U Trai; naba u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingkhñium jong phi ïa U Trai: ma ngi te ngi long aïu, ba phin da khñium ïa ngi?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Moses u la ong, “Kane kan long, haba U Trai un da ai ha phi la janmiet ïa ka doh ban bam, bad mynstep ïa u kpu haduh ban da kdang ruh; namar ba U Trai u la ïohsngew ïa ki jingkhñium jong phi ïa kiba phi khñium ïa u: ngi long aïu ma ngi? ki jingkhñium jong phi kim long ïa ngi, hynrei, ïa U Trai keiñ.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Moses u la kren ha u Aaron, “To ong ha u paidbah baroh ki khun Israel, ‘To da wan hajan ha khmat U Trai: naba u la ïohsngew ïa ki jingkhñium jong phi.’ ”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka la jia te, mynba u Aaron u dang kren ha uta u paidbah ki khun Israel, ba ki la ïakhmih shaphang kata ka ri khlaw, ha khmih ruh, ka burom U Trai ka la mihpaw ha uta u lyoh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Nga la ïohsngew ïa ki jingkhñium ki khun Israel: to kren ha ki, da kaba ong, ‘Ynda la janmiet phin ïoh bam ïa ka doh, bad mynstep ruh yn pynkdang ïa phi da u kpu; bad phin ïoh tip ba nga long ma nga U Trai U Blei jong phi.’ ”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka la jia te, haba la janmiet, ba ki 'iar khlaw ki la ïawan kiew, bad la ïatap lup ïa ka jaka shong dara jong ki: bad mynstep ka umjer ka la don baroh sawdong kata ka jaka shong dara.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te mynba kata ka umjer kaba la don ka la rngad noh, ha khmih, la don halor kata ka ri khlaw kaei re kaei kaba pyllun, kaba rit kum u thah halor ka khyndew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba ki khun Israel ki la ïohi ïa ka, ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ka manna?” naba kim tip kaei ka long. Te u Moses u la ong ha ki, “Une uta u kpu ïa uba U Trai u la ai ha phi ba phin bam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kane ka long kata ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum, ‘To lum phi uwei uwei baroh na ka katba u donkam ban bam; shi omer ïa uwei uwei u briew, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki briew jong phi, to phin shim, uwei uwei na ka bynta kita kiba don ha ki ïingjaiñ jong u.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh kumta, don kiba la lum kham bun, don ruh kiba kham duna.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ki la ïathew ïa ka ha ka omer, uta uba la lum kham bun um shym la don kaba tam, uta ruh uba la lum kham khyndiat um shym la duna; ki la lum uwei uwei baroh katba u donkam keiñ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Moses u la ong te, “To mano mano ruh wat pynsah satia na ka haduh lashai.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Pynban, kim shym la sngap ïa u Moses; hynrei, don kiba la pynsah na ka haduh mynstep, te ka la man ksaiñ, bad ka la iwtung ruh: te u Moses u la bitar ïa ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki la ju lum ruh ïa ka man ka step, uwei uwei baroh katba u donkam keiñ: te haba ka sngi ka la shit, ka la um noh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka bahynriew ki la lum ar shah u kpu, ar omer ïa uwei uwei u briew: te ki rangbah baroh jong u paidbah ki la ïawan ïathuh ha u Moses.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U ruh u la ong ha ki, “Kane ka long kata ïa kaba U Trai u la ong, ‘Lashai ka long ka jingshongthait jong ka Sabbaton bakhuid ha U Trai: to syang ïa kaba phin sa syang mynta, to shet ruh ïa kaba phin sa shet; bad kata kaba sah tam to buh noh ïa phi haduh lashai.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te la buh noh ïa ka haduh lashai, kumba u Moses u la hukum: te kam shym la iwtung, lymne ym shym la don ksaiñ ha ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong, “To bam ïa kata mynta; naba mynta ka long ka Sabbaton ïa U Trai: phim lah ban shem ïa kane mynta ha ka lyngkha.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynriew sngi phin lum ïa ka; hynrei, ha ka bahynñiew ka long ka Sabbaton, ha kata phin ym shem ei ei ruh em.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Pynban, la don na uta u paidbah kiba la mih noh ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew ïa ka ban lum, te kim shym la shem ei ei ruh em.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Slem haduh katno phin ym kohnguh ban sumar ïa ki hukum bad ki adong jong nga?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Phi ïohi ba U Trai u la ai ha phi ïa ka Sabbaton, namar kata, u la ai ha phi ha ka sngi ka bahynriew ïa kaba ar sngi u kpu; to shong uwei uwei u briew ha la ka jaka, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, to wat ai ban mih mano mano ruh na la ka jaka.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, uta u paidbah u la shongthait ha kata ka sngi ka bahynñiew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ka ïing Israel ki la khot ka kyrteng jong ka, “ka Manna”: te ka la long kum u symbai koriander, balieh; bad haba mad ïa ka ruh ka long kum u kpu uba da ka ngap.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U Moses u la ong ruh, “Kane ka long kata ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum, ‘To pyndap shi omer ha ka, ïa ka ban sumar ïa ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi; ba ki lah ban ïohi ïa uta u kpu da uba nga la bsa ïa phi ha kata ka ri khlaw, mynba nga la wallam noh ïa phi, na ka ri Ijipt.’ ”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> U Moses te u la ong ha u Aaron, “To shim ïa u khiew, bad to thep ha u shi omer ba-dap da ka manna to buh ruh ïa u ha khmat U Trai ïa ka ban sumar ïa ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses, kumta u Aaron u la buh ïa u ha khmat ka jingphla, ïa ka ban sumar.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun Israel te ki la ïabam ïa ka manna sawphew snem, tad ynda ki la ïawan poi sha ka ri kaba shong briew; ki la ïabam keiñ ïa ka manna tad ynda ki la ïawan poi sha ki rud ka ri Kanaan.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ka omer ka long kaba shiphew na ka ephah."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u paidlang ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïamih na ka ri khlaw Sin, ha la ki jingleit, katba kum ka hukum U Trai, bad ki la shong dara ha Rephidim: hynrei, ym shym la don um ban dih u paidbah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar kata, ki paidbah ki la khñium eh ïa u Moses, ki da ïa-ong ruh, “To ai um ïa ngi ba ngin dih.” Bad u Moses u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi ïakhñium eh ïa nga? Balei phi tynjuh ïa U Trai?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki paidbah te ki la ïasliang um eh hangta; bad ki paidbah ki la khñium ïa u Moses, ki da ïa-ong ruh, “Balei me la wallam noh ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, ban pynïap ïa ngi bad ïa ki khun jong ngi bad ïa ki jingri jong ngi de da kaba sliang?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Moses u la kyrpad jam ha U Trai, u da ong, “Ngan leh aïu ïa une u paidbah? Sa khyndiat kin sa lynthem ïa nga.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Moses, “To ïaid ha shuwa uta u paidbah, bad to shim lem bad me na ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel; to shim ruh ïa u diengduh jong me ha la ka kti, da uba me la shoh ïa kata ka wah, to leit ruh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha khmih, ngan ïeng ha khmat jong me hangta halor u mawsiang ha Horeb; bad men shoh ïa uta u mawsiang, te ka um kan sa mih noh na u, ba uta u paidbah un ïoh dih.” Te u Moses u la leh kumta ha khmat kita ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la khot ïa ka kyrteng jong kata ka jaka “Massah”, bad “Meribah”, namar ka jingïapyneh ki khun Israel, bad namar ba ki la tynjuh ïa U Trai, da kaba ong, “U Trai u don hapdeng jong ngi ne em?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, la wan ki Amalek, bad ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel ha Rephidim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha u Joshua, “To jied ha ngi ïa ki rangbah, bad to mih noh ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Amalek: lashai ngan ïeng ha khlieh uta u lum bad u diengduh jong U Blei ha ka kti jong nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la leh kumba u Moses u la ong ha u, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Amalek: te u Moses, u Aaron, bad u Hur ki la leit kiew ha khlieh uta u lum.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te katba u Moses u la dang rah sha jrong ïa la ki kti, ki lah ki Israel: te haba u la pynhiar ïa la ki kti, ki lah ki Amalek keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ki kti u Moses ki la sakhrai: te ki la shim da u maw, ki la buh ruh hapoh jong u, bad u la shong halor jong u: u Aaron de bad u Hur ki la ïakyrshan ïa ki kti jong u, uwei sha kawei ka liang, bad uwei sha kawei pat; kumta, ki kti jong u ki la neh skhem, haduh ban da la sep ka sngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Joshua u la jop thiaw ïa ki Amalek bad u paidbah jong u da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Trai u la ong ruh ha u Moses, “To thoh ïa kane ha ka kitab ban long ka jingpynkynmaw, bad to ïathuh ruh ha u Joshua: namar ngan pyndam noh khoit ïa ka jingkynmaw ïa ki Amalek napoh ka bneng.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Moses u la tei ïa ka duwan, bad u la khot ïa ka kyrteng jong ka “Jehobah-nissi”,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> naba u la ong, “Namar U Trai u la smai: U Trai un ïoh kaba ïaleh thma ïa ki Amalek pateng la pateng.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda u Jethro, u lyngdoh ka ri Midian, u kthaw kurim u Moses, u la ïohsngew ïa kata baroh ba U Blei u la lah leh ïa u Moses, bad ïa ki Israel u paidbah jong u, bad ba U Trai u la lah wallam noh ïa ki Israel na ka ri Ijipt;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ynda kumta, u Jethro, u kthaw kurim u Moses, u la shim ïa ka Sipporah, ka tnga u Moses, ynda u la lah phah noh ïa ka,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ïa ar ngut ki khun shynrang jong ka: ka kyrteng jong uwei na ki ka la long “u Gershom”: naba u la ong, “Nga la long u nongwanwir ha ri nongwei”;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te ka kyrteng jong uta uwei pat “ ‘u Elieser’: naba U Blei u kpa jong nga,” u la ong, “U la long ka jingïarap ïa nga, bad u la pyllait noh ïa nga na ka waitlam u Pharaoh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Jethro, u kthaw kurim u Moses, u la wanlam ha u Moses ïa ki khun shynrang bad ïa ka tnga jong u ha kata ka ri khlaw ha kaba u la shong dara, hajan uta u lum U Blei:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la ong ha u Moses, “Ma nga u Jethro, u kthaw kurim jong me nga la wan ha me, ryngkat bad ka tnga jong me, bad ar ngut ki khun shynrang jong ka lem bad ka.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Moses u la mih ban leit tan ïa la u kthaw kurim, bad u la nguh ïa u, bad u la doh ïa u; te haba ki la ïakylli shaphang ka bakoit bakhiah, ki la ïawan sha ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Moses u la ïathuh naduh haduh ha la u kthaw kurim ïa kaba U Trai u la leh ha u Pharaoh bad ha ki Ijipt na ka bynta ki Israel, bad ïa ka jingjynjar baroh kaba la jia ha kata ka lynti, bad kumno ba U Trai u la pyllait noh ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jethro u la kmen namar ka jinglehbha baroh kaba U Trai u la lah leh ïa ki Israel, ïa kiba u la lah pyllait noh na ka kti ki Ijipt.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Jethro u la ong ruh, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, uba la pyllait noh ïa phi na ka kti ki Ijipt, bad na ka kti u Pharaoh; uba la pyllait noh ïa une u paidbah napoh ka kti ki Ijipt.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mynta nga tip keiñ, ba U Trai u long uba kham khraw ïa ki blei baroh: wat ha kata hi keiñ, ha kaba ki la ïaleh sarong eh halor jong ki.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Jethro, u kthaw kurim u Moses, u la shim ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ïa ki jingkñia ainguh ïa U Blei: bad u Aaron u la wan lem bad ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh, ïa ka ban bam kpu lem bad u kthaw kurim u Moses ha khmat U Blei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, u Moses u la shong ban bishar ïa u paidbah: bad uta u paidbah u la ïaïeng hajan u Moses naduh mynstep haduh ba la ïongreiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u kthaw kurim u Moses u la ïohi ïa kata baroh ba u la leh ïa uta u paidbah, u la ong, “Kaei kane ba me leh ïa u paidbah? balei me shong marwei, bad ba ki briew baroh ki ïaïeng hajan jong me naduh mynstep haduh ba la ïongreiñ?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Moses u la ïathuh ha la u kthaw kurim, “Namar ba ki briew ki ju ïawan ha nga ban ïakylli na U Blei;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> haba ki ïadon kano kano ka kam, ki ïawan sha nga; bad nga bishar keiñ hapdeng ki paralok, bad nga ju pyntip ruh ha ki ïa ki hukum U Blei, bad ïa ki aiñ jong u.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u kthaw kurim u Moses u la ong ha u, “Kane kaba me leh kam long ka babha.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Shisha men sa duh bor noh, ma me hi, bad une u paidbah ruh uba don lem bad me: naba kane ka kam ka kham khia ïa me; mem don bor ban leh ïa kane weibriew.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> To sngap mynta ïa ka ktien jong nga, ngan ai ka jingsneng ïa me, bad U Blei un long ryngkat bad me: To long ma me na ka bynta ki briew ha khmat U Blei, ba men ïoh wallam ïa ki kam jong ki sha U Blei:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> men hikai ruh ha ki, ïa ki rukom bad ki hukum, bad men pyni ha ki, ïa ka lynti ha kaba ki dei ban ïaid, bad ïa ki kam ïa kiba ki dei ban leh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ruh putet, men jied na uta u paidbah baroh ïa ki briew kiba nang basian, ki basheptieng ïa U Blei, ïa ki briew keiñ ki bahok, kiba isih ïa ka jinglalot; men thung ruh kum kine halor jong ki, ba kin long ki nongsynshar ïa ki hajar, bad ki nongsynshar ïa ki spah, bad ki nongsynshar ïa ki sanphew, bad ki nongsynshar ïa ki phew.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> To ai ruh ba kine kin ïabishar ïa ki briew ha la ka sngi: te ïa ki kam kiba jur baroh kin ïawallam ha me, hynrei, ïa ki kam ki barit kin ïabishar hi: kumta kan long kham suk ïa me hi, ma ki ruh kin ïakit lem bad me ïa ka jingkit.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Lada men leh ïa kane, bad U Blei ruh un hukum ïa me kumta, te men long uba lah ban shah, bad une u paidbah baroh ruh un leit sha la ka jaka ha kaba suk.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la sngap ïa ka ktien u kthaw kurim jong u, u la leh ruh ïa kita baroh ïa kiba u la ong.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Moses u la jied na ki Israel baroh ïa ki briew kiba nang basian, bad u la thung ïa ki, ki rangbah halor uta u paidbah, ki nongsynshar ïa ki hajar, ki nongsynshar ïa ki spah, ki nongsynshar ïa ki sanphew, bad ki nongsynshar ïa ki phew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad kita ki la ïabishar ruh ïa u paidbah ha la ka sngi: te ïa kita ki kam kiba jur ki la ïawallam ha u Moses, hynrei, ïa ki kam ki barit baroh ki la ïabishar hi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> U Moses te u la pyllait noh ïa la u kthaw kurim; u ruh u la leit noh sha la ka ri."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha u bnai u balai ynda ki khun Israel ki la ïamih noh na ka ri Ijipt, ha kata kajuh ka sngi ki la ïawan poi sha ka ri khlaw Sinai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar ki la ïaleit mih noh na Rephidim, bad ki la ïawan poi sha ka ri khlaw Sinai, bad ki la ïashong dara ruh ha kata ka ri khlaw: te hangta ki Israel ki la shong dara marpyrshah ïa uta u lum.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Moses u la leit kiew sha U Blei, te U Trai u la khot ïa u na uta u lum, u da ong, “Kumne men ong ha ka ïing u Jakob, bad men ïathuh ha ki khun Israel:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Phi la ïohi ïa kata ïa kaba nga la leh ha ki Ijipt, kumno nga la bah ïa phi halor ki thapniang ki pukni, bad nga la wallam ïa phi ha lade hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te namar kata, lada shisha phin kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad sumar ïa ka jutang jong nga, te phin long ka jingkynshew kaba dei ka jong nga hi nalor ki briew baroh: naba ka pyrthei baroh ka jong nga keiñ:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> phin long ruh ha nga ka hima lyngdoh bad ka jaid bynriew bakyntang. Kine ki ktien ïa kiba men kren ha ki khun Israel.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Moses u la wan bad u la khot ïa ki tymmen basan jong u paidbah, bad u la buh ha khmat jong ki ïa kine ki ktien baroh ïa kiba U Trai u la hukum ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te uta u paidbah baroh ki la ïathuh lang, bad ki la ïa-ong ruh, “Ïa kata baroh ïa kaba U Trai u la kren ngin leh keiñ.” Bad u Moses u la leit ïathuh ïa kita ki ktien jong u paidbah ha U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ha khmih, ngan wan ha me ha u lyoh ba-dum, ba u paidbah un ïohsngew haba nga kren bad me, bad ba un ngeit ïa me ha la ka rta.” Bad u Moses u la ïathuh ïa kita ki ktien jong u paidbah ha U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To leit sha u paidbah, to pynkhuid ruh ïa ki mynta bad lashai, bad kin sait de ïa la ki jaiñkup,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ba kin khreh hamar ka sngi ka balai: namar ha kata ka sngi balai U Trai un sa wan hiar ha khmat u paidbah baroh halor u lum Sinai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Men buh ruh ïa ki pud ïa u paidbah baroh sawdong, da ong, ‘To sumar ïa lade, ba phin ym kiew sha uta u lum, lane ktah ïa ki rud jong u: uno uno ruh uba ktah ïa uta u lum yn pynïap shisha ïa u;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> wat ai ba ka kti kan ktah ïa u, hynrei, da shisha yn lynthem ïa u, lane siat ïap ïa u, la u long u mrad lane u briew, un ym im shuh:’ Haba ka turoi kan sawa jam slem, kin sa kiew sha uta u lum.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Moses u la leit hiar te na uta u lum sha uta u paidbah, bad u la pynkhuid ïa uta u paidbah; bad ki la sait ïa la ki jaiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la ong ruh ha u paidbah, “To long phi kiba la khreh ha ka sngi ka balai: wat leit phi ha la ki tnga.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi balai, mynstep eh, la don ki pyrthat bad ki leilieh, bad u lyoh u barben halor uta u lum, bad ka jingsawa ka turoi bajam eh; katba ki briew baroh ha ka jaka shong dara ki la ïakhynñiuh keiñ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Moses u la wallam noh ïa u paidbah na kata ka dara ïa ka ban ïashem bad U Blei; te ki la ïaïeng ha trai uta u lum.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u lum Sinai u la mih tdem baroh uwei, namar U Trai u la hiar halor jong u ha ka ding; bad ka tdem jong u ka la kiew kum ka tdem ka lawar ding, bad uta u lum baroh uwei u la khynñiuh eh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te mynba ka jingsawa ka turoi ka la slem eh, bad ka la nang kham jam nang kham jam, u Moses u la kren, bad U Blei u la phai ktien ïa u da ka ktien sawa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Trai te u la wan hiar halor u lum Sinai, halor ka khlieh uta u lum: te U Trai u la khot ïa u Moses sha khlieh uta u lum; u Moses u la leit kiew ruh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To leit hiar, to hukum skhem ïa ki briew, ba ïoh kin tur lyngba ha U Trai ban khmih shaiñ, bad ba ïoh bun na ki kin ïap noh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad to ai ba ki lyngdoh ruh de, kiba ju wan hajan U Trai, kin ïapynkhuid ïa lade, ïoh ba U Trai un kyntur ïa ki.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha U Trai, “U paidbah um lah ban wan kiew sha u lum Sinai: naba me la hukum skhem ïa ngi, da kaba ong, ‘To buh ki pud sawdong ïa u lum, to pynkyntang ruh ïa u.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u, “To khie, to hiar ruh; bad men wan kiew, ma me, bad u Aaron lem bad me: hynrei, wat ai ba kita ki lyngdoh bad uta u paidbah kin wan tur lyngba sha U Trai, ïoh ba u un kyntur ha ki keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la leit hiar sha uta u paidbah, bad u la kren ha ki."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Blei u la kren ïa kine ki ktien baroh, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ma nga U Trai uba U Blei jong me, uba la wallam noh ïa me na ka ri Ijipt, na ka ïing ka jinglongmraw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Men ym ïoh kiwei kiwei ki blei nalor jong nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Men ym thaw bleithaw ïa lade, lymne ïa ka dur jong kaei kaei ruh kaba don ha bneng sha jrong, lymne ha ka khyndew shapoh, lymne ha ka um hapoh ka khyndew:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> men ym dem ïa ki, lymne shakri ïa ki: naba nga U Trai uba U Blei jong me nga long U Blei u bathut shen, uba pynwan ïa ka jingpalat ki kpa ha ki khun, haduh ka balai bad ka basaw pateng bynriew jong kiba isih ïa nga;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad uba leh isynei ïa ki hajar, kiba ieit ïa nga bad kiba sumar ruh ïa ki hukum jong nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Men ym ong thala ïa ka kyrteng U Trai U Blei jong me; naba U Trai un ym pynksan ïa uba ong thala ïa ka kyrteng jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Kynmaw ïa ka sngi Sabbaton, ban rakhe khuid ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynriew sngi men trei, bad men leh ïa ka kam jong me baroh:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynrei, ka sngi ka bahynñiew ka long ka Sabbaton ïa U Trai U Blei jong me: ha kata men ym leh kaei kaei ruh ka kam, ma me, lymne u khun jong me, lymne ka khun jong me, lymne u mraw jong me, lymne ka mraw jong me, lymne ka jingri jong me, lymne u nongwei uba hapoh ka phalor jong me:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> naba ha ki hynriew sngi, U Trai u la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew, ïa ka duriaw ruh, bad ïa baroh katba don ha ki, u la shong sngi ruh ha kata ka sngi ka bahynñiew: namar kata, U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa ka sngi Sabbaton, bad u la pynkyntang khuid ïa ka ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “To burom ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie: ba yn pynslem ïa ka rta jong me ha ka khyndew ïa kaba U Trai U Blei jong me u ai ha me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Men ym pynïap.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Men ym klim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Men ym tuh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Men ym sakhi lamler ïa u paramarjan jong me.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Men ym ikwah ïa ka ïing u paramarjan jong me, men ym ikwah ïa ka tnga u paramarjan jong me, lymne ïa u mraw jong u, lymne ïa ka mraw jong u, lymne ïa u masi jong u, lymne ïa u kadda jong u, lymne ïa kaei kaei ruh kaba dei ka jong u paramarjan jong me.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Uta u paidbah baroh te u la ïohi ïa kita ki pyrthat, bad ïa kita ki leilieh, bad ïa kata ka jingsawa ka turoi, bad ïa uta u lum u da mih tdem: te haba uta u paidbah u la ïohi, u la kynriah noh, bad u la ïeng noh na sha jngai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la ïa-ong ruh ha u Moses, “To kren ma me ha ngi, te ngin sngap: hynrei, wat ai ba U Blei un kren ha ngi, ïoh ngi ïap.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Wat sheptieng: namar ïa ka ban tynjuh ïa phi U Blei u la wan, bad ba ka jingsheptieng ïa u kan long ha khmat jong phi, ba phin ym leh pop.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uta u paidbah te u la ïaïeng na sha jngai, bad u Moses u la nang jan sha kata ka jingdum ha kaba U Blei u la don.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Kumne men ong ha ki khun Israel, ‘Phi la ïohi ba nga la kren ha phi na bneng.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nalor jong nga wat thaw ïa ki blei da ka rupa, lymne wat thaw ha phi ïa ki blei da ka ksiar.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Men thaw ïa nga ka duwan da ka khyndew, bad men kñia ïa ki jingainguh thang, bad ïa ki jingkñia bapynïasuk jong me halor jong ka, ïa ki langbrot jong me, bad ïa ki masi dab jong me: ha ki jaka baroh ha kiba nga buh ïa ka jingpynkynmaw ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, ngan wan sha me, bad ngan kyrkhu ruh ïa me.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, lada men thaw ïa nga ka duwan da u maw, wat tei ïa ka da ki maw ba la shtah: namar lada me rah da la ka atiar halor jong ka, me la pyntngit ïa ka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Lymne wat kiew da ki kyrdan ha ka duwan jong nga, ïoh ba kan paw ka jinglyngkhuit jong me ha ka.’ ”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Te kine ki long ki jingbishar ïa kiba men buh ha khmat jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Lada men thied ïa u mraw Hebru, un shakri hynriew snem: te ha ka bahynñiew un ïohlait noh khlem siew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lada u la wan weibriew hi, un leit noh weibriew hi: lada u la shongkurim, te ka tnga jong u kan leit noh lem bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lada u kynrad jong u, u la ai ka tnga ïa u, bad ka la kha ki khun ha u ki shynrang ne kynthei; kata ka tnga bad kita ki khun jong ka kin long ki jong u kynrad jong ka, u te un leit noh marwei hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te lada uta u mraw un ong skhem, ‘Nga ieit ïa la u kynrad, ïa la ka tnga, bad ïa la ki khun de; ngam sngewbha ban lait noh ei’,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ynda kumta, u kynrad jong u, un wallam ïa u sha ki nongbishar, un wallam ruh ïa u sha ka jingkhang, lane sha ka shawkad; bad u kynrad jong u te un sa sam lyngba ïa ka shkor jong u da ka jingsam; te un shakri ïa u ha la ka rta.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Te lada u briew un die ïa la ka khun ban long ka mraw, kan ym ïoh leit noh kumba leit ki mraw shynrang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lada u kynrad jong ka um ibit shuh ïa ka, uba la ïatehktien ïa ka ha lade, te ka dei ïa u ban shah ban sait ram ïa ka: ban die noh ïa ka ha ki nongwei un ym lah ynda u la leh shukor ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te lada u la pynïatehktien ïa ka ha la u khun, un leh bad ka katba kum ka rukom ki khun kynthei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Lada u la shim te da kawei pat; un ym pynduna ïa ka jingbam jong ka, ïa ka jaiñkup jaiñsem, bad ïa ka ïing jong ka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te lada um leh ïa ka, ïa kine lai tylli, kan ïohlait noh khlem siew sbai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Uta uba shoh ïa u briew, katba un ïap, yn pynïap shisha ïa u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te lada u briew um shym la ap thap, hynrei, U Blei u la aiti ïa u ha ka kti jong u; te ngan buh ïa me ka jaka sha kaba un phet ïap noh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, lada u briew un da wan da ka bamut sniew lypa ïa la u paramarjan, khnang ban pynïap ïa u da ka jingshukor; to shim ïa u ïa ka ban pynïap noh, wat na ka duwan jong nga ruh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Uta te uba shoh ïa la u kpa, lane ïa la ka kmie, ka dei shisha ban pynïap ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Uta uba tuh briew, bad uba die ïa u, lane lada shem ïa u ha ka kti jong u, ka dei shisha ban pynïap ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Bad uta uba tim ïa la u kpa, lane ïa la ka kmie, ka dei shisha ban pynïap ïa u.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Lada ki briew te ki da ïakajia paralok, bad ba uwei u da shoh ïa uwei pat da u maw, lane u da kham ïa la ka kti, te ba um pat ïap noh, hynrei, ba la pynthiah ïa u:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> lada un da khie pat, bad ba u da ïaid kai da la u diengduh, te uta u nongshoh un ïohlait: tangba, un buria ïa ka por ba u la duh, bad ba un pynkhiah bha pat ïa u ruh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Te lada u briew un shoh ïa la u shakri, lane ïa la ka shakri, da u dieng, ba u ïap shen ha ka kti jong u; ka dei shisha ban pynhiar kput ïa u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, lada un im shi sngi ne ar sngi, yn ym pynhiar kput ïa u: naba u long ka dor ki sbai jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Lada ki briew ki da ïakajia, bad ki pynmynsaw ïa ka kynthei ba la punkhun, katba kan liat khun, hynrei, kam shym ïap: ka dei shisha ban pynshitom ïa uta, katba u tnga jong kata ka briew un dawa; un sa siew ruh katba rai ki nongbishar.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Lada kan jia ïa ka, ban ïap; te men ai ïa ka jingim namar ka jingim,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ka khmat namar ka khmat, ka bniat namar ka bniat, ka kti namar ka kti, ka kjat namar ka kjat,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> kaba ing namar kaba ing, ka jingmong namar ka jingmong, ka jingjngem snam namar ka jingjngem snam.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Te lada u briew un shoh ïa ka khmat u mraw jong u, lane ïa ka khmat ka mraw jong u, ba ka la sep; un pyllait noh ïa u na ka bynta kata ka khmat jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te lada un lop ïa ka bniat u mraw, lane ïa ka bniat ka mraw jong u; un pyllait noh ïa u na ka bynta kata ka bniat jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Lada u masi u tur briew, ïa u shynrang lane ïa ka kynthei, ba kumta ki ïap, te ka dei shisha ban lynthem ïa uta u masi, bad ban ym bam ïa ka doh jong u ruh; hynrei, u trai uta u masi un lait keiñ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hynrei, lada uta u masi u la ju tur da la ka reng mynshuwa, bad ïa kata ruh la lah pyntip da ki sakhi ha u trai jong u, bad ba u ruh um shym la set noh ïa u, hynrei, ba u da pynïap ïa u shynrang lane ïa ka kynthei; ïa uta u masi ka dei ban lynthem, bad ïa u trai jong u ruh ka dei ban pynïap.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Lada la daiñ kuna ïa u, ka dei ïa u ban ai ka dor na ka bynta ka jingim jong u katba la rai ïa u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Lada u la tur ïa u khynnah, lane ïa ka khynnah, yn leh ïa u kat kane ka jingbishar.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Lada uta u masi un tur ïa u mraw, lane ïa ka mraw; un da ai ha u kynrad jong ki laiphew shekel rupa, ïa uta u masi ruh ka dei ban lynthem.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Bad lada u briew un plie ïa ka pukri, lane lada u briew un tih ïa ka pukri bad um tap ïa ka, bad u masi ne u kadda un da hap hangta,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> u trai jong kata ka pukri un buria; bad un ai da ki tyngka ha uta u trai jong ki; te ïa uta u mrad ba la ïap un ïoh sha u keiñ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Lada u masi jong uwei u briew u tur ïa u jong uwei pat, ba un ïap ruh; te kin die ïa uta u masi ba-im, bad kin ïasam ïa ka dor jong u; bad ïa uta u baïap ruh kin ïasam.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Lane lada la lah tip ba uta u masi u la ju tur mynshuwa, bad u trai jong u um shym la set noh ïa u; shisha un da buria masi kylliang, bad ïa uta u baïap un ïoh sha u keiñ."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Lada u briew un tuh ïa u masi, lane ïa ka langbrot, bad un pynïap ïa ka, lane un die ïa ka; un buria san tylli ki masi dab namar uwei u masi, bad saw tylli ki langbrot namar kawei ka langbrot.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba shem ïa u nongtuh ba u dang prat ïa ka ïing, bad la shoh ïap ïa u ruh, kam dei ban pynhiar kput na ka bynta uta.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lada ka sngi ka la mih ha u, ka dei ban pynhiar kput na ka bynta jong u: ka dei ïa u ban pynburia pat biang; lada um don ei ei ruh em, te yn sa die ïa u na ka bynta kata ka jingtuh jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lada la shem shisha ha ka kti jong u ïa kata ka jingtuh ba dang im, la ka long u masi, ne ka kadda, ne ka langbrot; un pynburia ar shah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Lada u briew un pynbam ïa ka lyngkha lane ïa ka brisoh, da kaba buh ïa u mrad la u jong, ban bam ha ka lyngkha jong uwei pat; un sa pynburia pat na ka babha tam ka lyngkha jong u, lane na ka babha tam ka brisoh jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Lada ka ding ka la meh, bad ka la kem ïa ki dieng shiah, katba la pyning ïa u Kew ha ka thup, lane ïa u bym pat ot, lane ïa ka lyngkha; uta uba la pynmeh ïa kata ka ding un sa pynburia pat baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Haba u briew un ai sumar ha la u paramarjan ïa ki tyngka ne ïa kaei kaei ruh, bad haba la tuh noh ïa kata na ka ïing uta u briew; lada shem ïa u nongtuh, un pynburia ar shah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te lada ym shem ïa uta u nongtuh, ynda kumta, yn wallam ïa u trai kata ka ïing ha ki nongbishar, ban tohkit la u la ktah ne em ïa kaei kaei ruh ka jong u paramarjan jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Naba ïa ka kynja ka jingpalat baroh, la ka long na ka bynta u masi, lane ka kadda, lane ka langbrot, lane ka jaiñkup, lane na ka bynta kaei kaei ruh kaba la jah, ïa kaba uwei pat u kam kum la ka jong, ka dei ïa ka daw jong ki baroh ar liang ban poi ha khmat ki nongbishar; te uta ïa uba kita ki nongbishar kin ïa-pynrem, un sa buria ar shah ïa la u paramarjan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Lada u briew u ai sumar ha la u paramarjan ïa ka kadda, lane ïa u masi, lane ïa ka langbrot, lane ïa ka mrad kaei kaei ruh; bad haba ka ïap noh, ne ka mynsaw, ne la ñiah noh ïa ka khlem da ïohi mano mano ruh,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> te ka jingpynsmai U Trai kan da long hapdeng jong ki baroh ar ngut, ba um shym la ktah kti ïa kaei kaei ruh ka jong u paramarjan jong u; bad u trai jong ka un pdiang ïa kata, uta te un ym pynburia satia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te lada la tuh ïa ka na u, un sa pynburia kaba biang ha u trai jong ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lada la bam mrad ïa ka, un wallam ïa ka kum ka jingsakhi; te un ym buria shuh ïa kata kaba la bam mrad.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Lada u briew un shim kylliang na la u paramarjan, te lada kan mynsaw, lane kan ïap, haba u trai jong ka um don ryngkat bad ka, ka dei ïa u shisha ban pynburia ïa ka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te lada u trai jong ka u don ryngkat hangta, un ym pynburia ïa ka: lada ka long kaba wai, na ka bynta kaba wai jong ka, ka la wan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Lada u briew un pynshoi ïa ka samla ka bym pat ïatehktien, bad u thiah ruh bad ka, shisha un ai jingai na ka bynta jong ka ba kan long ka tnga jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Lada u kpa jong ka um mon satia ban ai ïa ka ha u, un sa buria katba kum ka bynta ki theisotti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Men ym shah ïa ka nongkren byrtong ban im.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Uno uno ruh uba thiah lem bad ka mrad, ka dei shisha ban pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Yn pynduh noh ïa uta uba kñia ainguh ha kiwei pat ki blei, nalor jong U Trai hi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Men ym pynshitom lane banbor ïa u nongwei: naba phi hi phi la ju long nongwei ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wat banbeiñ ïa kano kano ruh ka riewkynthei, lane ïa ki khunswet.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Lada men lehbeiñ ïa ki ha kano kano ka rukom, bad ba kin shu kyrpad ha nga, nga da shisha ngan sngap ïa ka jingkyrpad jong ki;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad kan sa meh ka jingbitar jong nga, te ngan pynïap ïa phi da ka waitlam; te ki tnga jong phi kin sa long ki riewkynthei, bad ki khun jong phi kin sa long ki khunswet.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Lada men ai kylliang sbai ha uwei u baduk na ki briew jong nga uba hajan jong me, men ym long ha u kum u nongshim than; lymne men ym kheiñ sut ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Lada men shim bynda na la u paramarjan da ka jaiñkup, men ai pat ha u hamar kaba sep ka sngi:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> naba kata hi ka long ïa ka ban tap ïa u, ka long ka jaiñkup ïa ka snieh jong u: un kup thiah da ei? kan jia te, haba u kyrpad ha nga, ba ngan sngap; naba nga uba isynei.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Men ym krenbeiñ ïa ki nongbishar, lymne men ym tim ïa u rangbah u paidbah jong me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Men ym pyntud ban ainguh ïa u banyngkong na ki soh ba-ih jong me, bad na ki umsoh jong me. Men ai ha nga ïa u banyngkong na ki khun shynrang jong me.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Men sa leh kumjuh ïa la ki masi dab, bad ïa ki langbrot jong me; hynñiew sngi un long lem bad la ka kmie; ha ka baphra sngi men ai ïa u ha nga.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Phin long ruh ki briew bakyntang ha nga; lymne wat bam ïa ka doh ba la tar ki mrad ha lum; to phin bred ïa ka ha ki ksew."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Wat pynmih ïa ka jingbna balamler: wat ïasoh lem bad ki bymman ban long u nongsakhi bymhok.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Men ym bud ïa u paidbah ïa ka ban leh sniew; lymne wat phai ktien ha ka jingïakajia, da kaba bud ïa kiba bun ban pynsniew ïa ka jingbishar;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> lymne wat ïashah ïa u baduk ha ka jingïakajia jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Lada men shem ïa u masi dab lane ïa ka kadda u nongshun jong me ba ïaid sakma, da shisha men da wallam ïa u ha u pat.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Lada me ïohi ïa ka kadda jong uba shun ïa me ba ka la kyllon hapoh la ka jingkit, te men ym ïarap ïa u? Da shisha men da ïarap lem bad u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Ha ka jingïakajia jong u, men ym pynsniew ïa ka jingbishar u baduk jong me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> To men kiar jngai na ka kam ka bashukor; lymne wat pynïap ïa uba lui lui bad u bahok: naba nga ngan ym pynksan ïa u bymman.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wat bamsap: naba kaba bamsap ka pynmatlah ïa ki bastad, bad ka pynbakla ruh ïa ki ktien jong ki bahok.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Wat banbor ïa u nongwei: naba phi sngewthuh ïa ka dohnud u nongwei, naba phi hi ruh phi la ju long ki nongwei ha ka ri Ijipt.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Hynriew snem ruh men bet ïa ka khyndew jong me, bad men lum ïa ki soh jong ka;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> hynrei, ha ka snem ka bahynñiew men iehnoh ïa ka, ba kan long shrah ba ki baduk ki jong me kin ïoh bam: bad kata ïa kaba ki ïa-iehnoh kin bam ki mrad khlaw. Kumjuh ruh men leh bad la ka brisoh, bad la ki dieng Olib de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Hynriew sngi men leh ïa ka kam jong me, bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew men shong sngi: ba u masi jong me, bad ka kadda jong me kin ïoh shongthait, bad ba u khun ka mraw jong me, bad u nongwei, kin shong pyngngad ruh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha kiei kiei baroh ba nga la ong ha phi phin sumar biang: wat kynmaw ïa ka kyrteng kiwei ki blei, lymne wat ai ban ïohsngew ïa ka na ka shyntur jong me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Lai sien shi snem men rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam ïa nga.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Men rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat: hynñiew sngi men bam ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat, kumba nga la hukum ïa me ha ka por ba la buh ha u bnai Abib (naba ha uta me la mih na ka ri Ijipt); bad wat ai ban mihpaw suda uwei ruh ha khmat jong nga:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Aïom Ot, ki soh nyngkong ki jingtrei jong me, ïa kiba me la bet ha ka lyngkha: bad Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Jingïalum ruh, ha ka bakut ka snem, haba me la lum ïa ki jingtrei jong me na ka lyngkha.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Lai sien shi snem ki shynrang jong me baroh kin ïa-mihpaw ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong me.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Men ym kñia ïa ka snam ka jingkñia jong nga lem bad u kpu ba dei thiat; lymne wat ai ban sah ka khleiñ ka jingkñia jong nga haduh mynstep.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Men wallam ïa u banyngkong na ki soh nyngkong ka khyndew jong me ha ka ïing U Trai U Blei jong me. Wat shet ïa u khun blang ha ka dud ka kmie jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ha khmih, nga phah ïa u angel ha shuwa jong me, ban sumar ïa me ha lynti, bad ban wallam ïa me sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba nga la khreh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> To burom ïa u, bad to kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong u; wat pynbitar ïa u: namar un ym map ïa ki jingpalat jong phi; naba ka kyrteng jong nga ka don ha u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Hynrei, lada shisha men kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong u, bad men leh ïa kaba nga kren baroh; te ngan long u nongshun ïa ki nongshun jong me, bad u nongïaleh ïa ki nongïaleh jong me.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Naba u angel jong nga un ïaid ha shuwa jong me, bad un ïalam ïa me shapoh sha ki Amor, bad ki Hit, bad ki Peris, bad ki Kanaan, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus de: bad ngan pynjot noh ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Men ym dem ha ki blei jong ki, lymne shakri ïa ki, lymne leh katba kum ki kam jong ki: hynrei, men pynduh khoit ïa ki, bad lympat ïa ki durblei jong ki lyngkhot lyngkhai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Phin shakri te ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, te un kyrkhu ïa u kpu jong me, bad ïa ka um jong me; bad ngan shim noh ïa ka jingpang napdeng jong me.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kin ym don ei ei ruh em, ha ka ri jong me, kiba liat khun, lane ki balyngki: ngan sa pyndap biang ïa ka jingkheiñ ki sngi jong me.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngan phah ïa ka jingsheptieng jong nga ha shuwa jong me, bad ngan pynjot noh ïa ki briew baroh sha kiba men wan, bad ngan pynphai dien ïa ki nongshun jong me baroh na me.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ngan phah ïa ki kyieng ha shuwa jong me, ki ban beh noh ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Kanaan, bad ïa ki Hit, na khmat jong me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ngan ym beh ïa ki na khmat jong me ha kaba shi snem; ïoh ba kata ka ri kan long kynjah, bad u mrad khlaw un man bun pyrshah ïa me.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mian pa mian keiñ ngan beh noh ïa ki na khmat jong me, tad ynda me la roi, bad me la ïoh pateng ïa kata ka ri ruh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ïa ki pud jong me te ngan buh, naduh ka Duriaw Basaw haduh ka duriaw ki Philistia, bad naduh ka ri khlaw haduh kata ka wah: namar ngan aiti ïa ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri ha ka kti jong phi; te men beh noh ïa ki na khmat jong phi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Men ym pynlong ïa ka jutang bad ki, lymne bad ki blei jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Wat shah ba kin ïashong sah ha ka ri jong me, ïoh ba kin ïalam ïa me ban leh pop ïa nga: namar lada men shakri ïa ki blei jong ki, da shisha kata kan long ka jingriam ïa me.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la ong ha u Moses, “To wan kiew sha U Trai, ma me, bad u Aaron, bad u Nadab, bad u Abihu, bad ki hynñiewphew ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel; bad to mane phi na sha jngai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te tang u Moses hi un wan hajan ïa U Trai; hynrei, ki, kin ym wan hajan, lymne uta u paidbah un ym leit lem bad u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Moses te u la wan ïathuh ha uta u paidbah ïa ki ktien U Trai baroh, bad ïa ki jingbishar baroh: te uta u paidbah baroh u la ïathuh da kawei ka ktien, u da ong ruh, “Ïa ki ktien baroh kiba U Trai u la ong; ngin leh keiñ.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Moses u la thoh ïa ki ktien U Trai baroh, bad u la khie ruh dang step, bad u la tei ïa ka duwan ha trai uta u lum, bad ïa ki khat-ar ki païa, katba kum ki khat-ar jaid Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u la phah ïa ki samla na ki khun Israel, kiba la kñia ïa ki jingainguh thang, bad ki la kñia da ki masi lyngraw ïa ka jingkñia bapynïasuk ha U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim shiteng na ka snam, bad u la buh ïa ka ha ka pliang; bad shiteng na kata ka snam u la synreit halor kata ka duwan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Haba u la shim te ïa ka kitab ka jutang, u la pule ha kaba ïohsngew uta u paidbah; ki te ki la ong, “Ïa kata baroh kaba U Trai u la kren, ngin leh, bad ngin kohnguh.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim ïa kata ka snam, bad u la synreit ïa ka halor uta u paidbah, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, ka snam jong kata ka jutang ïa kaba U Trai u la pynlong bad phi shaphang kine ki ktien baroh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, u Moses u la leit kiew, bad u Aaron, u Nadab, bad u Abihu, bad hynñiewphew ngut ki tymmen basan ki Israel,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki la ïohi ïa U Blei ki Israel; te la don hapoh ki sla'jat jong u kumba la siang da u maw Sapphir, bad kum ka met jong ki bneng ha ka jingphyrnai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te halor kita ki bakhraw batri jong ki khun Israel um shym la buh ïa la ka kti: hynrei, ki la ïohi keiñ ïa U Blei, te ki la ïabam ki la ïadih.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To wan kiew sha nga ha une u lum, to sah hangta ruh: bad ngan ai ha me ïa ki maw lyngkniap, bad ïa ki hukum bad ïa ki adong ïa kiba nga la thoh, ba men ïoh hikai ïa ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Moses u la ïeng, bad u Joshua u shakri jong u; bad u Moses u la leit kiew sha uta u lum jong U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha kita ki tymmen basan, “To nang ap ïa ngi hangne, tad ynda ngin da wan pat sha phi; te ha khmih, u Aaron bad u Hur ki ïadon lem bad phi: lada uno uno ruh u don kano kano ruh ka kam, ai ba un leit ha ki.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Moses u la leit kiew sha uta u lum, bad u lyoh u la tap ïa uta u lum.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka burom U Trai ka la neh halor u lum Sinai, uta u lyoh te u la tap ïa u, hynriew sngi: te ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, u la khot ïa u Moses napdeng uta u lyoh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka jingkhmih ka burom U Trai te ka la long kum ka ding kaba bam duh ha khlieh uta u lum ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Moses u la leit shapdeng uta u lyoh, bad u la kiew noh sha uta u lum: bad u Moses u la sah ruh ha uta u lum sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, ba kin wallam ha nga ïa ka jingainguh: na u briew baroh uba ai sngewbha na la ka dohnud keiñ phin shim ïa kita ki jingainguh jong nga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kane te ka jingainguh ïa kaba phin shim na ki: ïa ka ksiar, ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka tama;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ïa ka jaiñ babyrïong, bad ïa ka basaw bthuh, bad ïa ka basaw syng-iang, bad ïa ka jaiñ linen bani, bad ïa u shñiuh blang;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ïa ki snieh ki langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ki snieh takash, bad ïa u dieng Shittim;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ïa ka umphniang ïa ka jingshai, bad ïa ki musla ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ïa ki maw Oniks, bad ïa ki maw ban buh ha ka ephod, bad ha ka jingdeng shadem de.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad to kin thaw ïa ka jaka kyntang ïa nga; khnang ba ngan ïoh shongneh hapdeng jong phi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Katba kum kita baroh ïa kiba nga la pyni ha me, ïa kata ka dur Ka Tabernakl, bad ki dur ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, kumta keiñ phin thaw ïa ka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Te kin thaw ïa ka synduk da u dieng Shittim: ka lynter jong ka, ar pruh shiteng, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, shi pruh shiteng, bad ka jingjrong jong ka ruh, shi pruh shiteng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad men suit ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla, shapoh bad shabar men suit ksiar ïa ka keiñ, bad men thaw halor jong ka, ïa ka pansngiat da ka ksiar baroh sawdong.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa ki saw tylli ki kyrwoh da ka ksiar, bad buh ïa ki ha ki saw ki dong jong ka; ha kawei ka liang jong ka, ar tylli ki kyrwoh, bad ha kawei pat ka liang jong ka, ar tylli ki kyrwoh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad men thaw ïa ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad men da suit ksiar ïa ki ruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Men buh ruh ïa kita ki dieng jingbah ha kita ki kyrwoh ha baroh ar liang kata ka synduk, ïa ka ban bah da ki ïa ka synduk.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kita ki dieng jingbah kin ïaisah ha kita ki kyrwoh kata ka synduk: wat sei shuh ïa ki na ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad men thep ha kata ka synduk ïa ka jingphla ïa kaba ngan sa ai ha me.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa ka jingtap-isynei da ka ksiar banylla; ka lynter jong ka, ar pruh shiteng, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka ruh, shi pruh shiteng.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad men thaw ar tylli ki Kherub da ka ksiar, da kaba shoh tylli men thaw ïa ki, na ki baroh ar ki tduh jong kata ka jingtap-isynei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ïa uwei u Kherub men thaw na kawei ka tduh, bad ïa uta uwei pat u Kherub na kata kawei pat ka tduh: na kata ka jingtap-isynei hi keiñ phin thaw ïa kita ki Kherub na baroh ar ki tduh jong ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kita ki Kherub te kin pynïar ïa la ki thapniang sha jrong, ki da kah ïa kata ka jingtap-isynei da la ki thapniang, bad kin ïaphai markhmat; shaphang kata ka jingtap-isynei kita ki Kherub kin ïa-peit.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad men buh ïa kata ka jingtap-isynei halor kata ka synduk; bad men thep ha kata ka synduk ïa kata ka jingphla ïa kaba ngan sa ai ha me.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te hangta ngan ïashem bad me, bad nalor kata ka jingtap-isynei, napdeng kita ki ar tylli ki Kherub kiba halor kata ka synduk ka jingphla, ngan ïathuh ha me ïa kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba ngan hukum ïa ki khun Israel.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka miej na u dieng Shittim: ka lynter jong ka, ar pruh, ka pyngkiang jong ka, shi pruh, bad shi pruh shiteng, ka jingjrong jong ka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad men suit ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla, bad to thaw ïa ka pansngiat ruh ïa ka baroh sawdong da ka ksiar.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad men thaw ka rmiang ïa ka, kaba shi khup baroh sawdong, men thaw ruh ïa ka pansngiat ksiar halor kata ka rmiang jong ka baroh sawdong.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad men thaw ïa ka saw tylli ki kyrwoh da ka ksiar, bad to buh ïa kita ki kyrwoh ha kita ki saw ki dong jong ka kiba ha ki saw ki kjat jong ka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ha marpyrshah kata ka rmiang kin don kita ki kyrwoh, ban long ki jaka ïa ki dieng jingbah ki ban bah ïa kata ka miej.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa kita ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad to suit ksiar ïa ki, ïa ka ban bah ïa kata ka miej da ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad men thaw ïa ki pliang jong ka, bad ïa ki siang jong ka, bad ïa ki jingtap jong ka ruh, bad ïa ki khuri jong ka ruh, ki ban theh jingtheh da ki; da ka ksiar banylla men thaw ïa ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Halor kata ka miej te, men buh ïa u 'pu pyni ha khmat jong nga ha la ka sngi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak da ka ksiar banylla: ba la shoh tylli men thaw ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak, ka met jong ka, bad ki tnat jong ka, ki shata sharak jong ka, bad ki shrong jong ka, bad ki syntiew jong ka ruh de, kin long na kata kajuh;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad hynriew tylli ki tnat kin ïamih na ki ar liang jong ka; lai tylli ki tnat ka dieng pynïeng sharak na kawei ka liang, bad lai tylli ki tnat jong kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak na kawei pat ka liang;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> lai tylli ki shata sharak ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam, bad ka shrong bad u syntiew, ha kawei ka tnat; bad lai tylli ki shata sharak ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam ha kata kawei pat ka tnat, bad ka shrong bad u syntiew; kumjuh ha kita ki hynriew tylli ki tnat kiba mih na kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad ha kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak kin long saw tylli ki shata sharak ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam, lem bad ki shrong bad ki syntiew jong ki:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad kawei ka shrong kan long hapoh ar tylli ki tnat jong ka, bad kawei ka shrong kan long hapoh ar tylli ki tnat jong ka, katba kum kita ki hynriew tnat kiba ïamih na kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ki shrong jong ki bad ki tnat jong ki kin long na kajuh: baroh keiñ kan long ba la shoh tylli da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Men thaw ruh hynñiew tylli ki sharak jong ka, bad men tbeh ïa kita ki sharak jong ka, ba kin ai jingshai ha pyrshah ka khmat jong ka.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ki nap lur sharak jong ka, bad ki khuri jong ka ruh, kin long da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kata ka ksiar banylla da kaba men thaw ïa ka, lem bad kine ki pliang baroh, kan long shi talent.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te men sumar ba men thaw ïa ki keiñ ha la ka dur ka dur, ïa kaba la pyni ha me ha uta u lum."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ïa Ka Tabernakl ruh men thaw da ki shiphew ki jingkah; da ki jaiñ linen bani ba la jyrthiaw, bad ka babyrïong, bad basaw bthuh, bad basaw syng-iang, men thaw ïa ki, kiba don Kherub da ka jingtrei stad.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka lynter jong kawei ka jingkah kan long arphew phra pruh, bad ka pyngkiang kawei ka jingkah, saw pruh: bad kita ki jingkah baroh te kin ïoh kajuh ka jingthew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> San tylli ki jingkah yn pynïasoh lang paralok; bad san tylli kiwei pat ki jingkah yn pynïasoh lang paralok.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa ki kyrwoh da ka babyrïong ha ka rmiang kawei ka jingkah na ka rmiang ha ka jingpynïasoh; kumjuh ruh men thaw ha ka rmiang eh jong ka jingkah kaba kham harud, ha ka jingpynïasoh ka ba-ar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh men thaw ha kawei ka jingkah, bad sanphew ki kyrwoh men thaw ha kata ka jingkah kaba don ha ka jingpynïasoh ka ba-ar; ba kita ki kyrwoh kin ïasoh lang baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Men thaw ruh sanphew tylli ki jingpyndait da ka ksiar, bad men pynïasoh lang ïa kita ki jingkah da kita ki jingpyndait, ba kan long kawei Ka Tabernakl.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ki jingkah da u 'ñiuh blang, ïa ka ban long ka jingsop ïa Ka Tabernakl: men thaw khatwei tylli ki jingkah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka lynter jong kawei kan long laiphew pruh bad ka pyngkiang jong kawei ka jingkah, saw pruh; bad kita ki khatwei tylli ki jingkah kin long kajuh ka jingthew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad men pynïasoh san tylli ki jingkah kyrpang, bad hynriew tylli ki jingkah kyrpang, te ïa kata ka jingkah ka bahynriew men pynlong ar syrtap ha khmat jong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad men thaw sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh ha ka rmiang jong kata ka jingkah, kaba harud eh ha ka jingpynïasoh, bad sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh ha ka rmiang jong kata kawei pat ka jingkah ha ka jingpynïasoh ka ba-ar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “To thaw ruh sanphew tylli ki jingpyndait da ka tama, to buh ruh ïa kita ki jingpyndait ha kita ki kyrwoh, bad to pynïasoh lang ruh ïa kata ka jingtap, ba kan long kawei keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, kata kaba tam kaba sah na kita ki jingkah ka jingsop, kata ka shiteng ka jingkah keiñ kaba sah tam, kan noh sha kyrpong Ka Tabernakl.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad shi pruh ha kawei ka liang, bad shi pruh ha kawei pat ka liang, na kata kaba sah tam ha ka lynter kata ka jingsop, kan noh halor kita ki liang jong Ka Tabernakl, ha kane ka liang bad ha katai ka liang, ïa ka ban tap ïa ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad men thaw ruh ïa ka jingtap halor kata ka jingsop da ki snieh langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ka jingtap halor kata ruh da ki snieh takash.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “To shna ki lyntang ïa Ka Tabernakl na u dieng Shittim ïa ka ban ker pynïeng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Shiphew pruh, ka lynter jong kawei ka lyntang, bad shi pruh shiteng, ka pyngkiang jong kawei ka lyntang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ar tylli ki tnaw kin long ha kawei ka lyntang, ba la buh ter ter marpyrshah: kumne keiñ men thaw ïa ki lyntang Ka Tabernakl baroh,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad men shna ïa ki lyntang ïa Ka Tabernakl, arphew tylli ki lyntang ha ka liang kaba shaphang shathie.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad men thaw sawphew tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa, hapoh kita ki arphew tylli ki lyntang; ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei ka lyntang ïa kita ki ar tylli ki tnaw jong ka, bad ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei pat ka lyntang ïa kita ki ar tylli ki tnaw jong ka;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ïa ka liang ka ba-ar jong Ka Tabernakl kaba shaphang shatei, kin long arphew tylli ki lyntang;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad sawphew tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa jong ki; ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei ka lyntang, bad ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei pat ka lyntang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Men shna ruh hynriew tylli ki lyntang ïa ka liang jong Ka Tabernakl kaba shaphang sepngi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ar tylli ki lyntang men shna ïa ki dong jong Ka Tabernakl baroh ar liang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad yn pynïasoh lang ïa ki shapoh, bad yn pynïasoh lang na khlieh jong ka da kawei ka kyrwoh: kumne keiñ kan long ïa ki baroh ar; kin long ïa kita ar tylli ki dong.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kin long ruh phra tylli ki lyntang, bad ki thliew tnaw rupa jong ki, khathynriew ki thliew tnaw; ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei ka lyntang, bad ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei pat ka lyntang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Men shna ruh ïa ki dieng khap da u dieng Shittim; san tylli ïa ki lyntang jong kawei ka liang Ka Tabernakl,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ïa san tylli ki dieng khap ïa ki lyntang jong kawei pat ka liang Ka Tabernakl, bad san tylli ki dieng khap ïa ki lyntang jong kawei ka liang Ka Tabernakl, ïa kita baroh ar ki liang kiba shaphang sepngi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te uta u dieng khap pdeng, uba hapdeng kita ki lyntang un da kot baroh shilynter.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad men suit ksiar ïa kita ki lyntang, bad men thaw ïa ki kyrwoh jong ki da ka ksiar ban long ki jaka ïa kita ki dieng khap: bad to men suit ksiar ïa kita ki dieng khap ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad men pynïeng ïa Ka Tabernakl katba kum kata ka dur jong ka, ïa kaba la pyni ha me ha uta u lum.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka jingkah pdeng da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad da ka linen bani ba la jyrthiaw: yn thaw ïa ka, kaba don ki Kherub da ka jingtrei bastad;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad men woh ïa ka halor ki saw tylli ki rishot dieng Shittim ba la suit ksiar, ki bnoh jong ki da ka ksiar, ha ki saw tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad men woh ïa kata ka jingkah pdeng ha kita ki jingpyndait, ba me lah ban wallam hapoh hangta shapoh kata ka jingkah keiñ ïa ka synduk ka jingphla: bad kata ka jingkah pdeng kan pynïakhlad ha phi hapdeng ka jaka kyntang bad ka bakyntang tam eh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> To men buh ïa ka jingtap-isynei halor kata ka synduk ka jingphla ha kata ka bakyntang tam eh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad men buh ïa kata ka miej habar kata ka jingkah, bad ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak de marpyrshah kata ka miej ha ka liang Ka Tabernakl kaba shaphang shathie: bad kata ka miej men buh shaphang shatei.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “To men thaw ïa ka pyrda ruh ïa ka jingkhang jong kata ka ïingjaiñ da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la jyrthiaw, ba la suh ruh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad men thaw ïa kata ka pyrda san tylli ki rishot da u dieng Shittim, men da suit ksiar ïa ki ruh; ki bnoh jong ki da ka ksiar; bad ïa kita men saiñdur san tylli ki thliew tnaw tama."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka duwan da u dieng Shittim, san pruh ka lynter, bad san pruh ka pyngkiang; kata ka duwan kan long sawdong; bad ka jingjrong jong ka, lai pruh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad men thaw ïa ki reng jong ka ha ki saw ki dong jong ka: ki reng jong ka kin long na kajuh: bad men suit ïa ka ruh da ka tama.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad men thaw de ïa ki pliang jong ka ban pdiang ïa ka dpei jong ka, bad ïa ki siang jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka, bad ïa ki proh jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang ding jong ka ruh: ïa ki jingbuh jong ka baroh men thaw da ka tama.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad men thaw ïa ka jaka sliew ding ïa kaba la thain kriah da ka tama; bad halor kata ka kriah ha ki saw ki dong jong ka, men thaw saw tylli ki kyrwoh tama.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad men buh ïa ka hapoh ka thliew jong kata ka duwan na shapoh, ba kata ka kriah kan kot haduh pdeng kata ka duwan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa ki dieng jingbah ïa kata ka duwan, ïa ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim keiñ, da suit da ka tama ïa ki ruh;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ïa kita ki dieng jingbah men pynphrung ha kita ki kyrwoh, bad kita ki dieng jingbah kin long ha ki baroh ar liang kata ka duwan, ïa ka ban bah ïa ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Men thaw ïa ka, kaba thliew da ki lyntang kumba la pyni ïa me ha uta u lum, kumta hi keiñ, men thaw ïa ka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “To men thaw ruh ïa ka phyllaw Ka Tabernakl; ha ka liang kaba shaphang shathie, ki pyrda kata ka phyllaw kin long da ka jaiñ linen bani ba la jyrthiaw, shispah pruh, ka lynter ïa kawei ka liang;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad kita arphew tylli ki rishot jong ka, bad kita arphew tylli ki thliew tnaw jong ki, kin long da ka tama; ki bnoh jong kita ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki, kin long da ka rupa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumjuh ruh, ha ka liang kaba shaphang shatei, ka lynter ki pyrda kan long shispah pruh, bad arphew tylli ki rishot jong ki, bad arphew tylli ki thliew tnaw jong ki da ka tama; ki bnoh jong kita ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki da ka rupa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ïa ka pyngkiang ka phyllaw shaphang sepngi kin long ki pyrda, sanphew pruh; ki rishot jong ki shiphew, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki shiphew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka pyngkiang ka phyllaw ha ka liang shaphang mihngi kan long sanphew pruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki pyrda jong kawei ka liang kin long khatsan pruh: ki rishot jong ki, lai, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki, lai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ha kawei pat ka liang ruh kin long ki pyrda, khatsan pruh; ki rishot jong ki, lai tylli, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki, lai tylli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ïa ka khyrdop ka phyllaw te kan long ka pyrda, arphew pruh, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la jyrthiaw, ba la suh ruh; ki rishot jong ki, saw tylli, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki, saw tylli.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ïa ki rishot baroh sawdong jong ka phyllaw yn thaw shrong da ka rupa; ki bnoh jong ki yn long da ka rupa, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki da ka tama.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka lynter kata ka phyllaw kan long shispah pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, sanphew sanphew, ka jingjrong ruh, san pruh, da ka linen bani ba la jyrthiaw, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki da ka tama.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Baroh ki pliang jong Ka Tabernakl ha ka jingleh kam jong ka baroh, bad ki prek jong ka baroh ruh, bad ki snar baroh jong ka phyllaw, kin long da ka tama.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Bad men hukum ïa ki khun Israel, ba kin wallam ha me ka umphniang Olib ba la tylliat, ka bakhuid ïa ka jingshai, ïa ka ban pynmeh ïa kata ka sharak khlem da pud.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, shabar kata ka jingkah kaba ha khmat ka jingphla, u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin ïasumar ïa ka naduh mynmiet haduh mynstep ha khmat U Trai; kane kan long ka hukum ha la ka rta ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki na ka bynta ki khun Israel."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Bad to shim ha me ïa u Aaron u hynmen jong me, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u lem bad u, napdeng ki khun Israel, ïa ka ban kam ïa ka kam lyngdoh ïa nga, ïa u Aaron keiñ, ïa u Nadab, bad ïa u Abihu, ïa u Eleasar bad ïa u Ithamar, ki khun shynrang jong u Aaron.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Men thaw ruh ïa ki jaiñkup bakyntang ïa u Aaron u hynmen jong me, na ka bynta ka burom bad na ka bynta ka jingitynnad.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Men kren ruh ha kita baroh kat ki bastad ka dohnud, ïa kiba nga la pyndap da ka mynsiem ka jingstad, ba kin ïathain ïa ki jaiñkup ïa u Aaron ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa u, ban kam ïa ka kam lyngdoh ïa nga.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kine ki long kita ki jaiñkup ba kin ïathain; ïa ka jingdeng shadem, bad ïa ka ephod, bad ïa ka barandi, bad ïa ka sopti ba la pynpur, ïa ka meitr, bad ïa ka jingpanpoh ruh: kumta keiñ, kin ïathaw ïa ki jaiñkup bakyntang ïa u Aaron u hynmen jong me, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, ïa ka ban kam ïa ka kam lyngdoh ïa nga.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Kin shim te ïa ka ksiar, bad ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kin thaw ïa ka ephod da ka ksiar, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir da ka jingtrei bastad.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kan don ar tylli ki tyrpeng ba la pynïasoh ha ki baroh ar ki rmiang jong ka; kumta te, yn pynïasoh lang ïa ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kata ka jingpanpoh ba la pynpur jong ka ephod kaba halor jong ka, kan long da kajuh, ba la thaw da kajuh hi keiñ; da ka ksiar keiñ, ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To men shim ruh ar tylli ki mawlynnai Oniks, bad to pruid halor jong ki ruh ïa ki kyrteng ki khun Israel;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynriew na ki kyrteng jong ki ha uwei u maw bad hynriew ki kyrteng jong kiwei pat ha uwei pat u maw, katba kum ka jingkha jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Da ka jingtrei u nongpruid ha u maw, kum ki jingpruid ka mohor keiñ, men pruid ha kita ki ar tylli ki maw ïa ki kyrteng ki khun Israel: men thaw ïa ki ban buh ha ki shrong ka ksiar.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Men buh ruh ïa kita ki ar tylli ki maw ha ki tyrpeng ka ephod, kum ka jingpynkynmaw ïa ki khun Israel: bad u Aaron un bah ïa ki kyrteng jong ki ha khmat U Trai halor baroh ar ki tyrpeng jong u kum ka jingpynkynmaw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To men thaw ruh ïa ki shrong ksiar,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ar tylli ki kynjri ha ki tduh jong ki da ka ksiar banylla; na kaba la thain men thaw ïa ki; bad to pynïasoh ruh ïa kita ki kynjri ba la thain ha kita ki shrong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “To men thaw ruh ïa ka jingdeng shadem ka jingbishar, da ka jingtrei bastad; kum ka rukom jong ka ephod men thaw ïa ka, da ka ksiar, ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir, men thaw ïa ka keiñ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kan long kaba sawdong bad kaba ar syrtap; ka lynter jong ka, shi tda; bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, shi tda.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad men thep ha ka ïa ki mawlynnai, saw kyrdan ki maw keiñ: ka kyrdan kaba da u Sardios, u Topas, bad u Karbunkl, kan long ka kyrdan ka banyngkong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka kyrdan ka ba-ar, da u Emerald, u Sapphir, bad u Diamond.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka kyrdan ka balai, u Ligur, u Agate, bad u Amethyst.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka kyrdan ka basaw, u Beryl, bad u Oniks, bad u Jasper; yn thep ïa ki ha ka ksiar ha ki jaka ker jong ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ha kita ki maw kin don ki kyrteng ki khun Israel, khat-ar keiñ, kat kum ki kyrteng jong ki; kum kaba pruid jong ka mohor, uwei pa uwei baroh bad la ka kyrteng kyrteng, kat kum ki khat-ar ki jaid.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad halor kata ka jingdeng shadem, men thaw ïa ki kynjri ba la thain, da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> To men thaw ruh halor kata ka jingdeng shadem, ar tylli ki kyrwoh da ka ksiar; bad to pynïasoh ruh ïa kita ki kyrwoh ha ki ar dong jong kata ka jingdeng shadem.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad men woh ïa kita ki ar tylli ki kynjri ksiar ba la thain ha kita ki ar tylli ki kyrwoh kiba ha ki dong kata ka jingdeng shadem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ïa kita kiwei ki ar tylli ki tduh jong kita ar tylli ki kynjri ba la thain, men pynsnoh ha kita ar tylli ki shrong, bad men buh ïa ki halor ki tyrpeng jong ka ephod na khmat.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Men thaw ruh ar tylli ki kyrwoh da ka ksiar, bad men buh ruh ïa ki ha ki ar dong ka jingdeng shadem, ha ka rmiang jong ka, kaba ha kata ka liang jong ka ephod kaba shapoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad men thaw sa ar tylli ki kyrwoh da ka ksiar, bad men buh ïa ki ha ki ar liang kata ka ephod na sharum, shaphang khmat jong ka, ha marpyrshah ïa kawei ka syrtap jong ka, shaneng kata ka jingpanpoh ba la pynpur jong ka ephod.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad da u ksai babyrïong, kin teh ïa kata ka jingdeng shadem na ki kyrwoh jong ka ha ki kyrwoh jong kata ka ephod, ba kan ïoh long shaneng kata ka jingpanpoh ba la pynpur jong kata ka ephod, bad ba kata ka jingdeng shadem kan ym lait shuh na ka ephod.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Aaron ruh un bah ha kata ka jingdeng shadem ka jingbishar, ïa ki kyrteng ki khun Israel halor la ka shyllipnud, haba u leit bsut shapoh kata ka jaka kyntang, kum ka jingpynkynmaw ha khmat U Trai ha la ka sngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Men buh ruh ha kata ka jingdeng shadem ka jingbishar, ïa kita ki Urim bad ïa kita ki Thummim; bad kin ïalong halor ka shyllipnud u Aaron, haba u leit bsut shapoh ha khmat U Trai; bad u Aaron un bah ïa ka jingbishar ki khun Israel halor la ka shyllipnud ha khmat U Trai ha la ka sngi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka barandi jong kata ka ephod baroh da ka babyrïong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad men pong ryndang ïa ka, na marpdeng jong ka: to kyntang baroh sawdong ka thliew jong ka, kum ka thliew jong ka jymphong kieng, ba kan ym kad keiñ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ha ka rmiang jong ka men thaw ïa ki soh Pong da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, baroh sawdong na ka rmiang jong ka; bad ïa ki shakuriaw da ka ksiar hapdeng jong ki baroh sawdong,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> ka shakuriaw ksiar bad u soh Pong, bad ka shakuriaw ksiar bad u syntiew soh Pong, ha ka rmiang kata ka barandi baroh sawdong.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Aaron un phong ïa ka haba u shakri: bad ba yn ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa jong u haba u leit bsut sha kata ka jaka kyntang ha khmat U Trai, bad haba u mih noh, ba um ïap noh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Men thaw ruh ïa ka sla da ka ksiar banylla, bad men pruid ha ka, kum ki jingpruid jong ka mohor, ‘Ka jingkhuid ha U Trai.’",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad men teh ïa ka da u ksai babyrïong, ba kan long halor kata ka meitr, sha khmat kata ka meitr kan long keiñ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kan long te ha ka shyllangmat u Aaron, ba u Aaron un bah ïa ka pop jong kita kiei kiei ruh ki bakhuid, ïa kiba ki khun Israel kin pynkyntang ha ki jingai bakyntang jong ki baroh; bad kan long ha la ka sngi ha ka shyllangmat jong u, ba yn ïoh pdiang ïa ki ha khmat U Trai.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “To men pynpur ïa ka sopti da ka linen bani, bad to men thaw ïa ka meitr ruh da ka linen bani, bad ïa ka jingpanpoh ruh to men thaw da kaba suh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> “Ïa ki khun shynrang u Aaron ruh men thaw ïa ki sopti, ïa ki jingpanpoh ruh men thaw ïa ki, bad ïa ki tupia men thaw ïa ki, na ka bynta ka burom bad ka jingitynnad.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> To men pynphong ruh ïa ki ha u Aaron u hynmen jong me, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u lem bad u; bad men pynsleh ïa ki, bad men pynkyntang ïa ki, bad men pynkhuid ïa ki de, ba kin ïoh kam ha nga ha ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Men thaw ïa ki, ïa ki patlun linen ban tap ïa ka jinglyngkhuit jong ki; kin kot ruh naduh ka syngkai haduh ki lbong;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad u Aaron un phong ïa ki, bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin phong ïa ki, haba ki leit bsut hapoh Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, lane haba ki wan hajan ka duwan ïa ka ban shakri ha kata ka jaka kyntang ba kin ym kit pop bad ïap noh: kane kan long ka hukum ïa u bad ïa u symbai jong u hadien jong u ha la ka rta."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Kumne te men leh ïa ki, ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa ki, ïa ka ban kam ha nga ha ka kam lyngdoh: To shim uwei u masi lyngraw bad ar tylli ki langbrot shynrang bajanai,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> lem bad u kpu bakhlem thiat, bad ki 'pu stang ruh bakhlem thiat ba la ïakhleh da ka umphniang, bad ki 'putharo bakhlem thiat ba la kyllan da ka umphniang; da u 'pu Kew keiñ men thaw ïa ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Men thep ïa ki ruh ha kawei ka shang, bad to wallam ïa ki ha kata ka shang, lem bad uta u masi lyngraw bad kita ki ar tylli ki langbrot shynrang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> To ïalam ruh ïa u Aaron bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad to men sait ïa ki da ka um.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad men shim ïa kita ki jaiñkup, bad pynphong ha u Aaron ïa kata ka sopti, bad ïa kata ka barandi jong ka ephod, bad ïa kata ka ephod, bad ïa kata ka jingdeng shadem, bad to pynpanpoh ïa u da ka jingpanpoh ba la pynpur jong ka ephod;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad men pynphong ïa kata ka meitr ha ka khlieh jong u, bad to buh ruh ïa kata ka pansngiat bakhuid halor kata ka meitr.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, men shim ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad to theh ïa ka ruh halor ka khlieh jong u, bad pynsleh ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad men wallam ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad men pynphong ki sopti ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad men pynpanpoh ïa ki da ki jingpanpoh, ïa u Aaron keiñ bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad men pynphong ïa ki da kita ki tupia: bad kata ka kam lyngdoh ruh kan ïailong ka jong ki da ka hukum pateng la pateng: bad men pynkyntang ruh ïa u Aaron bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Bad men phah lam ïa uta u masi lyngraw ha khmat Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng: bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin ïabuh ïa la ki kti halor ka khlieh jong uta u masi lyngraw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To men pynïap te ïa uta u masi lyngraw ha khmat U Trai, hajan ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To men shim de na ka snam uta u masi lyngraw, bad to buh ïa ka ha ki reng jong ka duwan da ka shynriah'ti jong me; bad to theh ïa kata ka snam baroh ha syndah ka trai kata ka duwan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad men shim ïa ka khleiñ baroh de kaba tap ïa ki snier, bad ïa ka sbiar kaba haneng u dohnud, bad ïa ki khyllai baroh ar, bad ïa ka khleiñ kaba halor jong ki, bad to thang ïa ki halor kata ka duwan.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ïa ka doh uta u masi lyngraw, bad ïa ka snieh jong u de, bad ïa ka eit jong u, men thang ha ka ding shabar ka dara: ka long ka jingkñia namar ka pop.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “To men shim ruh ïa uwei u langbrot; bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin ïabuh ïa la ki kti halor ka khlieh uta u langbrot,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad men pynïap ïa uta u langbrot, bad men shim ruh ïa ka snam jong u, bad to synreit ïa ka halor kata ka duwan baroh sawdong.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad men ot lyngkhot lyngkhot ïa uta u langbrot, to sait ruh ïa ki snier jong u, bad ïa ki kjat jong u, bad to buh ïa ki ruh lem bad kita ki dkhot jong u, bad ka khlieh jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Men thang ruh ïa uta u langbrot baroh halor kata ka duwan: ka long ka jingainguh thang ïa U Trai: ka long ka jingiw baiwbih, ka jingainguh keiñ kaba da ka ding ha U Trai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Men shim ruh ïa uta uwei pat u langbrot; bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin ïabuh ïa la ki kti halor ka khlieh uta u langbrot;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hadien kata, men pynïap ïa uta u langbrot, bad men shim na ka snam jong u, bad tah halor ka sohlah shkor kamon jong u Aaron, bad halor ka sohlah shkor kamon ki khun shynrang jong u, bad halor ka 'ti kmie ka kti kamon jong ki, bad halor ka 'jat kmie ka sla'jat kamon jong ki, bad to synreit ïa ka snam baroh sawdong halor kata ka duwan.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad men shim na kata ka snam kaba halor kata ka duwan, bad na kata ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad to synreit halor u Aaron, bad halor ki jaiñkup jong u, bad halor ki khun shynrang jong u, bad halor ki jaiñkup ki khun shynrang jong u lem bad u; kumta keiñ, yn pynkyntang khuid ïa u, bad ïa ki jaiñkup jong u, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad ïa ki jaiñkup ki khun shynrang jong u lem bad u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Bad na uta u langbrot ruh men shim ïa ka khleiñ, bad ïa ka dongnai, bad ïa ka khleiñ kaba tap ïa ki snier ruh, bad ïa ka sbiar kaba haneng u dohnud, bad ïa ki khyllai baroh ar, bad ïa ka khleiñ ruh kaba halor jong ki, bad ïa ka kti kamon de; namar u long u langbrot ka jingpynkyntang keiñ,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad ïa uwei u kpu, bad ïa uwei u 'pu stang ba la khleh umphniang, bad ïa uwei u 'putharo na kata ka shi shang u kpu bakhlem thiat uba ha khmat U Trai,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> te men buh ïa kita baroh ha ki kti u Aaron, bad ha ki kti ki khun shynrang jong u; bad men pynkaweh ïa ki ban long ka jingainguh kaweh ha khmat U Trai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad men shim ïa ki na ki kti jong ki, bad to thang ïa ki halor kata ka duwan ïa ka ban long ka jingainguh thang, ka jingiw baiwbih keiñ ha khmat U Trai: ka long keiñ ka jingainguh kaba da ka ding ha U Trai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Bad men shim ïa ka shadem uta u langbrot ka jingpynkyntang jong u Aaron, bad to kaweh ïa ka, ïa ka ban long ka jingainguh kaweh ha khmat U Trai: bad kata kan long ka bynta jong me.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Men pynkyntang ruh ïa kata ka shadem jong ka jingainguh kaweh, bad ïa kata ka kti jong kata ka jingainguh bakyntiew, ïa kaba la kaweh, bad ïa kaba la pynkyntiew, na ka jong uta u langbrot ka jingpynkyntang, na kata keiñ kaba na ka bynta u Aaron, bad na kata kaba na ka bynta ki khun shynrang jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kan long ruh ka jong u Aaron bad ka jong ki khun shynrang jong u da ka hukum ha la ka rta na ki khun Israel: naba ka long ka jingainguh bakyntiew; bad kan long ruh ka jingainguh bakyntiew na ki khun Israel kaba na ki jingkñia ki jingainguh bapynïasuk jong ki, kata ka long ka jingainguh bakyntiew jong ki ha U Trai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Bad kita ki jaiñ bakyntang jong u Aaron kin long ki jong ki khun shynrang jong u hadien jong u, ha kita yn pynsleh ïa ki, bad ha kita yn pynkyntang ruh ïa ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad uta u khun jong u uba long u lyngdoh ha ka jaka jong u un phong ïa kita hynñiew sngi, haba u wan ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ïa ka ban shakri ha kata ka jaka bakyntang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Men shim ruh ïa uta u langbrot ka jingpynkyntang, bad to shet ïa ka doh jong u ha kata ka jaka bakyntang.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin ïabam ïa ka doh jong uta u langbrot, bad ïa uta u kpu uba ha kata ka shang, hajan ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad kin ïabam ïa kita kiei kiei ruh da kiba la pynlong ïa ka kuna, ïa ka ban pynkyntang bad ban pynkhuid ïa ki: hynrei, u nongwei un ym ïoh bam na kita, naba ki long ki bakyntang khuid.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te lada don kaei kaei ruh na ka doh jong kita ki jingpynkyntang, lane na uta u kpu, kiba sah haduh mynstep, men thang ïa kata kaba sah ha ka ding: yn ym bam ïa ka, naba ka long ka bakyntang khuid.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Kumne te, to leh ha u Aaron, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong u, kat kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba nga la hukum ïa me: hynñiew sngi men pynkyntang ïa ki.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad men kñia ha la ka sngi ïa uwei u masi lyngraw ïa ka ban long ka kuna namar ka pop ïa ka ban pynïasuk: bad men pynkhuid ruh ïa kata ka duwan, ynda me la pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta jong ka; bad to pynsleh ïa ka, ïa ka ban pynkyntang ïa ka.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynñiew sngi men pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta kata ka duwan, bad men pynkyntang ïa ka: te kan long ka duwan ba la kyntang tam eh: kaei kaei baroh ba pyndei ïa kata ka duwan kan long bakyntang.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Te ïa kane to men ainguh halor kata ka duwan; ïa ar tylli ki khun langbrot kiba shi snem man la ka sngi khlem da pud.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ïa uwei u khun langbrot men ainguh mynstep, bad ïa uwei pat men ainguh la janmiet:",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> lem bad uwei u khun langbrot ruh men ïakhleh shi bynta na kaba shiphew ephah u 'purew, lem bad shi pawa hin ka umphniang ba la tylliat; bad shi pawa hin ka Waiñ ruh ban long ka jingainguh dih.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad ïa uta uwei pat u khun langbrot men ainguh la janmiet, men leh ha u ruh kumba ha kata ka jingainguh bam kaba mynstep, bad katba kum ka jingainguh dih jong ka, ïa ka ban long ka jingiw baiwbih, ka jingainguh kaba da ka ding keiñ ha U Trai.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kane kan long ka jingainguh thang ha la ka sngi ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi baroh hajan ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ha khmat U Trai: ha kaba ngan ïashem bad phi, ïa ka ban kren hangta ha me.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hangta ruh, ngan ïashem bad ki khun Israel; ïa Ka Tabernakl de yn pynkyntang khuid da ka burom jong nga.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ngan pynkyntang ruh ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ïa kata ka duwan: bad ngan pynkyntang ïa u Aaron bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, ba kin kam ha nga ha ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ngan shong duh ruh hapdeng ki khun Israel, bad ngan long U Blei jong ki.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kin sa tip ruh ba nga long ma nga, U Trai U Blei jong ki, uba la wallam noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt, ba ngan ïoh shong duh hapdeng jong ki; nga long ma nga keiñ, U Trai U Blei jong ki."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “To men thaw ïa ka duwan ïa ka ban thang ïa ka jingiwbih thang: da u dieng Shittim keiñ men thaw ïa ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Shi pruh, kan long ka lynter jong ka, bad shi pruh, ka pyngkiang jong ka; kaba sawdong kan long: ka jingjrong jong ka, ar pruh: ki reng jong ka na ujuh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad men suit ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla, ïa ka neng jong ka, bad ïa ki krung jong ka baroh sawdong, bad ïa ki reng jong ka ruh; bad men thaw ïa ka pansngiat ksiar ïa ka baroh sawdong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Men thaw ruh ar tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar ïa ka hapoh kata ka pansngiat jong ka, ha ki ar tylli ki dong jong ka, ha baroh ar ki krung jong ka men thaw keiñ ïa ki; te kin long ki jaka ïa ki dieng jingbah ïa ka ban bah ïa ka da ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad men thaw ruh ïa kita ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad men suit ïa ki da ka ksiar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad men buh ïa ka ha khmat kata ka jingkah kaba hajan ka synduk ka jingphla, ha khmat kata ka jingtap-isynei kaba halor kata ka jingphla, ha kaba ngan ïashem bad me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Aaron un thang halor jong ka, ïa ka jingiwbih thang da ki musla man ka step: haba u shna ïa ki sharak, un thang ïa ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ka,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad haba u Aaron u tbeh ïa kita ki sharak la janmiet ruh, un thang ïa ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ka, ka jingiwbih thang keiñ kaba ha la ka sngi ha khmat U Trai ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wat thang halor jong ka, ïa ka jingiwbih thang bapher, lymne ïa ka jingkñia thang, lymne ïa ka jingainguh bam; lymne wat theh phi halor jong ka, ïa ka jingainguh dih.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Aaron un pynlong ïa ka jingkñia bapynïasuk halor ki reng jong ka, shi sien shi snem: da ka snam kata ka jingkñia sait pop bapynïasuk, shi sien shi snem keiñ, un pynlong ïa ka kuna halor jong ka ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi: ka long ka bakyntang tam ïa U Trai.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u ong,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Haba me ñiew ïa kita kiba dei ban ñiew na ki khun Israel, te kin sa ai uwei baroh na ka bynta la ka mynsiem ïa ka kuna ha U Trai, haba me ñiew keiñ ïa ki; ba kan ym long ka jingïapthem hapdeng jong ki, haba me ñiew ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ïa kane kin sa ai, uwei uwei baroh hapdeng jong kita ba la hap ñiew, shiteng shekel katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang: (ka shekel ka long arphew gerah) ka shiteng shekel kan long kata ka jingainguh ïa U Trai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uwei uwei baroh uba la hap ñiew hapdeng jong ki, naduh uba arphew snem ka rta bad ba tam, un ai ïa ka jingainguh ïa U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U bariewspah un ym ai tam, bad u baduk un ym ai duna ïa kata ka shiteng shekel, haba ki ai ka jingainguh ïa U Trai, ïa ka ban pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta ki mynsiem jong phi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad men shim ïa kita ki sbai kuna na ki khun Israel, bad men buh ïa ki na ka bynta ka kam Ka Tabernakl jong ka jingïaseng; khnang ba kan long ka jingpynkynmaw ïa ki khun Israel ha khmat U Trai, ïa ka ban pynlong ïa ka kuna na ka bynta ki mynsiem jong phi.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “To men thaw ruh ïa ka dabor tama, bad ïa ka sla'jat jong ka ruh da ka tama, ïa ka ban sait ha ka: bad men buh ïa ka hapdeng Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng bad kata ka duwan, bad men theh um ruh ha ka,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u kin thet ïa la ki kti bad sait ïa la ki sla'jat ha ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Haba kin sa leit rung hapoh Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, kin sait da ka um, ba kin ym ïap; lane haba ki wan hajan ka duwan ïa ka ban kam, ban thang ïa ka jingkñia thang ha U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta kin thet keiñ ïa la ki kti bad sait ïa la ki sla'jat, ba kin ym ïap noh: kane te kan long ka hukum ha la ka rta ïa ki; ïa u keiñ bad ïa u symbai jong u ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Trai u la kren pat ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “To shim ruh ha me ïa ki jingiwbih bakordor, na ka mirr basngur, sanspah shekel; bad na ka sisia bathiang, shiteng na kata, arspah sanphew shekel keiñ; bad na ka kalamis bathiang, arspah sanphew shekel;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad na ka kassia, sanspah shekel; katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang, bad na ka umphniang Olib, shi hin;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad men thaw da ki, ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh bakhuid, ïa ka umphniang ba la ïakhleh keiñ kum ka rukom u apothekari: kan long ka umphniang bakhuid ïa ka ban pynsleh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Men pynsleh ruh da ka, ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ïa ka synduk ka jingphla,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ïa ka miej ruh bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka duwan ka jingiwbih thang de,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ïa kata ka duwan ka jingainguh thang ruh lem bad ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka dabor bad ïa ka sla'jat jong ka;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> to men pynkyntang ïa ki de, ba kin ïoh long ki bakyntang tam: baroh kat kaba pyndei ïa ki, kan long ka bakyntang keiñ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad men pynsleh ruh ïa u Aaron bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad men pynkyntang ïa ki, ba kin ïoh kam ha nga ha ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Men kren te ha ki khun Israel, da kaba ong, ‘Kane kan long ha nga ka umphniang bakhuid ïa ka ban pynsleh ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Wat pynsleh da ka, ïa ka met u briew, lymne ha ka rukom jingkhleh jong ka wat thaw da kawei pat kaba syriem ïa ka: ka long ka bakyntang, bad kan long ka bakyntang keiñ ha phi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Jar uba khleh ïa kaba kum kane, lane jar uba buh na ka ha u nongwei, yn ot noh keiñ ïa uta napdeng u paidlang jong u.’ ”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> U Trai u la kren ruh ha u Moses, “To shim ha me ïa ki jingiwbih bathiang, ïa ka stakte, bad ïa ka onikha bad ïa ka galbanam; ïa kine ki musla bathiang lem bad ka luban: na kawei kawei men shim kumjuh.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad men thaw da ki, ïa ka jingiwbih thang, ka jingiwbih keiñ kum ka rukom u apothekari, ïa kaba la ïakhleh mluh, ka bakhuid bad ka bakyntang;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad men shoh lwet eh khyndiat na ka, bad men buh ïa ka ha khmat ka jingphla ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ha kaba ngan ïashem bad me: kan long ha phi ka bakyntang tam eh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te kata ka jingiwbih thang ïa kaba phin thaw, wat thaw ïa lade keiñ kum kata ka rukom jong ka; kan long ïa phi ka bakyntang ïa U Trai.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Jar u ban thaw ïa kum kata, ïa ka ban iw ïa ka, yn ot noh ïa uta napdeng u paidlang jong u.”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ha khmih, nga la khot da ka kyrteng ïa u Besalil u khun u Uri, u khun u Hur, na ka jaid Judah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad nga la pyndap ïa u da U Mynsiem U Blei, ha ka jingstad, bad ha ka jingshemphang, bad ha ka jingtip, bad ha ki kynja jingtrei baroh,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ïa ka ban pyrkhat ïa ki kam bastad, ïa ka ban trei ha ka ksiar, bad ha ka rupa ruh, bad ha ka tama de,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ha ka buit stad ban shtah ïa ki maw ban thep ïa ki, bad ha kaba mut ha ki dieng ïa ka ban trei ha ka kynja jingtrei baroh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha khmih te, ma nga, nga la ai lem bad u ïa u Aholiab, u khun u Ahisamakh, na ka jaid Dan; bad ha ka dohnud jong kita ki bastad dohnud baroh nga la buh ïa ka jingstad, ïa ka ban thaw ïa kita baroh ïa kiba nga la hukum ïa me:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ïa ka synduk ka jingphla, bad ïa ka jingtap-isynei kaba halor jong ka, bad ïa ki jingbuh Ka Tabernakl baroh,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ïa ka miej ruh bad ïa ki jingbuh jong ka, bad ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak bakhuid lem bad ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka duwan ka jingiwbih thang ruh,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang lem bad ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka dabor bad ïa ka sla'jat jong ka,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ïa ki jaiñ ïa ka kam, bad ïa ki jaiñkup bakyntang ïa u Aaron lyngdoh, bad ïa ki jaiñkup ki khun shynrang jong u, ïa ka ban kam ha ka kam lyngdoh;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang baiwbih ïa ka jaka kyntang: kin leh ïa kita baroh keiñ kat kumba nga la hukum ïa me.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “To kren ruh ha ki khun Israel, da kaba ong, ‘Shisha phin rakhe ïa ki Sabbaton jong nga: naba ka long ka dak hapdeng jong nga bad phi ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong phi baroh; ïa ka ban ïoh tip ba long ma nga U Trai uba pynkyntang ïa phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, to sumar ïa ka Sabbaton; naba ka long ka bakhuid ïa phi: jar uba pyntngit ïa ka, ka dei shisha ban pynïap noh ïa u; naba uno uno ruh uba trei jingtrei ha ka, ïa kata ka mynsiem yn ot noh keiñ napdeng u paidlang jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynriew sngi ka dei ban trei jingtrei; hynrei, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew ka long ka Sabbaton ka jingshongthait, ka bakhuid ïa U Trai: jar uba trei jingtrei ha ka sngi Sabbaton, yn pynïap noh shisha ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar kata, ki khun Israel kin ïasumar ïa ka Sabbaton, da kaba rakhe ïa ka Sabbaton ha ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki, kum ka jutang ha la ka rta.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hapdeng jong nga bad ki khun Israel, kane ka long ka dak ha la ka rta: ba ha ka bahynriew sngi, U Trai u la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew, bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew u la shong sngi, bad u la shong pyngngad.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda U la wai noh ban kren ha u Moses ha u lum Sinai, U la ai ha u ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap jong ka jingphla, ki maw lyngkniap ba la thoh keiñ da ka shynriah'ti U Blei."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba uta u paidlang u la ïohi ba u Moses u tud ban wan hiar na uta u lum, uta u paidlang u la ïalum lang ha u Aaron, bad u la ong ha u, “To ïeng, to thaw blei ïa ngi, ban leit sha shuwa jong ngi; naba une u Moses, uta u briew keiñ uba la wallam artet ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, ngim tip shuh la jia aïu ïa u.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Aaron u la ong ha ki, “To law noh ïa ki jingdeng ksiar kiba ha ki shkor ki tnga jong phi, bad ïa ki jong ki khun shynrang jong phi, bad ïa ki jong ki khun kynthei jong phi, bad to wallam ïa ki ha nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te uta u paidlang baroh u la ïalaw noh ïa kita ki jingdeng ksiar kiba ha ki shkor jong ki, bad ki la ïawallam ha u Aaron.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haba u la pdiang te ïa ki na ki kti jong ki, u la pynlong dur da ka atiar, bad u la thaw khun masi da kaba shu saiñ: ki la ïa-ong te, “Une u long u blei jong me, A Israel, uba la wallam artet ïa me na ka ri Ijipt.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u Aaron u la ïohi ïa kane, u la tei ïa ka duwan ha khmat jong u: bad u Aaron u la pynbna, u da ong, “Lashai kan long ka jingkhawai ha U Trai.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te la dang step ki la ïakhie, bad ki la kñia ïa ki jingkñia thang, bad ki la ïawallam ïa ki jingkñia bapynïasuk; ynda kumta, kita ki paidlang ki la ïashong ban bam bad ban dih, bad ki la ïaïeng joit ban ïalehkai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To khie leit da hiar noh; naba uta u paidbah jong me, ïa uba me la wallam noh artet na ka ri Ijipt, u la pynsniew ïa lade;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ki la ïaid sakma noh kloi na kata ka lynti ïa kaba nga la hukum ïa ki: ki la ïathaw dur khun masi ba la shu saiñ ha ki, bad ki la ïamane ïa u, ki la ai jingkñia ruh ha uta, bad ki la ïa-ong, ‘Une u blei jong me, A Israel, uba la wallam noh artet ïa me na ka ri Ijipt.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ruh ha u Moses, “Nga la ïohi ïa une u paidlang, bad ha khmih, u long u paidlang uba eh ryndang;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, to iehnoh ïa nga mynta, ba ka jingbitar jong nga kan ïoh meh buk pyrshah ïa ki, bad ba ngan ïoh pynduh noh khoit ïa ki: bad ngan pynlong ïa me ïa ka jaid bynriew bakhraw.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Moses u la kyrpad ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong u, u da ong, “A Trai, balei ba ka jingbitar jong me kan meh buk pyrshah ïa u paidlang jong me, ïa uba me la wallam noh na ka ri Ijipt da ka borbah bad da ka kti badonbor?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Balei ba kita ki Ijipt kin ïoh kren, da kaba ong, ‘Khnang ïa ka ban tyllep u la ïalam noh ïa ki, ban pynïap ïa ki ha ki lum, bad ban pynjot noh khoit keiñ ïa ki na khmat ka pyrthei?’ To phai noh na ka jingbitar ba-itieng jong me, to kylla noh ruh na kane ka basniew pyrshah ïa u paidlang jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To kynmaw ïa la ki shakri, ïa u Abraham, ïa u Isaak, bad ïa u Israel, ha kiba me la smai da lade hi, bad me la ong ha ki, ‘Ngan pynroi ïa u symbai jong phi kat ki khlur ka bneng, bad ïa kane ka ri baroh shaphang kaba nga la kren, ngan ai ha u symbai jong phi, bad kin ïaïoh pateng ïa ka ha la ka rta.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda kumta, U Trai u la kylla noh na kata ka basniew ïa kaba u la thmu ban leh ha u paidlang jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Moses u la phai, bad u la leit hiar arsut na uta u lum, bad kita ki ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap jong ka jingphla ha ka kti jong u; kine ki maw lyngkniap ïa kiba la thoh halor baroh ar liang jong ki; halor baroh ar liang keiñ, la thoh ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kita ki maw lyngkniap ki la long ka jingthaw jong U Blei, bad ka jingthoh ruh ka la long ka jingthoh jong U Blei, ïa kaba la mut halor kita ki maw lyngkniap.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u Joshua u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa uta u paidbah katba ki ïarisa kynha, u la ong ha u Moses, “Don ka jingsawa kum ka thma ha kata ka dara.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong, “Kata kam long ka jingsawa kiba ïarisa na ka bynta kaba jop, lymne kam long ka jinglynñiar kiba ïashah jop; hynrei, ïa ka jingsawa kiba ïarwai ba nga ïohsngew keiñ.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka la jia te, katba u la wan hajan ka jaka shong dara, u la ïohi ïa uta u khun masi bad ïa kata ka jingshad; te ka jingbitar u Moses ka la khie buk, bad u la bred noh dak ïa kita ki maw lyngkniap na ka kti jong u, bad u la lympat ïa ki ha trai uta u lum.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Moses u la shim ïa uta u khun masi ïa uba ki la thaw, bad u la saiñ ïa u ha ka ding, bad u la pynlwet jin ïa u, bad u la ber ïa ka ruh halor ka um, bad u la pyndih ïa ki khun Israel na ka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Moses u la kylli ïa u Aaron, “U la leh aïu une u paidbah ïa me, ba me la wallam ïa ka pop bakhraw kat kane halor jong ki?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Aaron u la ïathuh, “Wat ai ba kan meh buk ka jingbitar u kynrad jong nga: me ithuh ïa une u paidlang, ba u dap keiñ da ka basniew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar ki la ïa-ong ha nga, ‘To thaw blei ïa ngi, ba un leit ha shuwa jong ngi: naba une u Moses, uta u briew uba la wallam noh artet ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, ngim tip shuh la jia aïu ïa u.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te nga la ong ha ki, ‘Jar uba don ka ksiar, to law noh;’ kumta keiñ ki la ïa-ai ha nga: bad nga la bred te ïa ka ha ka ding, te la mih noh da une u khun masi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba u Moses u la ïohi ïa uta u paidbah ba ki lyngkhuit, naba u Aaron u la lah pynlyngkhuit ïa ki, ïa ka ban pynjahburom ïa ki hapdeng ki nongshun jong ki,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> kumta, u Moses u la ïeng ha ka khyrdop ka jaka shong dara, bad u la ong, “Jar uba ha ka liang U Trai, to un wan ha nga.” Te ki khun shynrang jong u Lebi baroh ki la ïalum lang ha u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei jong u Israel, ‘To kieng u shynrang baroh ïa la ka waitlam ha la ka syngkai, bad to khie ruh shapoh bad shabar na kawei ka khyrdop sha kawei pat ka khyrdop jong kata ka dara, bad to pynïap noh ruh man u briew ïa la u para, bad man u briew ïa la u lok, bad man u briew ïa la u paramarjan.’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Lebi ki la leh kumba u la ong u Moses: te ha kata ka sngi la kyllon ïap na uta u paidbah kumba lai hajar ki rangbah.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Moses u la ong, “To pynkyntang ïa lade ha kane ka sngi ha U Trai, u briew baroh keiñ pyrshah ïa la u khun, bad pyrshah ïa la u para; ba ha kane ka sngi un ïoh ai ka jingkyrkhu halor jong phi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, u Moses u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Phi la leh ïa ka pop kaba khraw eh: mynta te ngan sa leit kiew sha U Trai; lehse nga lah ban pynlong ïa ka jingpynïasuk namar ka pop jong phi.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la leit phai sha U Trai, bad u la ong, “A, une u paidlang u la leh ïa ka pop ka bakhraw eh, bad ki la ïathaw blei da ka ksiar ha ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hynrei mynta, lada men map ïa ka pop jong ki — te lada da kumwei, to pyndam noh ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, na kata ka kitab jong me ïa kaba me la thoh.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Jar uba la leh pop pyrshah ïa nga, ïa uta keiñ ngan pyndam noh na ka kitab jong nga.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Namar kata, to khie leit mynta, to ïalam ma me ïa uta u paidbah sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba nga la ong ha me; ha khmih, u angel jong nga un ïaid ha shuwa jong me: hynrei, ha kata ka sngi ba ngan da wan khmih, ngan pynwan keiñ ïa ka pop jong ki halor jong ki hi.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te U Trai u la pynïapthem ïa uta u paidbah, namar ba ki la ïathaw ïa uta u khun masi, ïa uba u Aaron u la thaw."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To ïeng, to leit noh nangne, ma me bad uta u paidlang ïa uba me la wallam artet na ka ri Ijipt, sha kata ka ri ïa kaba nga la smai ha u Abraham, ha u Isaak, bad ha u Jakob, da kaba ong, ‘Ha u symbai jong me ngan ai ïa ka.’",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ngan phah ïa u angel jong nga ha shuwa jong me; bad ngan beh noh ma nga ïa ki Kanaan, ïa ki Amor, bad ïa ki Hit, bad ïa ki Peris, ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Jebus:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sha ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud bad ka ngap; namar nga, ngan ym leit kiew ryngkat hapdeng jong me; naba me u paidlang ba-eh ryndang; ba ïoh ngan pynduh noh khoit ïa me ha kata ka lynti.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba uta u paidlang u la ïohsngew ïa kine ki khubor basniew, ki la leh sngewsih: bad ym don shuh mano mano ruh ba deng ïa la ki jingdeng.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To ïathuh ha ki khun Israel, ‘Phi long u paidlang ba-eh ryndang; lada ngan wan kiew keiñ hapdeng jong me, shisyndon ngan pynduh noh khoit ïa me: namar kata, to law noh bak ïa la ki jingdeng na me, ba ngan ïoh tip aïu ngan sa leh ha me.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïalaw noh na lade ïa la ki jingdeng naduh u lum Horeb.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Moses u la ju rah noh ïa Ka Tabernakl u da pynïeng ïa ka shabar ka jaka shong dara, kham sha jngai na kata ka jaka shong dara; bad u la khot ïa ka, “Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.” Te ka la jia, ba uno uno ruh uba wad ïa U Trai u la mih shabar sha kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, kaba don shabar ka jaka shong dara.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ka la jia, mynba u Moses u la leit ha kata Ka Tabernakl, ba baroh uta u paidbah u la ïakhie buk, bad ki la ïaïeng ruh, uwei uwei baroh ha la ka jong ka jong ka jingkhang jong ka ïingjaiñ, bad ki la ïakhmih ïa u Moses, haduh ba u la leit hapoh kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba u Moses u la leit bsut ha kata Ka Tabernakl, uta u rishot lyoh u la hiar bad u la ïeng hajan ka jingkhang kata Ka Tabernakl: bad U Trai u la kren ha u Moses.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u paidbah baroh u la ïohi ïa uta u rishot lyoh ba u ïeng ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl; bad uta u paidbah u la ïakhie buk bad ki la ïamane uwei pa uwei keiñ, ha ka jingkhang la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la ïakren markhmat bad u Moses, kumba u briew u ju kren bad la u lok. Te u la leit phai noh pat sha kata ka dara; hynrei, u shakri jong u, u Joshua, u khun u Nun, u samla, um shym la kynriah shuh na kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Moses u la ong ha U Trai, “Ha khmih, me la ong ha nga, ‘To ïalam artet ïa une u paidbah:’ bad mem shym la pyntip ïa nga ïano men phah ryngkat bad nga. Pynban me la ong, ‘Nga ithuh ïa me da ka kyrteng, bad me la shem ruh ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong nga.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mynta, namar kata, nga kyrpad ïa me, lada nga la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, to pyni ha nga ïa ka lynti jong me, ba ngan ïoh ithuh ïa me, bad ba ngan ïoh shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me: to khmih ruh ba kane ka jaid bynriew ka long u paidlang jong me.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U te u la ong, “Ka khmat jong nga kan leit lem bad me bad ngan ai ka jingshongthait ruh ïa me.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha u, “Lymda leit ka khmat jong me lem bad ngi, te wat ïalam shuh ïa ngi nangne.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Naba da kumno yn tip hangne ba ma nga bad u paidlang jong me, ngi la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me? ym dei da kaba leit ma me ryngkat bad ngi, ba kumta, ma nga bad u paidlang jong me ngin sa long kiba la kyrpang na ki briew baroh kiba ha ka khmat ka pyrthei.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “Ngan leh ïa kane ruh ïa kaba me la kren: naba me la ïoh shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong nga, bad nga ithuh ïa me da ka kyrteng.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyni ha nga ïa ka burom jong me.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u la ong, “Ïa ka jingbha jong nga baroh ngan pynïaid ha shuwa jong me, bad ngan pynbna ïa ka kyrteng jong U Trai ha shuwa jong me; bad ngan ai ei ha uba ngan ai ei, bad ngan isynei ïa uba ngan isynei.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U la ong ruh, “Mem lah ban ïohi ïa ka khmat jong nga: naba u briew um lah keiñ ban ïohi ïa nga bad ba un im.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ruh, “Ha khmih, don ka jaka hajan jong nga, ha kaba men ïeng halor u mawsiang;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> te kan jia, katba ka burom jong nga ka ïaid lait, ba ngan buh ïa me hapoh ka krem jong uta u mawsiang, bad ngan tap ïa me da ka kti jong nga, katba nga dang ïaid lait;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ynda kumta, ngan weng noh ïa ka kti jong nga, te men ïohi ïa ka ingdong jong nga: hynrei, ïa ka khmat jong nga, yn ym ïohi keiñ.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To men shtah ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap kum kita ki banyngkong: bad ngan sa thoh halor kine ki maw lyngkniap ïa kita ki ktien kiba la don ha kita ki maw lyngkniap ki banyngkong, ïa kiba me la pynpait.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> To khreh te hamar kaba mynstep, bad to wan kiew dang step sha u lum Sinai, bad to wan ha nga hangta ha kliar uta u lum.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wat ai ba uno uno u briew ruh un wan kiew ryngkat bad me, lymne wat shah ba yn ïohi ïa uno uno u briew halor uta u lum baroh; lymne wat shah ïa ki kynhun langbrot lymne ïa ki jingri ban bam phlang ha khmat uta u lum.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la shtah ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap kum kita ki banyngkong; kumta, u Moses u la khie la dang step, bad u la leit kiew sha u lum Sinai, kumba U Trai u la lah hukum ïa u, bad u la leit lam ha la ka kti ïa kita ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai u la wan hiar ha u lyoh, bad u la ïeng hajan jong u hangta, bad u la pynbna ïa ka kyrteng U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la ïaid lait ha shuwa jong u, bad u la pynbna, “U Trai, U Trai, U Blei uba isynei bad ba aiei, uba ïaishah slem, bad uba kynrei ha ka jingbha bad ka jingshisha;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> uba bat ka jingisynei ïa ki hajar, uba map ïa ka jingpalat, bad ïa ka jingryngkang, bad ïa ka pop: bad un ym pynksan da lei lei ïa u bymman; uba pynwan ïa ka jingpalat jong ki kpa ha ki khun, bad ha ki khun jong ki khun, haduh ka balai bad ka basaw pateng bynriew.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Moses, da kaba leh kyrkieh, u la dem ngon haduh ka khyndew, bad u la mane dem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la ong, “Lada nga la shem mynta ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me, A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ai ba U Trai jong nga un leit ryngkat bad ngi; namar u long u paidlang ba-eh ryndang; to map ruh ïa ka jingpalat jong ngi, bad ïa ka pop jong ngi, bad to shim ïa ngi kum ka bynta jong me.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la ong te, “Ha khmih, nga thaw ïa ka jutang: ha khmat u paidlang jong me baroh ngan leh ïa ki jingkhyllah, kat kiba ym shym la leh ha ka pyrthei baroh, lymne ha kano kano ka jaid bynriew: bad uta u paidbah baroh ruh hapdeng kiba me don kin ïohi ïa ka kam U Trai, namar kata, ïa kaba ngan leh ïa me ka long kaba shyrkhei keiñ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “To men sumar ïa kata kaba nga hukum ïa me ha kane ka sngi: ha khmih, ngan beh noh na khmat jong me, ïa ki Amor, bad ïa ki Kanaan, bad ïa ki Hit, bad ïa ki Peris, bad ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Jebus.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To sumar ïa lade, ba men ym thaw ïa ka jutang bad ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri sha kaba me leit, ïoh ba kan long ka jingriam hapdeng jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, phin pynjot noh ïa ki duwan jong ki, bad phin pynpait ïa ki bleithaw jong ki, bad phin khet noh ïa ki 'law kyntang jong ki:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar men ym mane ïa uwei pat u blei; naba U Trai, uba ka kyrteng jong u, ‘U Bathut shen’, u long U Blei u bathut shen keiñ:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ïoh ba men thaw ïa ka jutang bad ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri, bad ki ïaleit klim bad ki blei jong ki, bad ki ïakñia ïa ki blei jong ki, bad khot lem ïa me ruh, bad ba me ruh men bam na ka jingkñia jong ki,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad men shim ruh na ki khun kynthei jong ki ha ki khun shynrang jong me, bad ki khun kynthei jong ki kin ïaleit klim bad ki blei jong ki, bad kin pynklim ruh ïa ki khun shynrang jong me bad ki blei jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Wat thaw ïa me ïa ki dur bleithaw ba la saiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “To men rakhe ïa Ka Niam U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat. Hynñiew sngi men bam ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat, kumba nga la hukum ïa me, ha la ka aïom ha u bnai Abib; namar ha uta u bnai Abib hi, me la mih noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Baroh ïa kaba la kha nyngkong na ka kpoh ka long ka jong nga; bad u shynrang baroh ïa uba la kha nyngkong hapdeng ki jingri jong me, la u long u masi ne u blang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, ïa u banyngkong jong ka kadda men siewspah da u khun langbrot: te lada men ym siewspah ïa u, te men kdiah ïa ka ryndang jong u. To men siewspah ruh ïa kiba la kha nyngkong baroh na ki khun shynrang jong me. Wat ai ïano ïano ruh ban paw suda ha khmat jong nga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Hynriew sngi men trei jingtrei, hynrei, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew men shongthait: ha ka aïom bet bad ha ka aïom ot men shong sngi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> To men rakhe ruh ïa Ka 'Niam Ki Taïew, jong ki soh nyngkong ka aïom ot Kew, bad ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Jinglum ha ka bakut ka snem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Lai sien shi snem, ki shynrang jong phi baroh kin ïapaw ha khmat U Trai U Blei, U Blei jong ki Israel keiñ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar ngan beh noh ïa kita ki jaid bynriew na khmat jong me, bad ngan pynïar ruh ïa ki pud jong me: lymne yn ym don mano mano ruh ban ikwah ïa ka ri jong me, haba men leit kiew ban paw ha khmat U Trai U Blei jong me, lai sien shi snem.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Wat ainguh ïa ka snam ka jingkñia jong nga lem bad u thiat: lymne wat ai ban pynsah haduh mynstep ïa ka jingkñia Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ka Jinglait.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> To men wallam sha ïing U Trai U Blei jong me ïa u babha tam eh na ki soh nyngkong ka ri jong me. Wat shet ïa u khun blang ha ka dud ka kmie jong u.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Moses, “To men thoh ïa kine ki ktien: namar katba kum kine ki ktien, nga la pynlong ïa ka jutang bad me bad u Israel ruh.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u la don hangta lem bad U Trai sawphew sngi bad sawphew miet; um shym la bam ïa u kpu, lymne dih ïa ka um. Te u la thoh halor kita ki maw lyngkniap ïa ki ktien kata ka jutang, ïa kita ki shiphew hukum keiñ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te mynba u Moses u la wan hiar na u lum Sinai bad kita ki ar tylli ki maw lyngkniap ka jingphla ha ka kti u Moses, mynba u la wan hiar na uta u lum, u Moses um tip ba ka snieh khmat jong u ka la tyngshaiñ ber katba u la kren bad U.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba u Aaron bad ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïohi ïa u Moses, ha khmih, ka snieh khmat jong u ka la tyngshaiñ ber; bad ki la ïasheptieng ban wan hajan jong u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hynrei, u Moses u la khot ïa ki; te u Aaron ruh bad ki rangbah u paidlang baroh ki la ïawan phai pat ha u: bad u Moses u la ïakren bad ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ynda kumta, ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïawan hajan: bad u la hukum ïa ki ïa kita baroh kiba U Trai u la lah kren ha u ha u lum Sinai.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te katba u Moses u la dang kren bad ki, u la buh ïa ka jingkah halor ka khmat jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, haba u Moses u la leit bsut ha khmat U Trai ban kren bad U, u la weng noh ïa kata ka jingkah, haduh ba un da mih noh; te haba u la mih noh, u la kren ha ki khun Israel ïa kata ïa kaba la hukum ïa u,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad ki khun Israel ki la ïohi ïa ka khmat u Moses, ba ka snieh khmat u Moses ka la tyngshaiñ ber: te u Moses u la buh pat ïa kata ka jingkah halor la ka khmat, haduh ha un da leit hapoh ban kren bad U."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Moses u la ïalum ruh ïa u paidlang baroh ki khun Israel, bad u la ong ha ki, “Kine ki long kita ki ktien ba U Trai u la hukum ïa phi ban leh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynriew sngi ka dei ban trei jingtrei, hynrei, ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew kan long ïa phi ka sngi bakhuid, ka Sabbaton keiñ ka jingshongthait ïa U Trai: jar uba trei jingtrei ha ka, yn pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Phi wat sliew ding ha ki ïing jong phi baroh ha kata ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Moses u la kren ha u paidlang ki khun Israel baroh, u da ong, “Kane ka long ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum, u da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> To phin shim napdeng jong phi ïa ka jingainguh ha U Trai: jar uba la sngewkloi ha la ka dohnud, to ai un wallam ïa ka, ban long ka jingainguh ha U Trai; ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka tama;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ïa ka babyrïong bad ïa ka basaw bthuh, bad ïa ka basaw syng-iang, bad ïa ka linen bani, bad ïa u 'ñiuh blang;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ïa ki snieh langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ki snieh takash, bad ïa ki dieng Shittim;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ïa ka umphniang ïa ka jingshai, bad ïa ki musla ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang baiwbih;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ïa ki maw Oniks, bad ïa ki maw ban thep ha ka ephod, bad ha ka jingdeng shadem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Bad uwei uwei baroh u bastad buit hapdeng jong phi un sa wan, bad un thaw ruh ïa kita baroh ïa kiba U Trai u la hukum;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ïa kata Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa ka ïingjaiñ jong ka, bad ïa ka jingsop jong ka, bad ïa ki jingpyndait jong ka, bad ïa ki lyntang jong ka, bad ïa ki dieng khap jong ka, ïa ki rishot jong ka, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ka;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ïa ka synduk, bad ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka, lem bad kata ka jingtap-isynei bad ïa ka jingkah ïa ka ban kah ïa ka;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ïa ka miej, bad ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa u 'pu pyni;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak ruh ban pynshai, bad ïa ki jingbuh jong ka, bad ïa ki sharak jong ka, lem bad ka umphniang ïa ka jingshai;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ïa ka duwan ka jingiwbih thang, bad ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka, bad ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang baiwbih, bad ïa ka pyrda ïa ka jingkhang, ha ka jaka rung shapoh Ka Tabernakl;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang, lem bad ka jingsliew ding tama jong ka, ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka ruh, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka dabor bad ïa ka sla'jat jong ka;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ïa ki pyrda jong ka phyllaw, ïa ki rishot jong ka, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ki, bad ïa ka pyrda ruh ïa ka jingkhang jong ka phyllaw;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ïa ki prek jong Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa ki snar jong ka phyllaw, lem bad ki tyllai jong ki;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ïa ki jaiñ ban leh ka kam, ïa ka ban leh ka kam keiñ ha ka jaka bakyntang, ïa ki jaiñkup bakyntang ïa u Aaron u lyngdoh, bad ïa ki jaiñkup ïa ki khun shynrang jong u ruh, ïa ka ban kam ha ka kam lyngdoh.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u paidlang ki khun Israel baroh ki la leit noh na khmat u Moses.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki la ïawan te, uwei uwei baroh kat uba ka dohnud jong u ka la kyntu eh ïa u, bad uwei uwei baroh kat kiba la ïamon na la ka mynsiem, ki la ïawallam ruh ïa ka jingainguh ïa U Trai, na ka bynta kata ka kam Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad na ka bynta ka jingshakri jong ka baroh, bad na ka bynta kita ki jaiñkup bakyntang.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki la ïawan te, ki shynrang bad ki kynthei ruh, kat kiba la mon hi ha la ka dohnud, bad ki la wallam ïa ki khadu, bad ïa ki sohshkor, bad ïa ki 'sah'ti, bad ïa ki kynjri, ïa ki kynja baroh ki jingdeng ksiar; u briew baroh keiñ uba la ainguh, u la ainguh da ka ksiar ha U Trai.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u briew baroh, ha uba la shem ïa ka babyrïong, bad ïa ka basaw bthuh, bad ïa ka basaw syng-iang, bad ïa ka linen bani, bad ïa u 'ñiuh blang, bad ïa ki snieh langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ki snieh takash, ki la ïawallam ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U briew baroh uba la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh da ka rupa bad ka tama, u la wallam ïa ka jingainguh keiñ ha U Trai: bad u briew baroh ha uba la shem ïa ki dieng Shittim ïa kano kano ruh ka kam jong ka jingshakri, u la wallam ïa ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki kynthei baroh ruh ki bastad jingmut ki la thir da la ki kti, ki la wallam ruh ïa kaba ki la lah thir, na ka babyrïong, bad na ka basaw bthuh, bad na ka basaw syng-iang, bad ïa ka linen bani.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kita ki kynthei baroh ruh ïa kiba la kyntu eh ha la ka dohnud ha ka jingstad ki la ïathir ïa u 'ñiuh blang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki nongsynshar te ki la ïawallam ïa ki maw Oniks, bad ïa ki maw ban thep ha ka ephod, bad ha ka jingdeng shadem;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ïa ki musla, bad ïa ka umphniang ïa ka jingshai, bad ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang baiwbih.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki khun Israel ki la ïawallam ïa ka jingainguh da la ka mon sngewbha hi ha U Trai; ki shynrang bad ki kynthei baroh, kiba la sngewmon hi, ki la ïawallam na ka bynta kita ki kam baroh, ïa kiba U Trai u la lah hukum ban leh da ka kti u Moses.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Moses te u la kren ha ki khun Israel, “Ha khmih, U Trai u la khot da ka kyrteng ïa u Besalil u khun u Uri, u khun u Hur, na ka jaid Judah;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad u la pyndap ïa u da U Mynsiem U Blei, ha ka jingstad, ha ka jingshemphang, bad ha ka jingsngewthuh, bad ha ka kynja jingtrei baroh;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ïa ka ban pyrkhat ïa ki kam baphylla, ïa ka ban trei keiñ ha ka ksiar, ha ka rupa, bad ha ka tama,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ha kaba shna ïa ki mawlynnai ban thep ïa ki, bad ha kaba mutdur ha ki dieng, ïa ka ban trei ïa ki jingtrei bastad baroh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la ai buit ha ka dohnud jong u ïa ka ban hikai ïa kiwei, ma u keiñ, bad u Aholiab, u khun u Ahisamakh, na ka jaid Dan.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ïa ki, u la pyndap da ka jingstad ka dohnud, ïa ka ban trei ïa ki kynja jingtrei baroh, ka jong uba mutdur, bad jong uba trei stad buit, bad jong uba suh pynpur, ha ka babyrïong, bad ha ka basaw bthuh, bad ha ka basaw syng-iang, bad ha ka linen bani ruh, bad ha kaba thain, da kaba leh keiñ ïa kano kano ruh ka kam, bad da kaba pyrkhat ïa ki jingtrei bastad buit."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ynda kumta, ki la ïatrei u Besalil bad u Aholiab, bad u briew baroh u bastad ka dohnud, ha kiba U Trai u la buh ka jingstad bad ka jingshemphang ban nang ban trei ïa ki kynja jingtrei baroh jong ki kam ka jaka kyntang, katba kum ïa kita baroh ba U Trai u la lah hukum.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Moses u la khot ïa u Besalil bad ïa u Aholiab, bad ïa u briew u bastad ka dohnud baroh, ha kiba U Trai u la lah buh ka jingstad, uwei uwei baroh keiñ uba ka dohnud jong u ka la kyntu eh ïa u ban wan trei ïa kata ka kam;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ki la shim na u Moses ïa kita ki jingainguh baroh, ïa kiba la lah wallam ki khun Israel ïa ka ban trei ïa ka kam ka jaka kyntang, ban thaw ïa ka. Ki la ïa nang wallam shuh ha u ïa ki jingainguh basngewmon bha hi man ka step,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te kita ki riewstad baroh kiba la trei ïa ka kam jong ka jaka kyntang, ki la wan noh uwei uwei baroh na la ka kam ïa kaba ki dang ïathaw;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ki la kren ha u Moses, ki da ong, “Kita ki briew ki ïawallam shibun nalor kaba biang ïa ka jingtrei jong kata ka kam, ïa kaba U Trai u la hukum ban thaw keiñ.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Moses u la ai hukum, bad ki la ïa-pynbna ïa ka ha ka jaka shong dara baroh, da kaba ong, “Wat ai ba u shynrang lymne ka kynthei ban khreh ei ei ruh na ka bynta ka jingainguh ïa ka jaka kyntang.” Kumta keiñ, la khang noh ïa uta u paidbah ba kin ym wallam shuh,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> namar ki la don kiei kiei ruh kiba biang eh, bad la tam ruh, ban thaw ïa ka kam baroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u briew baroh u bastad hapdeng kita kiba trei ïa ka kam Ka Tabernakl u la thaw shiphew tylli ki jingkah da ka linen bani ba la thir; bad ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, lem bad ki Kherub da ka kam bastad ki la thaw ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Arphew phra pruh ka lynter kawei ka jingkah, bad saw pruh ka pyngkiang kawei ka jingkah: ki jingkah baroh ki la don kajuh ka jingthew keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la pynïasoh lang san tylli ki jingkah: ïa kita ki san tylli kiwei pat ruh u la pynïasoh lang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki kyrwoh da ka babyrïong ba ka rmiang kawei ka jingkah, ha ka bakut eh ha kata ka jingpynïasoh: kumjuh u la thaw ha ka rmiang kaba harud eh kawei pat ka jingkah, ha kata ka jingpynïasoh ka ba-ar;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh u la thaw ha kawei ka jingkah, bad sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh u la thaw ha ka rmiang jong ka jingkah kaba ha kata ka jingpynïasoh jong ka ba-ar: kawei ka kyrwoh ka ïapyrshah bad kawei pat ka kyrwoh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la thaw sanphew tylli ki jingpyndait ksiar, bad u la pynïasoh lang ruh ïa kita ki jingkah da kita ki jingpyndait: kumta keiñ, ka la long kawei Ka Tabernakl.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki jingkah da u 'ñiuh blang, ïa ka ban long ka jingsop ïa Ka Tabernakl: khatwei tylli ki jingkah u la thaw ïa ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Laiphew pruh, ka lynter kawei ka jingkah, bad saw pruh, ka pyngkiang kawei ka jingkah: kita ki khatwei tylli ki jingkah ki la don kajuh ka jingthew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la pynïasoh san tylli ki jingkah kyrpang, bad hynriew tylli ki jingkah kyrpang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la thaw sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh ha ka rmiang eh jong ka jingkah ha ka jingpynïasoh, bad sanphew tylli ki kyrwoh u la thaw ha ka rmiang kata ka jingkah ka bapynïasoh ïa ka ba-ar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la thaw ruh sanphew tylli ki jingpyndait tama ïa ka ban pynïasoh lang ïa ka jingsop, ba kan long kawei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka jingtap ïa kata ka jingsop da ki snieh langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ka jingtap da ki snieh takash halor kata.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki lyntang ïa kata Ka Tabernakl da u dieng Shittim, da kaba pynïeng ïa ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka lynter kawei ka lyntang, shiphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang kawei ka lyntang, shi pruh shiteng.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kawei ka lyntang ka don ar tylli ki tnaw, ba la pyndait uwei ha uwei: kumne u la leh ïa ki lyntang Ka Tabernakl baroh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la thaw ruh ïa ki lyntang ïa kata Ka Tabernakl; ïa arphew tylli ki lyntang ïa ka liang kaba shaphang shathie;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ïa sawphew tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa u la thaw hapoh kita ki arphew tylli ki lyntang; ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei ka lyntang ïa ki baroh ar ki tnaw jong ka, bad ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei pat ka lyntang ïa ki baroh ar ki tnaw jong ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ïa kawei pat ka liang jong Ka Tabernakl, kaba shaphang shatei, u la thaw arphew tylli ki lyntang,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> lem bad ki sawphew tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa jong ki; ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei ka lyntang, bad ar tylli ki thliew tnaw hapoh kawei pat ka lyntang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ïa kata ka liang kaba shaphang sepngi jong Ka Tabernakl u la thaw hynriew tylli ki lyntang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ar tylli ki lyntang u la thaw, ïa ki dong jong Ka Tabernakl ha kata ka liang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad la pynïasoh ïa ki shapoh, bad la pynïasoh lang ïa ki na shaneng ruh ha kawei ka kyrwoh: kumne keiñ, u la leh ïa ki baroh ar ha kita ki baroh ar ki dong.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad la don phra tylli ki lyntang, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki, ki la long khathynriew ki thliew tnaw rupa; ar ar tylli ki thliew tnaw keiñ hapoh kawei kawei ka lyntang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki dieng khap da u dieng Shittim; san tylli ïa ki lyntang jong kawei ka liang jong Ka Tabernakl,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad san tylli ki dieng khap ïa ki lyntang kawei pat ka liang Ka Tabernakl, bad san tylli ki dieng khap ïa ki lyntang Ka Tabernakl ha kata ka liang kaba shaphang sepngi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa uta u dieng khap uba hapdeng ban kot baroh shilynter jong kita ki lyntang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la suit ksiar ïa kita ki lyntang, bad u la thaw ïa ki kyrwoh ksiar jong ki, ki kyrwoh ïa kita ki dieng khap keiñ, bad u la suit ksiar ruh ïa kita ki dieng khap.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka jingkah pdeng da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir: bad ki Kherub u la thaw ïa ka da ka jingtrei bastad.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka, saw tylli ki rishot da u dieng Shittim, bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ki: ki kyrwoh jong ki ruh ki long da ka ksiar; bad u la saiñ ïa ki saw tylli ki thliew tnaw rupa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa ka pyrda ïa ka jingkhang kata Ka Tabernakl, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir, da kaba suh pynpur;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ïa kita ki san tylli ki rishot jong ka lem bad ki kyrwoh jong ki: bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ki khlieh jong ki, bad ïa ki shrong jong ki: hynrei, ki san tylli ki thliew tnaw jong ki, ki la long da ka tama."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Besalil u la thaw ïa kata ka synduk da u dieng Shittim; ar pruh shiteng, ka lynter jong ka, shi pruh shiteng, ka pyngkiang jong ka, bad shi pruh shiteng, ka jingjrong jong ka ruh:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la suit ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla shapoh bad shabar, bad u la thaw ka pansngiat da ka ksiar ïa ka, baroh sawdong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la saiñ ïa ka, saw tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar ha ki sawdong jong ka; ar tylli ki kyrwoh ha kawei ka liang, bad ar tylli ki kyrwoh ha kawei pat ka liang jong ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la pynphrung ïa kita ki dieng jingbah ha kita ki kyrwoh ha ki liang jong kata ka synduk, ïa ka ban bah ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka jingtap-isynei da ka ksiar banylla; ar pruh shiteng, ka lynter jong ka, bad shi pruh shiteng, ka pyngkiang jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la thaw ruh ar tylli ki Kherub ksiar; shitylli u la thaw ïa ki na kajuh ka dkhot, kata na baroh ar ki tduh kata ka jingtap-isynei;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ïa uwei u Kherub na ka tduh kaba shaphang shane, bad uwei u Kherub na kata ka tduh kaba shaphang shatei: na kata ka jingtap-isynei hi keiñ u la thaw ïa kita ki Kherub na ki tduh jong ka baroh ar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kita ki Kherub da kaba pyiar ïa la ki thapniang sha jrong, ki la kah da la ki thapniang ïa kata ka jingtap-isynei, bad ki la phai markhmat; shaphang kata ka jingtap-isynei keiñ ki la ïa-peit ki khmat jong kita ki Kherub.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa kata ka miej da u dieng Shittim: ar pruh, ka lynter jong ka, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, shi pruh; bad shi pruh shiteng, ka jingjrong jong ka;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad u la suit ïa ka da ka ksiar banylla, bad u la thaw ïa ka, ka pansngiat da ka ksiar baroh sawdong.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U la thaw ïa ka shrong ruh ïa ka, shi khup baroh sawdong, bad u la thaw ïa ka pansngiat ksiar ïa kata ka shrong baroh sawdong.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la saiñ ïa ka, saw tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar, bad u la buh ïa kita ki kyrwoh ha kita ki saw ki dong jong ka kiba ha ki saw ki kjat jong ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha marpyrshah kata ka shrong la don kita ki kyrwoh, ki kyrwoh ïa kita ki dieng jingbah keiñ ïa ka ban bah ïa kata ka miej.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa kita ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ki de, ïa ka ban bah ïa kata ka miej.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U la thaw ruh da ka ksiar banylla ïa kita ki pliang kiba halor kata ka miej, ïa ki khuri jong ka, bad ïa ki siang jong ka, bad ïa ki khiew jong ka ruh, bad ïa ki jingtap ban tap da ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la thaw te ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak da ka ksiar banylla: da kaba shoh tylli shi dkhot keiñ u la thaw ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak; ïa ka met jong ka, bad ïa ki tnat jong ka, ïa ki khiew jong ka, ïa ki shrong jong ka, bad ïa ki syntiew jong ka ruh, ki la long da kata kajuh hi keiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad hynriew tylli ki tnat kiba mih noh na ki liang jong ka; lai tylli ki tnat jong kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak na kawei ka liang jong ka, bad lai tylli ki tnat jong kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak na kata kawei pat ka liang jong ka;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ha kawei ka tnat lai tylli ki khiew ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam, ka shrong bad u syntiew; bad ha kawei pat ka tnat lai tylli ki khiew ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam, ka shrong bad u syntiew: kumjuh ruh ha kita ki hynriew tylli ki tnat ba-mih noh na kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ha kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak la don ruh saw tylli ki khiew ba la thaw kum ki soh Khyllam, ki shrong jong ka bad ki syntiew jong ka ruh,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ka shrong hapoh ar tylli na ki tnat jong ka, bad ka shrong hapoh ar tylli na ki tnat jong ka, bad ka shrong hapoh ar tylli na ki tnat jong ka, katba kum kita ki hynriew ki tnat ba-mih noh na ka keiñ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki shrong jong ki bad ki tnat jong ki, ki la long na kajuh: baroh kawei keiñ ka la long ba la shoh tylli na ka ksiar banylla.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki hynñiew tylli ki sharak jong ka, bad ïa ki nap lur jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka ruh, da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U la thaw ïa ka bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh da shi talent ka ksiar banylla.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa ka duwan ka jingiwbih thang da u dieng Shittim: shi pruh, ka lynter jong ka, bad shi pruh, ka pyngkiang jong ka ruh, kaba sawdong keiñ; bad ka jingjrong jong ka, ar pruh: ki reng jong ka ki la long na kajuh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ka, ïa ka khlieh jong ka, bad ïa ki liang jong ka baroh sawdong, bad ïa ki reng jong ka: u la thaw ruh ïa ka, ïa ka pansngiat da ka ksiar baroh sawdong.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka, ar tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar hapoh ka pansngiat jong ka, na ki ar tylli ki dong jong ka, ha ki ar tylli ki krung jong ka, kita ki kyrwoh ïa ki dieng jingbah keiñ ïa ka ban bah ïa ka da ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa kita ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad u la suit da ka ksiar ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh ka bakyntang, bad ïa kata ka jingiwbih thang basngur da ki musla ki baiwbih, kum ka rukom u apothekari."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang da u dieng Shittim: ka lynter jong ka, san pruh; bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, san pruh; kaba sawdong keiñ; bad ka jingjrong jong ka, lai pruh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki reng jong ka ha ki saw ki dong jong ka; kita ki reng jong ka ki la long na kajuh: bad u la suit da ka tama ïa ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ki pliang baroh jong kata ka duwan, ïa ki khiew, bad ïa ki siang, bad ïa ki khuri, bad ïa ki proh doh, bad ïa ki pliang dieng: ïa kita ki pliang baroh u la thaw da ka tama.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa kata ka duwan ïa ka jaka sliew ding da ka tama, kum ka kriah hapoh ka thliew jong ka na shapoh, ban kot haduh ka pdeng jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la saiñ saw tylli ki kyrwoh ïa ki saw ki dong jong kata ka jaka sliew ding da ka tama, ïa ka ban long ki kyrwoh ïa ki dieng jingbah keiñ;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la thaw ïa kita ki dieng jingbah da u dieng Shittim, bad u la suit da ka tama ïa ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la pynphrung ruh ïa kita ki dieng jingbah ha kita ki kyrwoh kiba ha ki krung jong kata ka duwan, ïa ka ban bah ïa ka da ki; ïa ka thliew ka duwan u la thaw da ki lyntang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka dabor da ka tama, bad ïa ka kjat jong ka da ka tama, da ki ïitkhmih kita ki kynthei bashakri kiba shakri ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka phyllaw ruh: ha ka liang kaba shaphang shathie, ki pyrda kata ka phyllaw ki la long da ka linen bani ba la thir, shispah pruh:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ki rishot jong ki, arphew; bad ki thliew tnaw tama jong ki, arphew de; ki bnoh jong ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki da ka rupa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ha ka liang kaba shatei, shispah pruh; ki rishot jong ki, ki long arphew; bad ki thliew tnaw tama jong ki, ki long arphew; ki bnoh jong ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki da ka rupa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ha ka liang kaba shaphang sepngi, ki pyrda ki la long sanphew pruh, ki rishot jong ki, shiphew, bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki ruh, shiphew; ki bnoh jong kita ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki da ka rupa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha ka liang kaba shaphang mihngi, sanphew pruh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki pyrda kata kawei ka liang jong ka khyrdop ki la long khatsan pruh; ki rishot jong ki, lai tylli; bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki ruh, lai tylli.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad kumta, ïa kata kawei pat ka liang: ha baroh ar liang jong ka khyrdop ka phyllaw u la thaw ïa ki pyrda, khatsan pruh; ki rishot jong ki, lai tylli; bad ki thliew tnaw jong ki ruh, lai tylli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Baroh ki pyrda jong kata ka phyllaw baroh sawdong ki la long da ka linen bani ba la thir.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki thliew tnaw jong kita ki rishot ki la long da ka tama; ki bnoh jong ki rishot bad ki shrong jong ki da ka rupa; bad ïa ki khlieh jong ki la suit rupa; bad ïa ki rishot baroh kata ka phyllaw la thaw shrong da ka rupa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka pyrda jong ka khyrdop kata ka phyllaw ka la long da kaba suh, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang ruh, bad ka linen bani ba la thir: bad ka lynter, arphew pruh; bad ka jingjrong ha ka pyngkiang, san pruh; ban ïabiang bad ki pyrda jong kata ka phyllaw.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki rishot jong ki ruh ki long saw tylli; bad ki thliew tnaw tama jong ki ruh, saw tylli; ki bnoh jong ki da ka rupa, bad ïa ki khlieh jong ki bad ïa ki shrong jong ki la suit da ka rupa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki prek baroh jong kata Ka Tabernakl, bad jong kata ka phyllaw baroh sawdong, ki la long da ka tama.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kane ka long ka jingkheiñ ka jong Ka Tabernakl, Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla keiñ, ïa kiba la kheiñ da ka hukum u Moses, ïa ka kam jong ki Lebi, da ka kti u Ithamar, u khun u Aaron u lyngdoh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Besalil u khun u Uri, u khun u Hur, na ka jaid Judah, u la thaw ïa kita baroh ïa kiba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> lem bad u ruh la don u Aholiab, u khun u Ahisamakh, na ka jaid Dan, u nongmut-dak, u nongtrei bastad buit, bad uba nang suh pynpur ha ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ha ka jaiñ linen bani.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kata ka ksiar baroh, ka ksiar ka jingainguh keiñ, kaba la leit ha kata ka kam baroh jong ka jaka kyntang, ka la long arphew khyndai talent, bad hynñiewspah laiphew shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka rupa jong kita kiba la kheiñ na uta u paidlang ka la long shispah talent, bad shi hajar hynñiewspah bad hynñiewphew san shekel, katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Shi bekah ïa uwei uwei baroh, kata ka long, shiteng shekel katba kum ka shekel ka jaka kyntang, na ka bynta uwei uwei baroh uba la hap kheiñ ïa u, naduh arphew snem ka rta bad ba tam, na ka bynta hynriewspah lai hajar bad sanspah sanphew ki briew.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad na kita ki shispah ki talent rupa la saiñ ïa kita ki thliew tnaw kata ka jaka kyntang, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong kata ka jingkah pdeng; shispah ki thliew tnaw da kita ki shispah talent, shi talent talent keiñ ïa kawei kawei ka thliew tnaw.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad na kita ki shi hajar hynñiewspah bad hynñiewphew san shekel u la thaw ïa ki bnoh ïa ki rishot, bad u la suit rupa ïa ki khlieh jong ki, bad u la ot shrong ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad kata ka tama ka jingainguh ka la long hynñiewphew talent, bad ar hajar sawspah shekel.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad na kata u la thaw ïa kita ki thliew tnaw ïa ki jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad ïa kata ka duwan tama, bad ïa kata ka jaka sliew ding tama ïa ka, bad ïa ki pliang baroh jong kata ka duwan,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ïa kita ki thliew tnaw kata ka phyllaw baroh sawdong ruh, bad ïa kita ki thliew tnaw ka khyrdop ka phyllaw, bad ïa ki prek baroh Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa ki snar baroh kata ka phyllaw baroh sawdong."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad na kata ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, ki la ïathaw ïa ki jaiñ ban kam jingkam, ïa ka ban trei ha ka jaka bakyntang, bad ïa ki jaiñkup bakyntang ïa u Aaron, kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa kata ka ephod da ka ksiar, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la shoh stang kum ki sla ïa kata ka ksiar, bad ki la ot ksai ksiar ïa ka, ïa ka ban suh ha kata ka babyrïong, bad ha kata ka basaw bthuh, bad ha kata ka basaw syng-iang, bad ha kata ka linen bani, da ka jingtrei bastad.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki la thaw ïa ki tyrpeng ïa ka, ban pynïasoh lang ïa ka: na ki baroh ar ki rmiang la pynïasoh lang ïa ka keiñ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kata ka jingpanpoh baphylla ka ephod jong u, kaba halor jong ka, ka la long na kajuh ha ka jingtrei jong ka; da ka ksiar, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki la shna ïa ki maw Oniks ba la thep ha ki shrong ksiar, ba la pruid kum ka jingpynpruid ïa ka mohor, da ki kyrteng ki khun Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la buh ïa ki ha ki tyrpeng jong kata ka ephod, ban long ki maw ka jingpynkynmaw ïa ki khun Israel; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U la thaw ruh ïa ka jingdeng shadem da ka jingtrei bastad, kum ka jingtrei ïa kata ka ephod; da ka ksiar, da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka la long sawdong; ki la thaw ar syrtap ïa kata ka jingdeng shadem: ka lynter jong ka, shi tda; bad ka pyngkiang jong ka ruh, shi tda; kaba ar syrtap keiñ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la thep ha ka, ïa ki saw kyrdan ki maw: shi kyrdan da u Sardios, u Topas, bad u Karbunkl: kane ka kyrdan banyngkong keiñ;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ka kyrdan ba-ar, da u Emerald, u Sapphir bad u Diamond;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ka kyrdan balai, da u Ligur, u Agate, bad u Amethyst;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ka kyrdan basaw, da u Beryl, u Oniks, bad u Jasper: bad la thep ïa ki ha la ki jaka ha ki shrong ksiar.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kita ki maw ki la long katba kum ki kyrteng ki khun Israel, khat-ar tylli keiñ, katba kum ki kyrteng jong ki uwei uwei baroh bad la ka kyrteng kyrteng: kum ki jingpruid ka mohor, katba kum kita ki khat-ar jaid keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ha ki rmiang kata ka jingdeng shadem ki la thaw ïa ki kynjri ba la thain da ka ksiar banylla.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki la thaw ruh, ar tylli ki shrong ksiar, bad ar tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar, bad ki la pyndait ïa kita ar tylli ki kyrwoh ha ki rmiang jong kata ka jingdeng shadem;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ki la buh ïa kita ki ar tylli ki kynjri ksiar ba la thain ha kita ki ar tylli ki kyrwoh ha ki rmiang jong kata ka jingdeng shadem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ïa kita ki ar tylli ki tduh jong kita ki kynjri ba la thain ki la pyndait ha kita ki ar tylli ki shrong, bad ki la buh ïa ki ha ki tyrpeng kata ka ephod shakhmat.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la thaw ruh, ar tylli ki kyrwoh ksiar, bad ki la buh ïa ki ha ki ar ki dong kata ka jingdeng shadem, ha kata ka rmiang jong ka kaba ha ka liang jong kata ka ephod na shapoh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki la thaw ar tylli kiwei pat ki kyrwoh ksiar, bad ki la buh ïa ki ha ki baroh ar liang kata ka ephod narum, shakhmat jong ka, ha marpyrshah ka jingpyndait jong ka, haneng ka jingpanpoh baphylla jong kata ka ephod.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la teh ïa kata ka jingdeng shadem na ki kyrwoh jong ka, ha ki kyrwoh jong kata ka ephod, da u ksai babyrïong, ba kan ïoh long haneng kata ka jingpanpoh baphylla jong kata ka ephod, ba kata ka jingdeng shadem kan ym ïohlait na kata ka ephod, kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la thaw ïa ka barandi jong kata ka ephod da kaba la thain, da ka babyrïong baroh;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> te u la pong ryndang ïa kata ka barandi na marpdeng jong ka, kum ka thliew jong ka jymphong kieng, bad la kyntang baroh sawdong ïa kata ka thliew ka jingphong, ba kan ym kad.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki la thaw ruh ha ki rmiang kata ka barandi ïa ki soh Pong da ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, bad ka linen bani ba la thir.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la thaw ïa ki shakuriaw da ka ksiar banylla, bad ki la buh ïa kita ki shakuriaw hapdeng kita ki soh Pong, ha ka rmiang kata ka barandi baroh sawdong hapdeng kita ki soh Pong;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ïa ka shakuriaw bad u soh Pong, ïa ka shakuriaw bad u soh Pong, ha ka rmiang kata ka barandi baroh sawdong, ban shakri ha ka; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki la thaw ïa ki sopti da ka linen bani ba la thain ïa u Aaron, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ïa ka meitr da ka linen bani, bad ïa ki tupia ba-itynnad da ka linen bani, bad ïa ki patlun de da ka linen bani ba la thir,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ïa ka jingpanpoh da ka linen bani ba la thir, bad ka babyrïong, bad ka basaw bthuh, bad ka basaw syng-iang, da kaba suh; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki la thaw ïa ka sla syntiew jong ka pansngiat bakhuid da ka ksiar banylla, bad ki la pruid halor jong ka, kum ki jingpruid ka mohor, “Ka jingkhuid ha U Trai.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki la teh ha ka da u ksai babyrïong, ban pynneh ïa ka haneng halor kata ka meitr; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta la pyndep ïa ka kam baroh Ka Tabernakl, kata ka ïingjaiñ jong ka jingïaseng keiñ: ki khun Israel ki la leh ruh katba kum ïa kata baroh ba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses, kumta keiñ ki la leh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki la ïawallam te ïa kata Ka Tabernakl ha u Moses, ïa kata ka ïingjaiñ keiñ, bad ïa ki jingbuh jong ka baroh, ïa ki jingpyndait jong ka, ïa ki lyntang jong ka, ïa ki dieng khap jong ka, bad ïa ki rishot jong ka ruh, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ka;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad ïa ka jingtap da ki snieh ki langbrot shynrang ba la suit rong saw, bad ïa ka jingtap da ki snieh takash, bad ïa ka jingkah ban sop;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ïa ka synduk ka jingphla, bad ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka, bad ïa kata ka jingtap-isynei;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ïa kata ka miej ruh, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ki 'pu pyni;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar banylla lem bad ki sharak jong ka, ïa kita ki sharak ban buh ter ter keiñ, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad ïa ka umphniang ïa ka jingshai;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ïa kata ka duwan ksiar, bad ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, bad ïa ka jingiwbih thang musla, bad ïa ka pyrda ïa ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ïa kata ka duwan tama, bad ïa ka jingsliew ding tama kaba dei ïa ka, ïa ki dieng jingbah jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, ïa ka dabor bad ïa ka kjat jong ka;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ïa ki pyrda jong kata ka phyllaw, ïa ki rishot jong ka ruh, bad ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ka, bad ïa ka pyrda ïa ka khyrdop kata ka phyllaw, ïa ki tyllai jong ka, bad ïa ki snar jong ka, bad ïa ki pliang baroh jong ka kam Ka Tabernakl, ïa ka ïingjaiñ kata ka jingïaseng keiñ;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ïa ki jaiñ ban kam jingkam, ïa ka ban trei ha ka jaka bakyntang, bad ïa kita ki jaiñ bakyntang de ïa u Aaron lyngdoh, bad ïa ki jaiñkup ki khun shynrang jong u, ïa ka ban kam ha ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Katba kum ïa kata baroh ba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses, kumta keiñ, ki khun Israel ki la trei ïa kata ka kam baroh.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u Moses u la khmih ïa kata ka kam baroh, te, ha khmih, ki la lah leh ïa ka kumba U Trai u la lah hukum, kumta hi keiñ, ki la leh ïa ka: bad u Moses u la kyrkhu ïa ki."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te U Trai u la kren ha u Moses, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ha ka sngi ka banyngkong jong u bnai banyngkong men sa pynïeng ïa Ka Tabernakl, ïa ka ïing jong ka jingïaseng keiñ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Men buh ruh hangta ïa ka synduk ka jingphla, bad to tap ïa kata ka synduk da kata ka jingkah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> To men wallam ruh ïa ka miej, bad men buh ryntih ïa kita kiba dei ban buh ryntih halor jong ka; bad to men wallam hapoh ruh ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak, bad to tbeh ïa ki sharak jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> To men buh ruh ïa ka duwan ksiar jong ka jingiwbih thang ha khmat ka synduk ka jingphla, bad to pynïeng ïa ka pyrda ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> To men buh ruh ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang ha khmat ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl jong ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> to men buh ruh ïa ka dabor hapdeng ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng bad kata ka duwan, bad men theh um ha ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To men pynïeng ïa ka phyllaw ruh baroh sawdong, bad to woh de ïa ka pyrda ha ka khyrdop kata ka phyllaw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad to men shim ïa ka umphniang bapynsleh, to pynsleh ruh ïa Ka Tabernakl, bad ïa kita baroh kiba don ha ka, bad men pynkyntang ïa ka, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh: te kan long ka bakyntang khuid.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To men pynsleh ruh ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang, bad ïa ki pliang jong ka baroh, bad to pynkyntang ïa kata ka duwan: te kan long ka duwan ka bakyntang tam eh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To men pynsleh ruh ïa ka dabor bad ïa ka kjat jong ka, to pynkyntang ïa ka ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Men wallam te ïa u Aaron bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u ha ka jingkhang jong Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, bad to sait ïa ki da ka um,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad men pynphong ïa u Aaron da kita ki jaiñkup bakyntang, bad to pynsleh ïa u, to pynkyntang ruh ïa u, ba un ïoh kam ha nga ha ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To men wallam ruh ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad to pynphong ïa ki da ki sopti,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad to men pynsleh ïa ki kumba me la pynsleh ïa u kpa jong ki, ba kin ïoh kam ha nga ha ka jingkam lyngdoh: kumta keiñ, ka jingpynsleh jong ki kan long ka jinglong lyngdoh ha la ka rta lyngba ki pateng la pateng bynriew jong ki.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Moses u la leh: katba kum ïa kata baroh ba U Trai u la hukum ïa u, kumta keiñ, u la leh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, ha u bnai banyngkong ha ka snem ba-ar, ha ka sngi ka banyngkong jong uta u bnai, la pynïeng ïa kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Moses u la pynïeng ïa kata Ka Tabernakl, bad u la pynskhem ïa ki thliew tnaw jong ka, bad u la pynïeng ïa ki lyntang jong ka, bad u la phrung ïa ki dieng khap jong ka, bad u la pynïeng ïa ki rishot jong ka;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad u la siang ïa kata ka jaiñsop halor kata Ka Tabernakl, bad u la buh ïa ka jingtap jong kata ka jaiñsop halor jong ka; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u la shim bad u la thep ruh ïa ka jingphla hapoh kata ka synduk, bad u la phrung ïa kita ki dieng jingbah ha kata ka synduk, bad u la buh ïa ka jingtap-isynei halor kata ka synduk:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad u la wallam ruh ïa kata ka synduk hapoh Ka Tabernakl, bad u la woh ïa kata ka jingkah pdeng, bad u la kah ïa ka synduk ka jingphla; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kata ka miej ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ha ka liang kata Ka Tabernakl kaba shaphang shatei, shabar kata ka jingkah pdeng.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la buh beit ïa kita ki kpu halor jong ka ha khmat U Trai; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kata ka dieng pynïeng sharak ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng, ha marpyrshah kata ka miej, ha ka liang kata Ka Tabernakl kaba shaphang shathie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u la tbeh ïa kita ki sharak ha khmat U Trai; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u la buh ïa kata ka duwan ksiar ha Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng ha khmat kata ka jingkah pdeng,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad u la thang ïa ka jingiwbih thang halor jong ka; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la woh ïa kata ka pyrda ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u la buh ïa ka duwan ka jingainguh thang hajan ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl, ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng keiñ, bad u la kñia halor jong ka ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ïa ka jingainguh bam; kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U la buh ruh ïa kata ka dabor hapdeng ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng bad kata ka duwan, bad u la theh um hangta ïa ka ban sait,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> te u Moses bad u Aaron bad ki khun shynrang jong u ki la thet ïa la ki kti bad ki la sait ïa la ki sla'jat ha ka;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> haba ki la ïaleit hapoh kata ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, bad haba ki la ïawan hajan kata ka duwan, ki la ju sait, ki la ju thet keiñ: kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la pynïeng ïa kata ka phyllaw baroh sawdong Ka Tabernakl bad kata ka duwan, bad u la woh ïa kata ka pyrda ha ka khyrdop ka phyllaw. Kumta keiñ, u Moses u la pyndep ïa kata ka kam.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u lyoh u la tap lup ïa ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, bad ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u Moses um lah ban rung hapoh kata ka ïingjaiñ ka jingïaseng, naba uta u lyoh u neh halor jong ka, bad kata ka burom U Trai ka la pyndap ïa kata Ka Tabernakl.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba uta u lyoh u la ïeng noh na Ka Tabernakl, ki khun Israel ki la ju sdang leit ha ki jingleit jong ki baroh;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> hynrei, lada uta u lyoh um ïeng noh, kumta te, kim ju leit jingleit keiñ tad ynda kata ka sngi ba u la ïeng noh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Naba uta u lyoh jong U Trai u la don halor kata Ka Tabernakl mynsngi, bad ka ding ka la don halor jong ka mynmiet, ha khmat ka ïing Israel baroh, ha ki jingleit jong ki baroh."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;